				</ul>','Plugin Alerting Disabled'=>'外掛警示已停用','Configuration Issue'=>'組態問題','Disconnect Timestamp'=>'中斷連線時間戳記','Disconnected'=>'已中斷連線','Site ID'=>'網站 ID','Connect Timestamp'=>'連線時間戳記','false'=>'否','true'=>'是','Connected'=>'已連線','Redirect to the URL below'=>'重新導向至下方網址','Show the standard Wordfence blocked message'=>'顯示標準 Wordfence 封鎖訊息','(unknown)'=>'（未知）','Enable Wordfence translations'=>'啟用 Wordfence 翻譯','(empty)'=>'（空）','Scanner'=>'掃描器','Diagnostic connection information for Wordfence Central.'=>'Wordfence Central 的診斷連線資訊。','Diagnostic Wordfence settings/constants.'=>'診斷 Wordfence 設定/常數。','Wordfence Settings'=>'Wordfence 設定','<strong>CAPTCHA EXPIRED</strong>: The CAPTCHA verification for this login attempt has expired. Please try again.'=>'<strong>CAPTCHA 已過期</strong>：此登入嘗試的 CAPTCHA 驗證已過期。請再試一次。','0.1 (probably a bot)'=>'0.1（可能是機器人）','If you were attempting to log in to this site, <a href="%s"><strong>Verify and Log In</strong></a>'=>'如果您正嘗試登入此網站，<a href="%s"><strong>請驗證並登入</strong></a>','Please verify a login attempt for your account on: %s'=>'請驗證您的帳號在以下網站的登入嘗試：%s','<strong>VERIFICATION REQUIRED</strong>: Additional verification is required for login. If there is a valid account for the provided login credentials, please check the email address associated with it for a verification link to continue logging in.'=>'<strong>需要驗證</strong>：登入需要額外的驗證。如果提供的登入認證有對應的有效帳號，請檢查與該帳號關聯的電子郵件地址以取得驗證連結，並繼續登入。','Disconnected from Wordfence Central'=>'已與 Wordfence Central 中斷連線','Unable to communicate with Wordfence Central'=>'無法與 Wordfence Central 通訊','The current site URL does not match the Wordfence Central connection information. Local connection information has been removed, but %s is still registered in Wordfence Central.'=>'目前的網站網址與 Wordfence Central 連線資訊不符。本機連線資訊已移除，但 %s 仍在 Wordfence Central 中註冊。','Failed obtaining vulnerability data, skipping check.'=>'取得漏洞資料失敗，略過檢查。','Failed obtaining core vulnerability data, skipping check.'=>'取得核心程式漏洞資料失敗，略過檢查。','Learn more'=>'進一步了解','WordPress version %s is now available. Please upgrade immediately to get the latest fixes and compatibility updates from WordPress.'=>'WordPress 版本 %s 現已推出。請立即升級以取得 WordPress 的最新修正和相容性更新。','WordPress version %s is now available for your site\'s current branch. Please upgrade immediately to get the latest security updates from WordPress.'=>'您的網站目前分支有 WordPress 版本 %s 可用。請立即升級以取得 WordPress 的最新安全性更新。','WordPress version %s is now available for your site\'s current branch. Please upgrade immediately to get the latest fixes and compatibility updates from WordPress.'=>'您的網站目前分支有 WordPress 版本 %s 可用。請立即升級以取得 WordPress 的最新修正和相容性更新。','Disconnect All'=>'全部中斷連線','If this is a single site with multiple domains or subdomains, you can dismiss this message.'=>'如果這是具有多個網域或子網域的單一網站，您可以關閉此訊息。','This may cause duplicated scan issues if both sites are currently active and reporting and is generally caused by duplicating the database from one site to another (e.g., from a production site to staging). We recommend disconnecting this site only, which will leave the matching site still connected.'=>'如果兩個網站目前都處於活動狀態並進行報告，這可能會導致重複掃描問題，通常是由於將資料庫從一個網站複製到另一個網站（例如：從正式環境網站到預備環境）所致。我們建議僅中斷此網站的連線，這將使相符的網站保持連線狀態。','Your site is currently linked to Wordfence Central under a different site URL.'=>'您的網站目前以不同的網站網址連結至 Wordfence Central。','All associated Wordfence Central connection data has been removed from the local database.'=>'所有相關聯的 Wordfence Central 連線資料已從本機資料庫移除。','Clear Local Connection Data'=>'清除本機連線資料','All associated Wordfence Central connection data has been cleared.'=>'所有相關聯的 Wordfence Central 連線資料已清除。','Successfully removed data'=>'已成功移除資料','If you use external services that may send POST requests without these headers, do not use this option, as they will be blocked.'=>'如果您使用的外部服務可能會在沒有這些標頭的情況下發送 POST 要求，請勿使用此選項，因為它們將被封鎖。','<strong>ERROR</strong>: Login failed with status code 503. Please contact the site administrator.'=>'<strong>錯誤</strong>：登入失敗，狀態碼 503。請聯絡網站管理員。','Login failed with status code 503. Please contact the site administrator.'=>'登入失敗，狀態碼 503。請聯絡網站管理員。','<strong>ERROR</strong>: Login failed with status code 403. Please contact the site administrator.'=>'<strong>錯誤</strong>：登入失敗，狀態碼 403。請聯絡網站管理員。','Login failed with status code 403. Please contact the site administrator.'=>'登入失敗，狀態碼 403。請聯絡網站管理員。','Thank you for providing your feedback on Wordfence Security'=>'感謝您提供關於 Wordfence Security 的意見反應','Submit Feedback'=>'提交意見反應','What can we do to improve Wordfence Security?'=>'我們可以做些什麼來改進 Wordfence Security？','Leave Review'=>'留下評論','Please consider leaving us a 5-star review on wordpress.org. Your review helps other members of the WordPress community find plugins that fit their needs.'=>'請考慮在 wordpress.org 上給我們留下 5 星評價。您的評論有助於 WordPress 社群的其他成員找到符合他們需求的外掛。','Are you enjoying using Wordfence Security?'=>'您喜歡使用 Wordfence Security 嗎？','It may have compatibility problems with the current version of WordPress or unknown security issues.'=>'它可能與目前的 WordPress 版本有相容性問題或存在未知的安全性問題。','Encountered bad date string for plugin "%s" in abandoned plugin check: %s'=>'在棄用外掛檢查中遇到外掛「%s」的錯誤日期字串：%s','(.user.ini not readable)'=>'(.user.ini 不可讀取)','(.user.ini not present)'=>'(.user.ini 不存在)','(not present)'=>'（不存在）','(.htaccess not readable)'=>'(.htaccess 不可讀取)','(.htaccess not present)'=>'(.htaccess 不存在)','.user.ini other auto prepend'=>'.user.ini 其他自動前置','.htaccess other auto prepend'=>'.htaccess 其他自動前置','WAF .user.ini contents'=>'網頁應用程式防火牆 .user.ini 內容','WAF .htaccess contents'=>'網頁應用程式防火牆 .htaccess 內容','%1$s Table in Database'=>'資料庫中有 %1$s 個資料表','In addition to the above list, the IPs (or CIDR ranges) in the selected preset will be ignored when determining the requesting IP via the X-Forwarded-For HTTP header.'=>'除了上述清單之外，在透過 X-Forwarded-For HTTP 標頭判斷請求 IP 時，還會忽略選定預設集中的 IP（或 CIDR 範圍）。','The selected trusted proxy preset is not valid: '=>'選定的受信任 Proxy 預設集無效：','Number of Database Tables'=>'資料庫資料表數量','Trusted Proxy Preset'=>'受信任的 Proxy 預設集','Internal error when connecting to Wordfence Central (see server error log)'=>'連線至 Wordfence Central 時發生內部錯誤（請見伺服器錯誤記錄）','Get help with Cloudflare compatibility'=>'取得 Cloudflare 相容性協助','Cloudflare appears to be blocking your site from connecting to itself.'=>'Cloudflare 似乎阻擋了您的網站連線到自身。','Update Check Error'=>'更新檢查錯誤','Acknowledge User'=>'確認使用者','We could not find that issue in the database.'=>'我們無法在資料庫中找到該問題。','Update Check Encountered Error on \'%s\''=>'「%s」的更新檢查發生錯誤','Update Check Encountered Error'=>'更新檢查發生錯誤','Wordfence cannot detect if this plugin/theme is up to date. This might be caused by a PHP compatibility issue in the plugin.'=>'Wordfence 無法偵測此外掛/佈景主題是否為最新版本。這可能是由於外掛中的 PHP 相容性問題所致。','Wordfence cannot detect if the installed plugins and themes are up to date. This might be caused by a PHP compatibility issue in one or more plugins/themes.'=>'Wordfence 無法偵測已安裝的外掛和佈景主題是否為最新版本。這可能是由於一個或多個外掛/佈景主題中的 PHP 相容性問題所致。','The update check performed during the scan encountered an error: %s'=>'掃描期間執行的更新檢查發生錯誤：%s','You must select either "Yes" or "No"'=>'您必須選擇「是」或「否」','Would you like WordPress security and vulnerability alerts sent to you via email?'=>'您想要透過電子郵件接收 WordPress 安全性和漏洞警示嗎？','The Wordfence 2FA Code can be found within the authenticator app you used when first activating two-factor authentication. You may also use one of your recovery codes.'=>'Wordfence 兩步驟驗證碼可以在您首次啟用兩步驟驗證時使用的驗證碼產生器 App 中找到。您也可以使用其中一組復原代碼。','If you cannot complete the setup process, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%s">click here for help<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'如果您無法完成設定程序，<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%s">點擊這裡尋求協助<span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>','Search All Options'=>'搜尋所有選項','<strong>ERROR</strong>: An error was encountered while trying to authenticate. Please try again.'=>'<strong>錯誤</strong>：嘗試驗證時發生錯誤。請再試一次。','Log In'=>'登入','Remember for 30 days'=>'記住 30 天','Wordfence 2FA Code'=>'Wordfence 兩步驟驗證碼','<strong>ERROR</strong>: An error was encountered while trying to send the message. Please try again.'=>'<strong>錯誤</strong>：嘗試傳送訊息時發生錯誤。請再試一次。','An error was encountered while trying to send the message. Please try again.'=>'嘗試傳送訊息時發生錯誤。請再試一次。','Message to Support'=>'給支援團隊的訊息','Skipping inaccessible directory: %s'=>'略過無法存取的目錄：%s','Below is a sample of these recent attacks:'=>'以下是近期這些攻擊的範例：','Wordfence is blocking these attacks, and we\'re sending this notice to make you aware that there is a higher volume of the attacks than usual. Additionally, the Wordfence Real-Time IP Blocklist can block known attackers\' IP addresses automatically for Premium users, including any probing requests that may not be malicious on their own. All Wordfence users can also opt to block the attacking IPs manually if desired. As always, be sure to watch your scan results and keep your plugins, themes and WordPress core version updated.'=>'Wordfence 正在封鎖這些攻擊，我們發送此通知是為了讓您知道攻擊量高於平時。此外，Wordfence 即時 IP 封鎖清單可以為進階版使用者自動封鎖已知攻擊者的 IP 位址，包括任何本身可能不具惡意的探測請求。如果需要，所有 Wordfence 使用者也可以選擇手動封鎖攻擊 IP。一如既往，請務必關注您的掃描結果並保持您的外掛、佈景主題和 WordPress 核心程式版本更新。','The Wordfence Web Application Firewall has blocked %1$d attacks over the last %2$s.'=>'Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆在過去 %2$s 內封鎖了 %1$d 次攻擊。','The Plugin "%s" has been removed from wordpress.org but is still installed on your site.'=>'外掛「%s」已從 wordpress.org 移除，但仍安裝在您的網站上。','North Macedonia, Republic of'=>'北馬其頓共和國','WAF Loaded Successfully'=>'網頁應用程式防火牆載入成功','Outdated plugin scan adjusted invalid return value in plugins_api filter for %s'=>'過時的外掛掃描調整了 %s 在 plugins_api 篩選器中的無效回傳值','Unable to output phpinfo content because it is disabled'=>'無法輸出 phpinfo 內容，因為它已被停用','Vulnerability Severity'=>'漏洞嚴重性','Show User Counts'=>'顯示使用者計數','User counts are currently disabled as the most recent attempt to count users failed to complete successfully.'=>'使用者計數目前已停用，因為最近一次統計使用者的嘗試未能成功完成。','User counts are hidden by default on sites with large numbers of users in order to improve performance.'=>'為了提高效能，在擁有大量使用者的網站上，預設會隱藏使用者計數。','Custom Capabilities / Multiple Roles'=>'自訂權限 / 多重角色','An error was detected with this site\'s configuration that is preventing a successful connection to Wordfence Central. Disconnecting from Central <a href="%s">on the Wordfence Dashboard</a> and reconnecting may resolve it. If the issue persists, please contact Wordfence support.'=>'偵測到此網站的設定發生錯誤，導致無法成功連線至 Wordfence Central。在 <a href="%s">Wordfence 控制台</a>上中斷與 Central 的連線並重新連線可能會解決此問題。如果問題持續存在，請聯絡 Wordfence 支援。','Fetching token for Wordfence Central authentication due to configuration issue.'=>'由於組態問題，正在擷取 Wordfence Central 驗證權杖。','reCAPTCHA'=>'reCAPTCHA','When enabled, the 2FA management interface embedded through the WooCommerce integration or via a shortcode will use a vertical stacked layout as opposed to horizontal columns. Adjust this setting as appropriate to match your theme. This may be overridden using the "stacked" attribute for individual shortcodes.'=>'啟用時，透過 WooCommerce 整合或短代碼嵌入的兩步驟驗證管理介面將使用垂直堆疊版面配置，而不是水平欄位。請適當調整此設定以符合您的佈景主題。這可以使用個別短代碼的「stacked」屬性來覆寫。','Use single-column layout for WooCommerce/shortcode 2FA management interface'=>'為 WooCommerce/短代碼兩步驟驗證管理介面使用單欄版面配置','When enabled, the "wordfence_2fa_management" shortcode may be used to provide access for users to manage 2FA settings on custom pages.'=>'啟用時，可以使用「wordfence_2fa_management」短代碼，讓使用者能夠在自訂頁面上管理兩步驟驗證設定。','2FA management shortcode'=>'兩步驟驗證管理短代碼','When enabled, a Wordfence 2FA tab will be added to the WooCommerce account menu which will provide access for users to manage 2FA settings outside of the WordPress admin area. Testing the WooCommerce account interface after enabling this feature is recommended to ensure theme compatibility.'=>'啟用時，將在 WooCommerce 帳號選單中新增 Wordfence 2FA 分頁，讓使用者能夠在 WordPress 管理區域之外管理兩步驟驗證設定。建議在啟用此功能後測試 WooCommerce 帳號介面，以確保佈景主題相容性。','Show Wordfence 2FA menu on WooCommerce Account page'=>'在 WooCommerce 帳號頁面上顯示 Wordfence 2FA 選單','WooCommerce integration'=>'WooCommerce 整合','WooCommerce & Custom Integrations'=>'WooCommerce 與自訂整合','If disabled, XML-RPC requests that attempt authentication will be rejected, whether the user has 2FA enabled or not.'=>'如果停用，嘗試驗證的 XML-RPC 請求將被拒絕，無論使用者是否啟用兩步驟驗證。','You do not have permission to manage 2FA settings for your account.'=>'您沒有權限管理您帳號的兩步驟驗證設定。','Permission Denied'=>'權限被拒絕','Two-Factor Authentication, or 2FA, significantly improves login security for your account. Wordfence 2FA works with a number of TOTP-based apps like Google Authenticator, FreeOTP, and Authy. For a full list of tested TOTP-based apps, <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">click here</a>.'=>'兩步驟驗證（或稱 2FA）可顯著提升您帳號的登入安全性。Wordfence 2FA 適用於許多 TOTP 應用程式，例如 Google Authenticator、FreeOTP 和 Authy。如需經過測試的 TOTP 應用程式完整清單，<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">請點擊這裡</a>。','Proceed'=>'繼續','Make Optional'=>'設為選用','Not Recommended'=>'不建議','2FA Relative URL (optional)'=>'兩步驟驗證相對網址（選用）','2FA Role'=>'兩步驟驗證角色','Send an email to users with the selected role to notify them of the grace period for enabling 2FA. Select the desired role and optionally specify the URL to be sent in the email to setup 2FA. If left blank, the URL defaults to the standard wordpress login and Wordfence’s Two-Factor Authentication plugin page. For example, if using WooCommerce, input the relative URL of the account page.'=>'傳送電子郵件給所選角色的使用者，通知他們啟用兩步驟驗證的寬限期。選擇所需的角色，並選擇性指定要在電子郵件中傳送的兩步驟驗證設定網址。如果留空，網址預設為標準 WordPress 登入和 Wordfence 的兩步驟驗證外掛頁面。例如：如果使用 WooCommerce，請輸入帳號頁面的相對網址。','2FA Notifications'=>'兩步驟驗證通知','In order to use 2FA with the WooCommerce customer role, you must either enable the "WooCommerce integration" option or use the "wordfence_2fa_management" shortcode to provide customers with access to the 2FA management interface. The default interface is only available through WordPress admin pages which are not accessible to users in the customer role.'=>'為了讓 WooCommerce 客戶角色使用兩步驟驗證，您必須啟用「WooCommerce 整合」選項，或使用「wordfence_2fa_management」短代碼，讓客戶能夠存取兩步驟驗證管理介面。預設介面僅可透過 WordPress 管理頁面存取，而客戶角色的使用者無法存取這些頁面。','Requiring 2FA for customers is not recommended as some customers may experience difficulties setting up or using two-factor authentication. Instead, using the "Optional" mode for users with the customer role is recommended which will allow customers to enable 2FA, but will not require them to do so.'=>'不建議要求客戶使用兩步驟驗證，因為有些客戶可能會在設定或使用兩步驟驗證時遇到困難。相反地，建議為具有客戶角色的使用者使用「選用」模式，這將允許客戶啟用兩步驟驗證，但不會強制要求他們這樣做。','Wordfence 2FA'=>'Wordfence 兩步驟驗證','<html><body><p>You do not currently have two-factor authentication active on your account, which will be required beginning %s.</p><p><a href="%s">Configure 2FA</a></p></body></html>'=>'<html><body><p>您的帳號目前尚未啟用兩步驟驗證，從 %s 開始將強制要求啟用。</p><p><a href="%s">設定兩步驟驗證</a></p></body></html>','The specified URL is invalid.'=>'指定的網址無效。','Are you sure you want to delete the selected Wordfence data? If you reactivate Wordfence later, deleted settings and history cannot be recovered.'=>'確定要刪除選定的 Wordfence 資料嗎？如果您稍後重新啟用 Wordfence，已刪除的設定和記錄將無法復原。','Delete Wordfence Data?'=>'刪除 Wordfence 資料？','The Wordfence firewall is still optimized. You should remove the firewall\'s extended protection before deleting to avoid PHP errors if some firewall files cannot be removed, or if PHP\'s "auto_prepend_file" setting is cached.'=>'Wordfence 防火牆仍處於最佳化狀態。您應該在刪除前移除防火牆的延伸保護，以避免在某些防火牆檔案無法移除或 PHP 的「auto_prepend_file」設定被快取時發生 PHP 錯誤。','Extended Protection Still Enabled'=>'延伸保護仍啟用中','Deactivate and Delete Data'=>'停用並刪除資料','Deactivate Wordfence'=>'停用 Wordfence','Invalid option specified'=>'指定了無效的選項','Delete Login Security tables and 2FA codes, but keep Wordfence tables and data'=>'刪除登入安全資料表和兩步驟驗證碼，但保留 Wordfence 資料表和資料','Delete Wordfence tables and data, but keep Login Security tables and 2FA codes'=>'刪除 Wordfence 資料表和資料，但保留登入安全資料表和兩步驟驗證碼','Keep all Wordfence tables and data'=>'保留所有 Wordfence 資料表和資料','Please try again. If the problem persists, please <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/help/api-key" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">contact Wordfence Support<span class="screen-reader-text">(opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'請再試一次。如果問題持續存在，請 <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/help/api-key" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">聯絡 Wordfence 支援<span class="screen-reader-text">（在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>','An error occurred while installing your license key.'=>'安裝您的授權金鑰時發生錯誤。','Congratulations! Wordfence Free is now active on your website.'=>'恭喜！Wordfence 免費版現已在您的網站上啟用。','Congratulations! Wordfence Care is now active on your website. Please note that some Care features are not enabled by default.'=>'恭喜！Wordfence Care 現已在您的網站上啟用。請注意，某些 Care 功能預設並未啟用。','Care License Installed'=>'Care 授權已安裝','Congratulations! Wordfence Response is now active on your website. Please note that some Response features are not enabled by default.'=>'恭喜！Wordfence Response 現已在您的網站上啟用。請注意，某些 Response 功能預設並未啟用。','Response License Installed'=>'Response 授權已安裝','Get a new license'=>'取得新授權','This is where future security alerts for your website will be sent. This can also be changed in Global Options.'=>'這是您網站未來的安全性警示將發送到的地方。這也可以在全域選項中更改。','Please enter a valid email address'=>'請輸入有效的電子郵件地址','Email'=>'電子郵件','Install an existing license'=>'安裝現有授權','Get Your Wordfence License'=>'取得您的 Wordfence 授權','Register with Wordfence to secure your site with the latest threat intelligence.'=>'註冊 Wordfence 以利用最新的威脅情資保護您的網站。','Install your license to finish activating Wordfence.'=>'安裝您的授權以完成啟用 Wordfence。','You must install a license to continue using Wordfence.'=>'您必須安裝授權才能繼續使用 Wordfence。','An unexpected error occurred while attempting to dismiss the notice. Please try again.'=>'嘗試關閉通知時發生未預期的錯誤。請再試一次。','You will be reminded again in 12 hours.'=>'12 小時後將再次提醒您。','Notice Dismissed'=>'通知已關閉','Remind Me Later'=>'稍後提醒我','An unexpected error occurred while attempting to configure Wordfence to delete its data on deactivation.'=>'嘗試設定 Wordfence 在停用時刪除其資料時發生未預期的錯誤。','You are about to deactivate Wordfence. Would you like to delete its data or keep it in place?'=>'您即將停用 Wordfence。您要刪除其資料還是保留？','Delete all Wordfence tables and data'=>'刪除所有 Wordfence 資料表和資料','This could be caused by a database problem. You may need to repair your "wfconfig" database table or fix your database user\'s privileges if they have changed recently, or you may need to reinstall Wordfence. Please <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">contact Wordfence support<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'這可能是由資料庫問題引起的。您可能需要修復您的「wfconfig」資料庫資料表，或者如果您的資料庫使用者權限最近有變更，請修正權限，或者您可能需要重新安裝 Wordfence。請 <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">聯絡 Wordfence 支援<span class="screen-reader-text"> （','Wordfence\'s license key is missing.'=>'Wordfence 的授權金鑰遺失。','An unknown error occurred.'=>'發生未知錯誤。','Install Wordfence'=>'安裝 Wordfence','An error occurred while retrieving your license information from the Wordfence servers. Please ensure that your server can reach www.wordfence.com on port 443.'=>'從 Wordfence 伺服器擷取您的授權資訊時發生錯誤。請確保您的伺服器可以透過連接埠 443 連線至 www.wordfence.com。','The link you used to access this page has expired, has already been used, or is otherwise invalid.'=>'您用來存取此頁面的連結已過期、已被使用或無效。','Too many installation requests have been made from your IP address. Please try again later.'=>'您的 IP 位址發出了太多安裝請求。請稍後再試。','Wordfence is already installed on this site. If you need to replace the current license, you may do so by visiting the "All Options" page of the Wordfence menu.'=>'Wordfence 已安裝在此網站上。如果您需要更換目前的授權，請前往 Wordfence 選單的「所有選項」頁面進行操作。','If this option is disabled, Wordfence can look up countries for visitor IP addresses using a local database, but cannot look up regions or cities'=>'如果停用此選項，Wordfence 可以使用本機資料庫查詢訪客 IP 位址的國家/地區，但無法查詢區域或城市','Scan Stage Failed'=>'掃描階段失敗','Wordfence will make up to %d attempts to resume each failed scan stage. This scan may recover if one of these attempts is successful.'=>'Wordfence 最多將嘗試 %d 次恢復每個失敗的掃描階段。如果其中一次嘗試成功，此掃描可能會恢復。','Wordfence will make one attempt to resume each failed scan stage. This scan may recover if this attempt is successful.'=>'Wordfence 將嘗試一次恢復每個失敗的掃描階段。如果此嘗試成功，此掃描可能會恢復。','Attempting to resume scan stage (%d attempt(s) remaining)...'=>'正在嘗試恢復掃描階段（剩餘 %d 次嘗試）...','Cached result for scan start test: %s'=>'掃描啟動測試的快取結果：%s','To protect your site from this vulnerability, the safest option is to deactivate and completely remove "%s" until a patched version is available. <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Get more information.<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'為了保護您的網站免受此漏洞影響，最安全的選擇是停用並完全移除「%s」，直到有修補版本可用為止。<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">取得更多資訊。<span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>','The Plugin "%s" has a security vulnerability.'=>'外掛「%s」有安全性漏洞。','Invalid number of scan resume attempts specified: %d'=>'指定的掃描恢復嘗試次數無效：%d','This page shows information that can be used for troubleshooting conflicts, configuration issues, or compatibility with other plugins, themes, or a host\'s environment. Failing tests are not always a sign of something that you need to fix, but can help the Wordfence team when troubleshooting a problem. (<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More <span class="screen-reader-text">opens in new tab</span></a>)'=>'此頁面顯示可用於排解衝突、組態問題或與其他外掛、佈景主題或主機環境的相容性問題的資訊。測試失敗並不總是表示您需要修復某些東西，但在排解問題時可以幫助 Wordfence 團隊。（<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">進一步了解 <span class="screen-reader-text">在新分頁中開啟</span></a>）','Maximum number of attempts to resume each scan stage'=>'恢復每個掃描階段的最大嘗試次數','Look up visitor IP locations via Wordfence servers'=>'透過 Wordfence 伺服器查詢訪客 IP 位置','This option requires cURL. (This may have no effect on some old PHP or cURL versions.)'=>'此選項需要 cURL。（這在某些舊的 PHP 或 cURL 版本上可能無效。）','Use only IPv4 to start scans'=>'僅使用 IPv4 啟動掃描','UA/Hostname/Referrer/IP Range not allowed'=>'UA/主機名稱/參照連結網址/IP 範圍不允許','Automatic updates enabled'=>'自動更新已啟用','Automatic updates disabled'=>'自動更新已停用','Disables automatic updates'=>'停用自動更新','Cron is enabled'=>'排程工作已啟用','Cron is disabled'=>'排程工作已停用','This diagnostic requires cURL'=>'此診斷需要 cURL','This diagnostic is unavailable as cURL appears to be supported, but was not used by WordPress for this request'=>'此診斷無法使用，因為 cURL 似乎受支援，但 WordPress 此請求未使用它','This likely indicates that the server either does not support IPv6 or does not have an IPv6 address assigned or associated with the domain. Original error message: %s'=>'這可能表示伺服器不支援 IPv6，或者沒有指派 IPv6 位址或與網域關聯。原始錯誤訊息：%s','IPv6 DNS resolution failed'=>'IPv6 DNS 解析失敗','When enabled, the last login timestamp will be displayed for each user on the WP Users page. When used in conjunction with reCAPTCHA, the most recent score will also be displayed for each user.'=>'啟用時，WP 使用者頁面上的每個使用者都會顯示上次登入的時間戳記。當與 reCAPTCHA 結合使用時，也會顯示每個使用者最近的評分。','Show last login column on WP Users page'=>'在 WP 使用者頁面上顯示上次登入欄位','Allowlisted IP addresses that bypass 2FA and reCAPTCHA'=>'允許略過兩步驟驗證和 reCAPTCHA 的 IP 位址','Login Security: Allowlisted IP addresses that bypass 2FA and reCAPTCHA'=>'登入安全性：允許略過兩步驟驗證和 reCAPTCHA 的 IP 位址','Ignoring invalid scan file child: %s'=>'忽略無效的掃描檔案子項：%s','Ignoring invalid base scan file: %s'=>'忽略無效的基礎掃描檔案：%s','Ignoring invalid expected scan file: %s'=>'忽略無效的預期掃描檔案：%s','Ignoring invalid scan path: %s'=>'忽略無效的掃描路徑：%s','This was a premium license key, but it is no longer valid, so premium features are disabled. You can either remove the invalid key and continue using Wordfence\'s free features, or enter a new premium key to upgrade. If you have questions, contact <a href="mailto:billing@wordfence.com">billing@wordfence.com</a>.'=>'這是一個進階版授權金鑰，但已失效，因此進階功能已停用。您可以移除無效的金鑰並繼續使用 Wordfence 的免費功能，或輸入新的進階版金鑰進行升級。如有疑問，請聯絡 <a href="mailto:billing@wordfence.com">billing@wordfence.com</a>。','Remove Invalid License'=>'移除無效授權','Premium License Deactivated'=>'進階版授權已停用','Unable to read file contents'=>'無法讀取檔案內容','Empty file path provided'=>'提供的檔案路徑為空','This link has expired. Refresh the scan results page and try again.'=>'此連結已過期。請重新整理掃描結果頁面並再試一次。','Edit Wordfence Options'=>'編輯 Wordfence 選項','The site admin can change this option.'=>'網站管理員可以變更此選項。','Application Passwords'=>'應用程式密碼','Wordfence Firewall &amp; Care License Enabled'=>'Wordfence 防火牆和 Care 授權已啟用','Wordfence Firewall &amp; Response License Enabled'=>'Wordfence 防火牆和 Response 授權已啟用','Sign up for Wordfence Care and we’ll take care of it. Our security experts will clean your site, resolve the infection, and perform a security audit. Get hands-on support with any security issue including help installing, configuring and optimizing Wordfence.'=>'註冊 Wordfence Care，我們將為您處理。我們的安全專家將清理您的網站、解決感染問題並執行安全稽核。獲得針對任何安全問題的實際支援，包括協助安裝、組態和最佳化 Wordfence。','Need help with a security issue?'=>'需要協助解決安全性問題嗎？','Learn More About Wordfence Response'=>'進一步了解 Wordfence Response','Learn More About Wordfence Care'=>'進一步了解 Wordfence Care','Sign up for Wordfence Care today and get expert help with any security issue. Wordfence Care is for business owners who put a premium on their time. With Wordfence Care, we take care of it, so that you can focus on your customers. Check out Wordfence Response for mission-critical WordPress websites.'=>'立即註冊 Wordfence Care，獲得任何安全問題的專家協助。Wordfence Care 適用於重視時間的企業主。有了 Wordfence Care，我們將為您處理，讓您可以專注於您的客戶。查看適用於關鍵任務 WordPress 網站的 Wordfence Response。','Wordfence Scan &amp; Care License Enabled'=>'Wordfence 掃描和 Care 授權已啟用','Wordfence Scan &amp; Response License Enabled'=>'Wordfence 掃描和 Response 授權已啟用','We have updated our policies. To continue using Wordfence, you will need to read and agree to the Wordfence License Terms and Conditions, the Services Subscription Agreement, and Terms of Service, and read and acknowledge the Wordfence Privacy Policy by clicking Review.'=>'我們已更新我們的政策。若要繼續使用 Wordfence，您需要閱讀並同意 Wordfence 授權條款與細則、服務訂閱協議和服務條款，並透過點擊「檢閱」來閱讀並確認 Wordfence 隱私權政策。','We have updated our policies. To continue using Wordfence, you will need to read and agree to the <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/license-terms-and-conditions/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Wordfence License Terms and Conditions<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>, the <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/services-subscription-agreement" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Services Subscription Agreement<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>, and <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/terms-of-service/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Terms of Service<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>, and read and acknowledge the <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/privacy-policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Wordfence Privacy Policy<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>.'=>'我們已更新我們的政策。若要繼續使用 Wordfence，您需要閱讀並同意 <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/license-terms-and-conditions/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Wordfence 授權條款與細則<span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>、<a href="https://www.wordfence.com/services-subscription-agreement" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">服務訂閱協議<span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>和 <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/terms-of-service/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">服務條款<span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>，並閱讀並確認 <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/privacy-policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Wordfence 隱私權政策<span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>。','<p>Are you sure you want to reset this site\'s Wordfence License? This will disable Premium features and return the site to the free version of Wordfence. Your settings will still be retained when reinstalling a license.</p><p>If autorenew is enabled for the current license, the license will renew at the next expiration date. If you would like to turn renewal off or assign the license to another site, log into wordfence.com to change it.</p>'=>'<p>確定要重設此網站的 Wordfence 授權嗎？這將停用進階功能並將網站回復為 Wordfence 免費版。重新安裝授權時，您的設定仍會保留。</p><p>如果目前授權已啟用自動續訂，授權將在下一個到期日續訂。如果您想關閉續訂或將授權指派給其他網站，請登入 wordfence.com 進行變更。</p>','Confirm Reset'=>'確認重設','Click here to manage your Wordfence licenses'=>'點擊這裡管理您的 Wordfence 授權','Reset site to a free license'=>'將網站重設為免費版授權','%s License Active'=>'%s 授權有效','%s License Expired'=>'%s 授權已過期','Upgrade to Response'=>'升級至 Response','Upgrade to Care'=>'升級至 Care','Free'=>'免費版','Wordfence Free'=>'Wordfence 免費版','Wordfence Premium'=>'Wordfence 進階版','Wordfence Response'=>'Wordfence Response','Care'=>'Care','Wordfence Care'=>'Wordfence Care','Upgrade to a 24/7 1-hour response time with Wordfence Response'=>'升級至 Wordfence Response 以獲得 24/7 全天候 1 小時回應時間','Upgrade to hands-on support with Wordfence Care'=>'升級至 Wordfence Care 以獲得實際操作支援','As a Wordfence Premium customer you\'re entitled to paid support via our ticketing system. Our senior support engineers respond to Premium tickets during regular business hours (Monday to Friday, 6am to 5pm Pacific and 9am to 8pm Eastern time) and have a direct line to our QA and development teams.'=>'身為 Wordfence 進階版客戶，您有權透過我們的工單系統獲得付費支援。我們的資深支援工程師會在正常營業時間（週一至週五，太平洋時間上午 6 點至下午 5 點，東部時間上午 9 點至晚上 8 點）回應進階版工單，並且可以直接聯繫我們的品保與開發團隊。','As a Wordfence Care customer you are entitled to hands-on priority support and have access to our incident response team. Our senior support engineers and incident response team respond to requests quickly within business hours (Monday to Friday, 6am to 5pm Pacific and 9am to 8pm Eastern time) and can sign-in to your site on request to assist with complex issues.'=>'身為 Wordfence Care 客戶，您有權獲得實際操作的優先支援，並可聯繫我們的事故應變團隊。我們的資深支援工程師和事故應變團隊會在營業時間（週一至週五，太平洋時間上午 6 點至下午 5 點，東部時間上午 9 點至晚上 8 點）內快速回應請求，並可根據請求登入您的網站協助解決複雜問題。','As a Wordfence Response customer you are entitled to hands-on priority support 24 hours a day 365 days a year. Our incident response team is available out of hours to handle urgent issues and security incidents. Our customer support team is available during business hours (Monday to Friday, 6am to 5pm Pacific and 9am to 8pm Eastern time) for product assistance. Both teams can sign-in to your site to assist, on request.'=>'身為 Wordfence Response 客戶，您有權獲得全年 365 天、每天 24 小時的實際操作優先支援。我們的事故應變團隊可在非營業時間處理緊急問題和安全事件。我們的客戶支援團隊可在營業時間（週一至週五，太平洋時間上午 6 點至下午 5 點，東部時間上午 9 點至晚上 8 點）提供產品協助。兩個團隊均可根據請求登入您的網站提供協助。','Learn about Wordfence Response'=>'了解 Wordfence Response','Learn about Wordfence Care and Wordfence Response'=>'了解 Wordfence Care 和 Wordfence Response','%s Enabled'=>'%s 已啟用','Automatic uninstallation cannot be completed, but you may still be able to <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">manually uninstall extended protection<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>.'=>'無法完成自動解除安裝，但您仍可 <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">手動解除安裝延伸保護<span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>。','If you cannot complete the uninstall process, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%s">click here for help<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'如果您無法完成解除安裝程序，<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%s">點擊這裡尋求協助<span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>','If you don\'t recognize this file, please <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/wordfence" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">contact us on the WordPress support forums<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a> before proceeding.'=>'如果您不認得此檔案，請在繼續之前 <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/wordfence" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">在 WordPress 支援論壇上聯絡我們<span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>。','You can find more details on alternative setup steps, including installation on SiteGround or for multiple sites sharing a single php.ini, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%s">in our documentation<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>.'=>'您可以在 <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%s">我們的說明文件<span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a> 中找到關於替代設定步驟的更多詳細資訊，包括在 SiteGround 上安裝或針對共用單一 php.ini 的多個網站進行安裝。','The Web Application Firewall is currently in Learning Mode. <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'網頁應用程式防火牆目前處於學習模式。<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">進一步了解<span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>','You can log in to <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">wordfence.com<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a> to accept the updated terms and privacy policy for all of your license keys at once.'=>'您可以登入 <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">wordfence.com<span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>，一次為您所有的授權金鑰接受更新後的條款和隱私權政策。','For most sites, we recommend allowing access from the United States, where Google and other benign crawlers are generally located. Many well-known crawlers also have locations in Europe, so be careful when blocking other countries, especially if you have not seen significant attacks from them.'=>'對於大多數網站，我們建議允許來自美國的存取，因為 Google 和其他良性檢索器通常位於該處。許多知名的檢索器在歐洲也有據點，因此在封鎖其他國家/地區時請務必小心，特別是如果您沒有發現來自這些國家/地區的重大攻擊。','U.S. Blocked'=>'美國已封鎖','Error Saving Block'=>'儲存封鎖時發生錯誤','Allow a grace period for this user prior to requiring Wordfence 2FA'=>'在要求 Wordfence 兩步驟驗證之前，允許此使用者有寬限期','2FA Grace Period'=>'兩步驟驗證寬限期','View users'=>'檢視使用者','When enabled, reCAPTCHA and 2FA prompt support will be added to WooCommerce login and registration forms in addition to the default WordPress forms. Testing WooCommerce forms after enabling this feature is recommended to ensure plugin compatibility.'=>'啟用時，reCAPTCHA 和兩步驟驗證提示支援除了預設的 WordPress 表單外，還會新增到 WooCommerce 登入和註冊表單。建議在啟用此功能後測試 WooCommerce 表單，以確保外掛相容性。','Page '=>'頁面 ','N/A'=>'不適用','Page %d is out of range'=>'頁面 %d 超出範圍','No users found in the %s state for the %s role'=>'在 %s 狀態下找不到 %s 角色的使用者','2FA is not required for the %s role'=>'%s 角色不需要兩步驟驗證','This page only shows users and roles on the main site of this network'=>'此頁面僅顯示此多站網路主網站上的使用者和角色','Send Anyway'=>'無論如何都要傳送','Notify'=>'通知','For roles that require 2FA, users will have this many days to set up 2FA. Failure to set up 2FA during this period will result in the user losing account access. This grace period will apply to new users from the time of account creation. For existing users, this grace period will apply relative to the time at which the requirement is implemented. This grace period will not automatically apply to admins and must be manually enabled for each admin user.'=>'對於需要兩步驟驗證的角色，使用者將有這麼多天來設定兩步驟驗證。未在此期間內設定兩步驟驗證將導致使用者失去帳號存取權。此寬限期將適用於從帳號建立時起的新使用者。對於現有使用者，此寬限期將相對於實施要求的時間適用。此寬限期不會自動適用於網站管理員，必須為每個網站管理員使用者手動啟用。','Setting the grace period to 0 will prevent users in roles where 2FA is required, including newly created users, from logging in if they have not already enabled two-factor authentication.'=>'將寬限期設為 0 將阻止需要兩步驟驗證的角色中的使用者（包括新建立的使用者）登入，如果他們尚未啟用兩步驟驗證。','2FA Roles'=>'兩步驟驗證角色','An error was encountered while trying to disable NTP. Please try again.'=>'嘗試停用 NTP 時發生錯誤。請再試一次。','Error Disabling NTP'=>'停用 NTP 時發生錯誤','An error was encountered while trying to reset the NTP state. Please try again.'=>'嘗試重設 NTP 狀態時發生錯誤。請再試一次。','Error Resetting NTP'=>'重設 NTP 時發生錯誤','NTP will be automatically disabled after 1 more attempt.'=>'NTP 將在再嘗試 1 次後自動停用。','NTP will be automatically disabled after %d more attempts.'=>'NTP 將在再嘗試 %d 次後自動停用。','NTP updates are currently failing.'=>'NTP 更新目前失敗。','NTP is currently <strong>enabled</strong>.'=>'NTP 目前已 <strong>啟用</strong>。','Reset'=>'重設','NTP was manually disabled.'=>'NTP 已手動停用。','NTP is currently disabled as %d subsequent attempts have failed.'=>'NTP 目前已停用，因為已連續 %d 次嘗試失敗。','The constant WORDFENCE_LS_DISABLE_NTP is defined which disables NTP entirely. Remove this constant or set it to a falsy value to enable NTP.'=>'已定義常數 WORDFENCE_LS_DISABLE_NTP，這完全停用了 NTP。移除此常數或將其設為 false 值以啟用 NTP。','NTP is a protocol that allows for remote time synchronization. Wordfence Login Security uses this protocol to ensure that it has the most accurate time which is necessary for TOTP-based two-factor authentication.'=>'NTP 是一種允許遠端時間同步的通訊協定。Wordfence 登入安全使用此通訊協定來確保擁有最準確的時間，這對於基於 TOTP 的兩步驟驗證是必要的。','Note: This feature requires a free site key and secret for the <a href="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/about/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google reCAPTCHA v3 Service</a>. To set up new reCAPTCHA keys, log into your Google account and go to the <a href="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">reCAPTCHA admin page</a>.'=>'注意：此功能需要 <a href="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/about/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google reCAPTCHA v3 服務</a>的免費網站金鑰和秘密金鑰。若要設定新的 reCAPTCHA 金鑰，請登入您的 Google 帳號並前往 <a href="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">reCAPTCHA 管理頁面</a>。','Two-factor authentication will be required for user <strong>%s</strong> beginning <strong>%s</strong>.'=>'使用者 <strong>%s</strong> 將於 <strong>%s</strong> 開始被要求使用兩步驟驗證。','Two-factor authentication will be required for your account beginning <strong>%s</strong>'=>'您的帳號將於 <strong>%s</strong> 開始被要求使用兩步驟驗證','An unexpected error occurred while attempting to revoke the grace period.'=>'嘗試撤銷寬限期時發生未預期的錯誤。','Revoke Grace Period'=>'撤銷寬限期','Unable to Revoke Grace Period'=>'無法撤銷寬限期','An unexpected error occurred while attempting to reset the grace period.'=>'嘗試重設寬限期時發生未預期的錯誤。','An unexpected error occurred while attempting to activate the grace period.'=>'嘗試啟用寬限期時發生未預期的錯誤。','Reset Grace Period'=>'重設寬限期','Activate Grace Period'=>'啟用寬限期','days'=>'天','Grace Period Override'=>'寬限期覆寫','Unable to Reset Grace Period'=>'無法重設寬限期','Unable to Activate Grace Period'=>'無法啟用寬限期','Users without 2FA active (%s)'=>'未啟用兩步驟驗證的使用者（%s）','Grace Period'=>'寬限期','<strong>LOGIN BLOCKED</strong>: 2FA is required to be active on your account. Please contact the site administrator.'=>'<strong>登入被封鎖</strong>：您的帳號必須啟用兩步驟驗證。請聯絡網站管理員。','Two-factor authentication must be activated for this account prior to %s.'=>'此帳號必須在 %s 之前啟用兩步驟驗證。','Two-factor authentication must be activated for your account prior to %s to avoid losing access.'=>'您的帳號必須在 %s 之前啟用兩步驟驗證，以免失去存取權。','Two-factor authentication is required for this account, but has not been configured.'=>'此帳號需要兩步驟驗證，但尚未設定。','Two-factor authentication is required for your account, but has not been configured.'=>'您的帳號需要兩步驟驗證，但尚未設定。','Manage Settings'=>'管理設定','WooCommerce appears to be installed, but the Wordfence Login Security WooCommerce integration is not currently enabled. Without this feature, WooCommerce forms will not support all functionality provided by Wordfence Login Security, including CAPTCHA for the login page and user registration.'=>'WooCommerce 似乎已安裝，但 Wordfence 登入安全 WooCommerce 整合目前未啟用。沒有此功能，WooCommerce 表單將不支援 Wordfence 登入安全提供的所有功能，包括登入頁面和使用者註冊的 CAPTCHA。','Locked Out<small class="wfls-sub-status">(Grace Period Exceeded)</small>'=>'已鎖定 <small class="wfls-sub-status">（超過寬限期）</small>','Locked Out<small class="wfls-sub-status">(Grace Period Disabled)</small>'=>'已鎖定 <small class="wfls-sub-status">（寬限期已停用）</small>','Inactive<small class="wfls-sub-status">(Grace Period)</small>'=>'未啟用 <small class="wfls-sub-status">（寬限期）</small>','Unable to dismiss notice'=>'無法關閉通知','Failed to reset grace period'=>'重設寬限期失敗','Invalid grace period override'=>'無效的寬限期覆寫','Invalid user specified'=>'指定的使用者無效','All users with the selected role already have two-factor authentication activated or have been locked out.'=>'所選角色的所有使用者都已啟用兩步驟驗證或已被鎖定。','No users currently exist with the selected role.'=>'目前沒有所選角色的使用者。','More than %d users exist for the selected role. This notification is not designed to handle large groups of users. In such instances, using a different solution for notifying users of upcoming 2FA requirements is recommended.'=>'所選角色有超過 %d 位使用者。此通知並非設計用於處理大量使用者。在這種情況下，建議使用其他解決方案來通知使用者即將到來的兩步驟驗證需求。','You do not have permission to dismiss this notice.'=>'您沒有權限關閉此通知。','You do not have permission to disable NTP.'=>'您沒有權限停用 NTP。','You do not have permission to reset the NTP failure count.'=>'您沒有權限重設 NTP 失敗計數。','You do not have permission to revoke the 2FA grace period.'=>'您沒有權限撤銷兩步驟驗證寬限期。','You do not have permission to reset the 2FA grace period.'=>'您沒有權限重設兩步驟驗證寬限期。','Enable %d scan option.'=>'啟用 %d 個掃描選項。','Re-enable %d firewall rule.'=>'重新啟用 %d 條防火牆規則。','Regex compilation failed for signature %d'=>'簽章 %d 的 Regex 編譯失敗','<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">進一步了解<span class="screen-reader-text"> （','If you cannot complete the setup process, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%s">click here for help<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>.'=>'如果您無法完成設定程序，<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%s">點擊這裡尋求協助<span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>。','Wordfence country blocking is currently set to block the United States. We recommend allowing access from the United States for Google and other benign crawlers, unless you choose to only block the login page.'=>'Wordfence 國家/地區封鎖目前組態為封鎖美國。除非您選擇僅封鎖登入頁面，否則我們建議允許來自美國的存取，以便 Google 和其他良性檢索器運作。','<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Get more information.<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">取得更多資訊。<span class="screen-reader-text"> （','<a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">%1$s<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'<a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">%1$s<span class="screen-reader-text"> （','Click here to learn more: <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Documentation<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'點擊這裡進一步了解：<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">說明文件<span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>',' (%d of %d attempts remaining)'=>' （剩餘 %d / %d 次嘗試）','(settings)'=>'（設定）','(failures exceeded limit)'=>'（失敗次數超過限制）','(WORDFENCE_LS_DISABLE_NTP)'=>'（WORDFENCE_LS_DISABLE_NTP）','Disabled '=>'已停用 ','NTP Status'=>'NTP 狀態','Checking <code>display_errors</code><br><em> (<a href="http://php.net/manual/en/errorfunc.configuration.php#ini.display-errors" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Should be disabled on production servers<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>)</em>'=>'正在檢查 <code>display_errors</code><br><em> （<a href="http://php.net/manual/en/errorfunc.configuration.php#ini.display-errors" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">應在正式環境伺服器上停用<span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>）</em>','PHP version >= PHP %s<br><em> (<a href="https://wordpress.org/about/requirements/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WordPress requirements</a>)</em> <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wfhelp"><span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'PHP 版本 >= PHP %s<br><em> （<a href="https://wordpress.org/about/requirements/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WordPress 需求</a>）</em> <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wfhelp"><span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>','Click here to learn more: <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Documentation<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'點擊這裡進一步了解：<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">說明文件<span class="screen-reader-text"> （','<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wf-help-link">Learn more<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> about Whois Lookup</span><span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wf-help-link">進一步了解<span class="wf-hidden-xs">關於 Whois 查詢</span><span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>',' (host setting <a href="%s" class="wfhelp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>)'=>' （主機設定 <a href="%s" class="wfhelp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>）','<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wf-help-link">Learn more<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> about Live Traffic</span><span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wf-help-link">進一步了解<span class="wf-hidden-xs">關於即時流量</span><span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>','<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wf-help-link">Learn more<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> about importing and exporting options</span><span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wf-help-link">進一步了解<span class="wf-hidden-xs">關於匯入和匯出選項</span><span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a>','<a href="%s" target="_blank">Click here<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'<a href="%s" target="_blank">點擊這裡<span class="screen-reader-text"> （','opens in new tab'=>'在新分頁中開啟','Unknown (mixed plugin version)'=>'未知（混合外掛版本）','Active WAF storage engine'=>'作用中的網頁應用程式防火牆儲存引擎','Configured WAF storage engine (WFWAF_STORAGE_ENGINE)'=>'已組態的網頁應用程式防火牆儲存引擎（WFWAF_STORAGE_ENGINE）','The WAF storage engine is currently set to mysqli, but Wordfence is unable to use the database. The WAF will fall back to using local file system storage instead.'=>'網頁應用程式防火牆儲存引擎目前設定為 mysqli，但 Wordfence 無法使用資料庫。網頁應用程式防火牆將退回改為使用本機檔案系統儲存。','Tables missing (prefix %1$s, %2$s): %3$s'=>'資料表遺失（前置詞 %1$s，%2$s）：%3$s','We could not write to %1$s. (%2$d bytes written) You may not have permission to modify files on your WordPress server.'=>'我們無法寫入 %1$s。（已寫入 %2$d 位元組）您可能沒有權限修改 WordPress 伺服器上的檔案。','Add Additional Signatures'=>'新增額外簽章','Edit trusted proxies'=>'編輯受信任的 Proxy','Your IP with this setting:'=>'您在此設定下的 IP：','Detected IP(s):'=>'偵測到的 IP：','click here for help'=>'點擊這裡尋求協助','If you cannot complete the setup process, '=>'如果您無法完成設定程序，','Error During Setup'=>'設定期間發生錯誤','Enable country blocking by upgrading to Premium.'=>'升級至進階版以啟用國家/地區封鎖。','You are running PHP version %1$s that is not supported by Wordfence %2$s. Wordfence features will not be available until PHP has been upgraded. We recommend using PHP version 8.1, but Wordfence will run on PHP version %3$s at a minimum.'=>'您執行的 PHP 版本 %1$s 不被 Wordfence %2$s 支援。在升級 PHP 之前，將無法使用 Wordfence 功能。我們建議使用 PHP 版本 8.1，但 Wordfence 最低可在 PHP 版本 %3$s 上運作。','Go to'=>'前往','Go:'=>'前往：','Scheduled time for day %s hour %s is: %s'=>'%s %s 的排程時間是：%s','Description: %s'=>'說明：%s','The issue type is: %s'=>'問題類型為：%s','No failed logins have been recorded.'=>'沒有記錄到失敗的登入。','No successful logins have been recorded.'=>'沒有記錄到成功的登入。','Failed'=>'失敗','Successful'=>'成功','We encountered an error trying load more data.'=>'我們在嘗試載入更多資料時遇到錯誤。','Show more'=>'顯示更多','7 Days'=>'7 天','Top IPs Blocked'=>'遭封鎖 IP 排行','Total Attacks'=>'總攻擊次數','Connect This Site'=>'連線此網站','Reconnect This Site'=>'重新連線此網站','No notifications received'=>'未收到通知','Top Countries by Number of Attacks - Last 7 Days'=>'攻擊次數最多的國家/地區排行 - 過去 7 天','Date'=>'日期','License renews in 1 day'=>'授權將於 1 天後續訂','License renews in %d days'=>'授權將於 %d 天後續訂','License renews tomorrow'=>'授權將於明天續訂','License renews today'=>'授權將於今天續訂','Live Updates Paused &mdash; Click inside window to resume'=>'即時更新已暫停 &mdash; 點擊視窗內部以恢復','Wordfence Live Activity:'=>'Wordfence 即時活動：','Wordfence activity for %1$s on %2$s'=>'%1$s 在 %2$s 的 Wordfence 活動','Blocking IP %1$s. %2$s'=>'封鎖 IP %1$s。%2$s','UA/Referrer/IP Range not allowed'=>'UA/參照連結網址/IP 範圍不允許','getHits got invalid hitType: %s'=>'getHits 收到無效的 hitType：%s','Invalid log type to wfLog: %s'=>'wfLog 的無效記錄類型：%s','Scan Engine Error: %s'=>'掃描引擎錯誤：%s','Scan terminated with error: %s'=>'掃描因錯誤而終止：%s','Initiating quick scan'=>'正在啟動快速掃描','Deferring scheduled scan by %s'=>'將排程掃描延遲 %s','Contacting Wordfence to initiate scan'=>'正在聯絡 Wordfence 以啟動掃描','Previous scan terminated with an error. See below.'=>'上次掃描因錯誤而終止。請見下方。','Scan can\'t continue - stored data not found after a fork. Got type: %s'=>'掃描無法繼續 - 分叉後找不到儲存的資料。取得類型：%s','Got a true deserialized value back from \'wfsd_engine\' with type: %s'=>'從 \'wfsd_engine\' 取得 true 反序列化值，類型為：%s','Setting up scanRunning and starting scan'=>'正在設定 scanRunning 並開始掃描','Setting up error handling environment'=>'正在設定錯誤處理環境','Requesting max memory'=>'請求最大記憶體','Using low resource scanning'=>'使用低資源掃描','There is already a scan running.'=>'已有掃描正在執行中。','Checking if scan is already running'=>'正在檢查掃描是否已在執行中','Wordfence could not start a scan because the cron key does not match the saved key. Saved: %1$s Sent: %2$s Current unexploded: %3$s'=>'Wordfence 無法開始掃描，因為 cron 金鑰與儲存的金鑰不符。已儲存：%1$s 已傳送：%2$s 目前未展開：%3$s','Checking saved cronkey against cronkey param'=>'正在對照 cronkey 參數檢查已儲存的 cronkey','Wordfence could not find a saved cron key to start the scan so assuming it started and exiting.'=>'Wordfence 找不到已儲存的 cron 金鑰來啟動掃描，因此假設它已啟動並結束。','The key used to start a scan expired. The value is: %1$s and split is: %2$s and time is: %3$d'=>'用於啟動掃描的金鑰已過期。值為：%1$s，分割為：%2$s，時間為：%3$d','Wordfence scan script accessed directly, or WF did not receive a cronkey.'=>'Wordfence 掃描指令碼被直接存取，或者 Wordfence 未收到 cron 金鑰。','Fetching stored cronkey for comparison.'=>'正在擷取已儲存的 cron 金鑰進行比較。','Verifying start request signature.'=>'正在驗證啟動要求簽章。','Scan engine received request.'=>'掃描引擎收到請求。','Cron test received and message printed'=>'收到排程工作測試並列印訊息','Looks like the Wordfence database tables have been deleted. You can fix this by de-activating and re-activating the Wordfence plugin from your Plugins menu.'=>'看起來 Wordfence 資料庫資料表已被刪除。您可以從「外掛」選單停用並重新啟用 Wordfence 外掛來修正此問題。','Could not connect to database to start scan: %s'=>'無法連線至資料庫以啟動掃描：%s','File last modified:'=>'檔案上次修改：','File Size:'=>'檔案大小：','Wordfence: File Viewer'=>'Wordfence：檔案檢視器','Mode'=>'模式','The Wordfence server\'s response did not contain the expected elements.'=>'Wordfence 伺服器的回應未包含預期的元素。','Unable to remove code execution protections applied to the .htaccess file in the uploads directory. Please check your permissions on that file.'=>'無法移除套用至 uploads 目錄中 .htaccess 檔案的程式碼執行保護。請檢查您對該檔案的權限。','Unable to save the .htaccess file needed to disable script execution in the uploads directory. Please check your permissions on that directory.'=>'無法儲存 uploads 目錄中停用指令碼執行所需的 .htaccess 檔案。請檢查您對該目錄的權限。','Error finishing writing value for %1$s (MySQLi error: [%2$s] %3$s)'=>'完成寫入 %1$s 的值時發生錯誤（MySQLi 錯誤：[%2$s] %3$s）','Error writing value for %1$s (MySQLi error: [%2$s] %3$s)'=>'寫入 %1$s 的值時發生錯誤（MySQLi 錯誤：[%2$s] %3$s）','Error writing value header for %s'=>'寫入 %s 的值標頭時發生錯誤','Error writing value chunk for %1$s (MySQLi error: [%2$s] %3$s)'=>'寫入 %1$s 的值區塊時發生錯誤（MySQLi 錯誤：[%2$s] %3$s）','Error reassembling value for %s'=>'重組 %s 的值時發生錯誤','wfConfig::set() got an array as second param with key: %1$s and value: %2$s'=>'wfConfig::set() 收到陣列作為第二個參數，鍵為：%1$s，值為：%2$s','The license you were using has been removed from your account. Please reach out to <a href="mailto:billing@wordfence.com">billing@wordfence.com</a> or create a Premium support case at <a href="https://support.wordfence.com/support/tickets" target="_blank">https://support.wordfence.com/support/tickets<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a> for more information. Our staff is happy to help.'=>'您使用的授權已從您的帳號移除。請聯絡 <a href="mailto:billing@wordfence.com">billing@wordfence.com</a> 或在 <a href="https://support.wordfence.com/support/tickets" target="_blank">https://support.wordfence.com/support/tickets<span class="screen-reader-text"> （在新分頁中開啟）</span></a> 建立進階版支援案件以獲取更多資訊。我們的工作人員很樂意提供協助。','&copy;&nbsp;%1$d to %2$d Wordfence &mdash; Visit <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/">Wordfence.com</a> for help, security updates and more.'=>'&copy;&nbsp;%1$d 至 %2$d Wordfence &mdash; 造訪 <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/">Wordfence.com</a> 取得說明、安全性更新等。','There are no differences between the original file and the file in the repository.'=>'原始檔案與存放庫中的檔案沒有差異。','Unknown Type'=>'未知類型','Plugin Version:'=>'外掛版本：','Plugin Name:'=>'外掛名稱：','Plugin File'=>'外掛檔案','Theme Version:'=>'佈景主題版本：','Theme Name:'=>'佈景主題名稱：','Theme File'=>'佈景主題檔案','WordPress Core File'=>'WordPress 核心程式檔案','File type:'=>'檔案類型：','Filename:'=>'檔案名稱：','The two panels below show a before and after view of a file on your system that has been modified. The left panel shows the original file before modification. The right panel shows your version of the file that has been modified. Use this view to determine if a file has been modified by an attacker or if this is a change that you or another trusted person made. If you are happy with the modifications you see here, then you should choose to ignore this file the next time Wordfence scans your system.'=>'下方的兩個面板顯示您系統上已修改檔案的修改前後檢視。左側面板顯示修改前的原始檔案。右側面板顯示您已修改的檔案版本。使用此檢視來判斷檔案是否被攻擊者修改，或者這是您或其他受信任的人所做的變更。如果您滿意在這裡看到的修改，則應選擇在下次 Wordfence 掃描您的系統時忽略此檔案。','Wordfence: Viewing File Differences'=>'Wordfence：檢視檔案差異','Wordfence: All recent hits for IP address %s'=>'Wordfence：IP 位址 %s 的所有近期點閱','We were unable to remove the <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> file in the root of the WordPress installation. It\'s possible WordPress cannot remove the <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> file because of file permissions. Please verify the permissions are correct and retry the removal.'=>'我們無法移除 WordPress 安裝根目錄中的 <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> 檔案。可能是因為檔案權限，WordPress 無法移除 <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> 檔案。請驗證權限正確並重試移除。','We were unable to make changes to the %1$s file. It\'s possible WordPress cannot write to the %1$s file because of file permissions. Please verify the permissions are correct and retry the installation.'=>'我們無法變更 %1$s 檔案。可能是因為檔案權限，WordPress 無法寫入 %1$s 檔案。請驗證權限正確並重試安裝。','We were unable to make changes to the .htaccess file. It\'s possible WordPress cannot write to the .htaccess file because of file permissions, which may have been set by another security plugin, or you may have set them manually. Please verify the permissions allow the web server to write to the file, and retry the installation.'=>'我們無法變更 .htaccess 檔案。可能是因為檔案權限，WordPress 無法寫入 .htaccess 檔案，這可能是由另一個安全性外掛設定的，或者您可能手動設定了它們。請驗證權限允許網頁伺服器寫入檔案，並重試安裝。','We were unable to create the <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> file in the root of the WordPress installation. It\'s possible WordPress cannot write to the <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> file because of file permissions. Please verify the permissions are correct and retry the installation.'=>'我們無法在 WordPress 安裝根目錄中建立 <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> 檔案。可能是因為檔案權限，WordPress 無法寫入 <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> 檔案。請驗證權限正確並重試安裝。','The update was successful!'=>'更新成功！','Blocked for %1$s in file: %2$s = %3$s'=>'因檔案中的 %1$s 而封鎖：%2$s = %3$s','Blocked for %1$s in cookie: %2$s = %3$s'=>'因 Cookie 中的 %1$s 而封鎖：%2$s = %3$s','Blocked for %1$s in POST body: %2$s = %3$s'=>'因 POST 本文中的 %1$s 而封鎖：%2$s = %3$s','Blocked for %1$s in query string: %2$s = %3$s'=>'因查詢字串中的 %1$s 而封鎖：%2$s = %3$s','Blocked for %s'=>'因 %s 而封鎖','Blocked because the IP is blocklisted'=>'因 IP 在封鎖清單中而封鎖','Allowlisted via Live Traffic'=>'透過即時流量加入允許清單','Required parameters not sent.'=>'未傳送必要的參數。','There was an error writing to your .htaccess file.'=>'寫入您的 .htaccess 檔案時發生錯誤。','Updating the .htaccess did not fix the issue. You may need to add <code>Options -Indexes</code> to your httpd.conf if using Apache, or find documentation on how to disable directory listing for your web server.'=>'更新 .htaccess 並未解決問題。如果是使用 Apache，您可能需要將 <code>Options -Indexes</code> 新增到您的 httpd.conf，或尋找關於如何為您的網頁伺服器停用目錄瀏覽的說明文件。','Wordfence could not find your .htaccess file.'=>'Wordfence 找不到您的 .htaccess 檔案。','This user\'s email is the network admin email. It will need to be changed before deleting this user.'=>'此使用者的電子郵件是多站網路管理員電子郵件。刪除此使用者之前需要先變更該電子郵件。','We could not find that user in the database.'=>'我們無法在資料庫中找到該使用者。','Wordfence activity in the past %s'=>'過去 %s 的 Wordfence 活動','Test email failed to send'=>'測試電子郵件傳送失敗','Test email sent successfully'=>'測試電子郵件已成功傳送','The IP you provided must be in dotted quad notation or use ranges with square brackets. e.g. 10.11.12.13 or 10.11.12.[1-50]'=>'您提供的 IP 必須使用點分四段記法或使用方括號表示範圍。例如：10.11.12.13 或 10.11.12.[1-50]','There was an error deleting the file.'=>'刪除檔案時發生錯誤。','The file <code>%s</code> was deleted successfully.'=>'檔案 <code>%s</code> 已成功刪除。','Return to scan results'=>'返回掃描結果','There was an error restoring the file.'=>'還原檔案時發生錯誤。','The file <code>%s</code> was restored successfully.'=>'檔案 <code>%s</code> 已成功還原。','If you want to reenable Wordfence Live Traffic, you need to deactivate %1$s and then go to the Wordfence options page and reenable Live Traffic there. Wordfence does work with %1$s, however Live Traffic will be disabled and the Wordfence firewall will also count less hits per visitor because of the %1$s caching function. All other functions should work correctly.'=>'如果您想重新啟用 Wordfence 即時流量，您需要停用 %1$s，然後前往 Wordfence 選項頁面並在那裡重新啟用即時流量。Wordfence 確實可與 %1$s 搭配使用，但即時流量將被停用，且由於 %1$s 快取功能，Wordfence 防火牆計算的每個訪客點閱數也會減少。所有其他功能應能正常運作。','The Wordfence Live Traffic feature has been disabled because you have %s active which is not compatible with Wordfence Live Traffic.'=>'Wordfence 即時流量功能已停用，因為您啟用了 %s，該外掛與 Wordfence 即時流量不相容。','An error occured when fetching the WAF configuration from the database.'=>'從資料庫擷取網頁應用程式防火牆組態時發生錯誤。','We were unable to write to %s which the WAF uses for storage. Please update permissions on the parent directory so the web server can write to it.'=>'我們無法寫入網頁應用程式防火牆用於儲存的 %s。請更新上層目錄的權限，以便網頁伺服器可以寫入。','<a href="%s">Click here</a> to rebuild the configuration file.'=>'<a href="%s">點擊這裡</a>以重建組態檔案。','Malware URLs'=>'惡意軟體網址','JavaScript Errors'=>'JavaScript 錯誤','Notifications'=>'通知','You have %d new Wordfence notification.'=>'您有 %d 則新的 Wordfence 通知。','No thanks.'=>'不用了，謝謝。','Yes, enable auto-update.'=>'是的，啟用自動更新。','Do you want Wordfence to stay up-to-date automatically?'=>'您希望 Wordfence 自動保持在最新狀態嗎？','to manually update it.'=>'手動更新。','visit the options page'=>'造訪選項頁面','or'=>'或','Click here to use the recommended setting'=>'點擊這裡使用建議設定','Your \'How does Wordfence get IPs\' setting is misconfigured.'=>'您的「Wordfence 如何取得 IP」設定有誤。','This site is currently using the Cloudflare "CF-Connecting-IP" HTTP header, which should only be used when the site is behind Cloudflare.'=>'此網站目前使用 Cloudflare "CF-Connecting-IP" HTTP 標頭，這應該只在網站位於 Cloudflare 後方時使用。','This site is currently using the X-Real-IP HTTP header, which should only be used when the site is behind a front-end proxy that outputs this header.'=>'此網站目前使用 X-Real-IP HTTP 標頭，這應該只在網站位於輸出此標頭的前端 Proxy 後方時使用。','This site is currently using the X-Forwarded-For HTTP header, which should only be used when the site is behind a front-end proxy that outputs this header.'=>'此網站目前使用 X-Forwarded-For HTTP 標頭，這應該只在網站位於輸出此標頭的前端 Proxy 後方時使用。','This site is currently using PHP\'s built in REMOTE_ADDR.'=>'此網站目前使用 PHP 內建的 REMOTE_ADDR。','It is not currently in extended protection mode but was configured to use an older version of PHP and may have become deactivated when PHP was updated. You may perform the configuration update automatically by <a href="%1$s">clicking here</a> or use the "Optimize the Wordfence Firewall" button on the Firewall Options page. <a class="wfhelp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%2$s"><span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'它目前未處於延伸保護模式，但已組態為使用較舊版本的 PHP，並可能在 PHP 更新時停用。您可以 <a href="%1$s">點擊這裡</a> 自動執行組態更新，或使用防火牆選項頁面上的「最佳化 Wordfence 防火牆」按鈕。<a class="wfhelp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%2$s"><span class="screen-reader-text"> （','It is currently configured to use an older version of PHP and may become deactivated if PHP is updated. You may perform the configuration update automatically by <a href="%1$s">clicking here</a>. <a class="wfhelp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%2$s"><span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'它目前組態為使用較舊版本的 PHP，如果 PHP 更新可能會停用。您可以 <a href="%1$s">點擊這裡</a> 自動執行組態更新。<a class="wfhelp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%2$s"><span class="screen-reader-text"> （','The configuration files are corrupt or inaccessible by the web server, which is preventing the WAF from functioning. Please verify the web server has permission to access the configuration files. You may also try to rebuild the configuration file by <a href="%1$s">clicking here</a>. It will automatically resume normal operation when it is fixed. <a class="wfhelp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%2$s"><span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'組態檔案損毀或網頁伺服器無法存取，這導致網頁應用程式防火牆無法運作。請驗證網頁伺服器是否有權限存取組態檔案。您也可以嘗試 <a href="%1$s">點擊這裡</a> 重建組態檔案。修復後將自動恢復正常運作。<a class="wfhelp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%2$s"><span class="screen-reader-text"> （','Wordfence generated an error on activation. The output we received during activation was:'=>'Wordfence 在啟用時產生錯誤。我們在啟用期間收到的輸出為：','locked out from logging in'=>'被鎖定無法登入','blocked for %s'=>'因 %s 而封鎖','blocked by the Wordfence Security Network'=>'被 Wordfence Security Network 封鎖','blocked by real-time IP blocklist'=>'被即時 IP 封鎖清單封鎖','blocked by firewall for %s'=>'因 %s 被防火牆封鎖','blocked by firewall'=>'被防火牆封鎖','Your test email was sent to the requested email address. The result we received from the WordPress wp_mail() function was: %s<br /><br />A \'True\' result means WordPress thinks the mail was sent without errors. A \'False\' result means that WordPress encountered an error sending your mail. Note that it\'s possible to get a \'True\' response with an error elsewhere in your mail system that may cause emails to not be delivered.'=>'您的測試電子郵件已傳送到要求的電子郵件地址。我們從 WordPress wp_mail() 函式收到的結果是：%s<br /><br />「True」結果表示 WordPress 認為郵件已無誤傳送。「False」結果表示 WordPress 在傳送郵件時遇到錯誤。請注意，即使得到「True」回應，郵件系統中的其他地方也可能發生錯誤，導致電子郵件無法送達。','Your rules have been updated successfully. You are currently using the free version of Wordfence. Upgrade to Wordfence premium to have your rules updated automatically as new threats emerge. <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/wafUpdateRules1/wordfence-signup/">Click here to purchase a premium license</a>. <em>Note: Your rules will still update every 30 days as a free user.</em>'=>'您的規則已成功更新。您目前使用的是 Wordfence 免費版。升級至 Wordfence 進階版，即可在新威脅出現時自動更新規則。<a href="https://www.wordfence.com/wafUpdateRules1/wordfence-signup/">點擊這裡購買進階版授權</a>。<em>注意：身為免費版使用者，您的規則仍會每 30 天更新一次。</em>','Your rules have been updated successfully.'=>'您的規則已成功更新。','Your Wordfence activity log was sent to %s'=>'您的 Wordfence 活動記錄已傳送到 %s','Your .htaccess has been updated successfully. Please verify your site is functioning normally.'=>'您的 .htaccess 已成功更新。請驗證您的網站是否運作正常。','You have unsaved changes to your options. If you leave this page, those changes will be lost.'=>'您有未儲存的選項變更。如果您離開此頁面，這些變更將會遺失。','You forgot to include a reason you\'re blocking this IP range. We ask you to include this for your own record keeping.'=>'您忘記包含封鎖此 IP 範圍的原因。我們要求您包含此內容以供您自己記錄。','You are using an Nginx web server and using a FastCGI processor like PHP5-FPM. You will need to manually modify your php.ini to disable <em>display_error</em>'=>'您正在使用 Nginx 網頁伺服器並使用 FastCGI 處理器（如 PHP5-FPM）。您需要手動修改您的 php.ini 以停用 <em>display_error</em>','You are using an Nginx web server and using a FastCGI processor like PHP5-FPM. You will need to manually delete or hide those files.'=>'您正在使用 Nginx 網頁伺服器並使用 FastCGI 處理器（如 PHP5-FPM）。您需要手動刪除或隱藏這些檔案。','You are using Nginx as your web server. You\'ll need to disable autoindexing in your nginx.conf. See the <a target=\'_blank\'  rel=\'noopener noreferrer\' href=\'https://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_autoindex_module.html\'>Nginx docs for more info</a> on how to do this.'=>'您正在使用 Nginx 作為網頁伺服器。您需要在 nginx.conf 中停用自動索引。請參閱 <a target=\'_blank\'  rel=\'noopener noreferrer\' href=\'https://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_autoindex_module.html\'>Nginx 說明文件</a> 以獲取更多資訊。','Wordfence is working...'=>'Wordfence 正在運作...','Wordfence Firewall blocked a background request to WordPress for the URL %s. If this occurred as a result of an intentional action, you may consider allowlisting the request to allow it in the future.'=>'Wordfence 防火牆封鎖了對 WordPress 網址 %s 的背景要求。如果這是因故意操作而發生，您可以考慮將該要求加入允許清單，以便將來允許該要求。','We encountered a problem'=>'我們遇到了一個問題','We can\'t modify your .htaccess file for you because: %s'=>'我們無法為您修改 .htaccess 檔案，因為：%s','We are about to change your <em>.htaccess</em> file. Please make a backup of this file before proceeding.'=>'我們即將變更您的 <em>.htaccess</em> 檔案。請在繼續之前備份此檔案。','WHOIS LOOKUP'=>'WHOIS 查詢','User ID'=>'使用者 ID','Use one of these %s codes to log in if you lose access to your authenticator device. Codes are 16 characters long, plus optional spaces. Each one may be used only once.'=>'如果您失去驗證碼產生器裝置的存取權，請使用這些 %s 代碼之一登入。代碼長度為 16 個字元，加上選用空格。每個代碼只能使用一次。','Use one of these %s codes to log in if you are unable to access your phone. Codes are 16 characters long, plus optional spaces. Each one may be used only once.'=>'如果您無法存取手機，請使用這些 %s 代碼之一登入。代碼長度為 16 個字元，加上選用空格。每個代碼只能使用一次。','Unable to automatically hide file'=>'無法自動隱藏檔案','Type: %s'=>'類型：%s','Two Factor Status'=>'兩步驟驗證狀態','Throttled'=>'已節流','This will be shown only once. Keep these codes somewhere safe.'=>'這只會顯示一次。請將這些代碼保存在安全的地方。','There was an error while sending the email.'=>'傳送電子郵件時發生錯誤。','The request has been allowlisted. Please try it again.'=>'要求已加入允許清單。請再試一次。','The option %s was successfully removed.'=>'選項 %s 已成功移除。','The file %s was successfully restored.'=>'檔案 %s 已成功還原。','The file %s was successfully hidden from public view.'=>'檔案 %s 已成功從公開檢視中隱藏。','The file %s was successfully deleted.'=>'檔案 %s 已成功刪除。','The admin user %s was successfully deleted.'=>'管理員使用者 %s 已成功刪除。','The Full Path disclosure issue has been fixed'=>'完整路徑洩露問題已修復','The \'How does Wordfence get IPs\' option was successfully updated to the recommended value.'=>'「Wordfence 如何取得 IP」選項已成功更新為建議值。','Test Email Sent'=>'測試電子郵件已傳送','Successfully revoked admin'=>'已成功撤銷管理員','Successfully deleted admin'=>'已成功刪除管理員','Success updating option'=>'更新選項成功','Success restoring file'=>'還原檔案成功','Success removing option'=>'移除選項成功','Success deleting file'=>'刪除檔案成功','Specify an IP range, Hostname or Browser pattern'=>'指定 IP 範圍、主機名稱或瀏覽器模式','Specify a valid hostname'=>'指定有效的主機名稱','Specify a valid IP range'=>'指定有效的 IP 範圍','Sorry, but no data for that IP or domain was found.'=>'抱歉，找不到該 IP 或網域的資料。','Send'=>'傳送','Security Event'=>'安全性事件','Scan the code below with your authenticator app to add this account. Some authenticator apps also allow you to type in the text version instead.'=>'使用您的驗證器應用程式掃描下方代碼以新增此帳號。某些驗證器應用程式也允許您輸入文字版本。','Scan Complete.'=>'掃描完成。','Rules Updated'=>'規則已更新','Rule Update Failed'=>'規則更新失敗','Registered Users'=>'註冊使用者','Referer'=>'參照連結網址','Redirected by Country Blocking bypass URL'=>'被國家/地區封鎖略過網址重新導向','Redirected'=>'已重新導向','Recent Activity'=>'近期活動','Please specify either an IP address range, Hostname or a web browser pattern to match.'=>'請指定要比對的 IP 位址範圍、主機名稱或網頁瀏覽器模式。','Please specify a valid IP address range in the form of "1.2.3.4 - 1.2.3.5" without quotes. Make sure the dash between the IP addresses in a normal dash (a minus sign on your keyboard) and not another character that looks like a dash.'=>'請指定有效的 IP 位址範圍，格式為「1.2.3.4 - 1.2.3.5」(不含引號)。請確保 IP 位址之間的破折號是一般破折號 (鍵盤上的減號)，而不是其他看起來像破折號的字元。','Please specify a reason'=>'請指定原因','Please make a backup of this file before proceeding. If you need to restore this backup file, you can copy it to the following path from your site\'s root:'=>'請在繼續之前備份此檔案。如果您需要還原此備份檔案，可以將其從您網站的根目錄複製到以下路徑：','Please include your support ticket number or forum username.'=>'請附上您的支援工單號碼或論壇使用者名稱。','Please enter a valid email address.'=>'請輸入有效的電子郵件地址。','Paid Members Only'=>'僅限付費會員','Pages Not Found'=>'找不到頁面','OK'=>'確定','Note: Status will update when changes are saved'=>'注意：儲存變更後狀態將會更新','No rules were updated. Your website has reached the maximum number of rule update requests. Please try again later.'=>'沒有規則更新。您的網站已達到規則更新請求的上限。請稍後再試。','No rules were updated. Please verify your website can reach the Wordfence servers.'=>'沒有規則更新。請驗證您的網站是否可以連線至 Wordfence 伺服器。','No rules were updated. Please verify you have permissions to write to the /wp-content/wflogs directory.'=>'沒有規則更新。請驗證您是否有權寫入 /wp-content/wflogs 目錄。','No new issues have been found.'=>'未發現新問題。','No issues have been ignored.'=>'沒有被忽略的問題。','No activity to report yet. Please complete your first scan.'=>'尚無活動可報告。請完成您的第一次掃描。','Next Update Check: %s'=>'下次更新檢查：%s','Logins and Logouts'=>'登入和登出','Logins'=>'登入','Logged In'=>'已登入','Locked out from logging in'=>'被鎖定無法登入','Locked Out'=>'已鎖定','Learn more about repairing modified files.'=>'進一步了解修復已修改檔案的資訊。','Last Updated: %s'=>'上次更新：%s','Key:'=>'金鑰：','Humans'=>'真人','HTTP Response Code'=>'HTTP 回應碼','Google Crawlers'=>'Google 檢索器','Google Bot'=>'Google Bot','Firewall Response'=>'防火牆回應','Filter Traffic'=>'篩選流量','File restored OK'=>'檔案還原成功','File hidden successfully'=>'檔案已成功隱藏','Failed Login: Valid Username'=>'登入失敗：有效的使用者名稱','Failed Login: Invalid Username'=>'登入失敗：無效的使用者名稱','Failed Login'=>'登入失敗','Error Saving Options'=>'儲存選項時發生錯誤','Error Saving Option'=>'儲存選項時發生錯誤','Error Restoring Defaults'=>'還原預設值時發生錯誤','Error Enabling All Options Page'=>'啟用所有選項頁面時發生錯誤','Error'=>'錯誤','Enter the email address you would like to send the Wordfence activity log to. Note that the activity log may contain thousands of lines of data. This log is usually only sent to a member of the Wordfence support team. It also contains your PHP configuration from the phpinfo() function for diagnostic data.'=>'輸入您想要傳送 Wordfence 活動記錄的電子郵件地址。請注意，活動記錄可能包含數千行資料。此記錄通常只傳送給 Wordfence 支援團隊成員。它還包含來自 phpinfo() 函式的 PHP 設定以供診斷資料使用。','Email Wordfence Activity Log'=>'以電子郵件傳送 Wordfence 活動記錄','Email Diagnostic Report'=>'以電子郵件傳送診斷報告','Each line of 16 letters and numbers is a single recovery code, with optional spaces for readability. When typing your password, enter "wf" followed by the entire code like "mypassword wf1234 5678 90AB CDEF". If your site shows a separate prompt for entering a code after entering only your username and password, enter only the code like "1234 5678 90AB CDEF". Your recovery codes are:'=>'每行 16 個字母和數字為單一復原代碼，並帶有選用空格以提高可讀性。輸入密碼時，請輸入「wf」，後面接完整代碼，例如「mypassword wf1234 5678 90AB CDEF」。如果您的網站在僅輸入使用者名稱和密碼後顯示單獨的代碼輸入提示，請僅輸入代碼，例如「1234 5678 90AB CDEF」。您的復原代碼為：','Download Backup File'=>'下載備份檔案','Don\'t ask again'=>'不再詢問','Directory listing has been disabled on your server.'=>'目錄瀏覽已在您的伺服器上停用。','Directory Listing Disabled'=>'目錄瀏覽已停用','Diagnostic report has been sent successfully.'=>'診斷報告已成功傳送。','Crawlers'=>'檢索器','Click to fix .htaccess'=>'點擊修復 .htaccess','Click here to download a backup copy of your .htaccess file now'=>'點擊這裡立即下載您的 .htaccess 檔案備份複本','Click here to download a backup copy of this file now'=>'點擊這裡立即下載此檔案的備份複本','Cellphone Sign-in activated for user.'=>'使用者已啟用手機登入。','Cellphone Sign-In Recovery Codes'=>'手機登入復原代碼','Blocked by the Wordfence Web Application Firewall'=>'被 Wordfence Web 應用程式防火牆封鎖','Blocked by the Wordfence Security Network'=>'被 Wordfence Security Network 封鎖','Blocked by the Wordfence Application Firewall and plugin settings'=>'被 Wordfence 應用程式防火牆和外掛設定封鎖','Blocked by Wordfence plugin settings'=>'被 Wordfence 外掛設定封鎖','Blocked by Wordfence'=>'被 Wordfence 封鎖','Blocked WAF'=>'被 WAF 封鎖','Blocked By Firewall'=>'被防火牆封鎖','Block This Network'=>'封鎖此網路','Background Request Blocked'=>'背景請求被封鎖','Authentication Code'=>'驗證碼','Are you sure you want to allowlist this action?'=>'確定要將此動作加入允許清單嗎？','An error occurred when adding the request to the allowlist.'=>'將請求加入允許清單時發生錯誤。','An error occurred'=>'發生錯誤','All capabilties of admin user %s were successfully revoked.'=>'管理員使用者 %s 的所有權限已成功撤銷。','All Hits'=>'所有點閱','Add code to .htaccess'=>'將程式碼新增至 .htaccess','Add action to allowlist'=>'將動作新增至允許清單','Activity Log Sent'=>'活動記錄已傳送','404 Not Found'=>'404 找不到','.htaccess change'=>'.htaccess 變更','.htaccess Updated'=>'.htaccess 已更新','%s is not valid hostname'=>'%s 不是有效的主機名稱','%s in query string: %s'=>'%s 在查詢字串中：%s','%s in file: %s'=>'%s 在檔案中：%s','%s in cookie: %s'=>'%s 在 cookie 中：%s','%s in POST body: %s'=>'%s 在 POST 本文中：%s','${totalIPs} addresses in this network'=>'此網路中有 ${totalIPs} 個位址','File does not exist.'=>'檔案不存在。','We could not get the contents of the original file to do a comparison.'=>'我們無法取得原始檔案的內容進行比較。','Unknown file size.'=>'未知檔案大小。','Greater than 2 Gigs'=>'大於 2 GB','We could not open the requested file for reading. The error was: %s'=>'我們無法開啟請求的檔案進行讀取。錯誤為：%s','File contains illegal characters.'=>'檔案包含非法字元。','Invalid file requested. (Relative paths not allowed)'=>'請求的檔案無效。(不允許相對路徑)','File access blocked. (WORDFENCE_DISABLE_FILE_VIEWER is true)'=>'檔案存取被封鎖。(WORDFENCE_DISABLE_FILE_VIEWER 為 true)','An invalid IP address was specified.'=>'指定的 IP 位址無效。','Bad security token. It may have been more than 12 hours since you reloaded the page you came from. Try reloading the page you came from. If that doesn\'t work, please sign out and sign-in again.'=>'安全性憑證錯誤。您重新載入來源頁面後可能已超過 12 小時。請嘗試重新載入來源頁面。如果無效，請登出並重新登入。','Unknown dashboard data set.'=>'未知的控制台資料集。','Run a Scan'=>'執行掃描','Page contains %d malware URL: '=>'頁面包含 %d 個惡意軟體網址： ','Ajax request received to start scan.'=>'收到 Ajax 請求以啟動掃描。','An invalid file was specified for repair.'=>'指定修復的檔案無效。','We could not get the original file to do a repair.'=>'我們無法取得原始檔案進行修復。','Modifying the .htaccess file did not resolve the issue, so the original .htaccess file was restored. You can fix this manually by setting <code>display_errors</code> to <code>Off</code> in your php.ini if your site is on a VPS or dedicated server that you control.'=>'修改 .htaccess 檔案並未解決問題，因此還原了原始的 .htaccess 檔案。如果您的網站位於您控制的 VPS 或專用伺服器上，您可以透過在 php.ini 中將 <code>display_errors</code> 設定為 <code>Off</code> 來手動修正此問題。','Could not remove the option %1$s. The error was: %2$s'=>'無法移除選項 %1$s。錯誤為：%2$s','Could not remove the option because that issue does not appear to be a database related issue.'=>'無法移除選項，因為該問題似乎不是資料庫相關問題。','Could not remove the option because we could not find that issue.'=>'無法移除選項，因為我們找不到該問題。','Could not delete file %1$s. The error was: %2$s'=>'無法刪除檔案 %1$s。錯誤為：%2$s','Invalid email address given.'=>'提供的電子郵件地址無效。','more than %s'=>'超過 %s','A request was received to stop the previous scan.'=>'收到停止上次掃描的請求。','Scan stop request received.'=>'收到停止掃描請求。','An invalid status was specified when trying to update that issue.'=>'嘗試更新該問題時指定了無效的狀態。','An invalid operation was called.'=>'呼叫了無效的操作。','The IP address you\'re trying to block belongs to Google. Your options are currently set to not block these crawlers. Change this in Wordfence options if you want to manually block Google.'=>'您嘗試封鎖的 IP 位址屬於 Google。您的選項目前設定為不封鎖這些檢索器。如果您想手動封鎖 Google，請在 Wordfence 選項中變更此設定。','The IP address %s is in a range of IP addresses that Wordfence does not block. The IP range may be internal or belong to a service safe to allow access for.'=>'IP 位址 %s 位於 Wordfence 不封鎖的 IP 位址範圍內。IP 範圍可能是內部的，或者屬於安全允許存取的服務。','The IP address %s is allowlisted and can\'t be blocked. You can remove this IP from the allowlist on the Wordfence options page.'=>'IP 位址 %s 已列入允許清單，無法封鎖。您可以從 Wordfence 選項頁面的允許清單中移除此 IP。','You can\'t block your own IP address.'=>'您無法封鎖自己的 IP 位址。','Please enter a valid IP address to block.'=>'請輸入要封鎖的有效 IP 位址。','You don\'t have permission to repair .htaccess. You need to either fix the file manually using FTP or change the file permissions and ownership so that your web server has write access to repair the file.'=>'您沒有權限修復 .htaccess。您需要使用 FTP 手動修復檔案，或變更檔案權限和擁有權，以便您的網頁伺服器具有寫入權限來修復檔案。','An invalid file was requested for hiding.'=>'請求隱藏的檔案無效。','An error occurred while trying to hide the file.'=>'嘗試隱藏檔案時發生錯誤。','We could not find that issue in our database.'=>'我們無法在資料庫中找到該問題。','We found your .htaccess file but could not open it for writing: %s'=>'我們找到了您的 .htaccess 檔案，但無法開啟以進行寫入：%s','We could not find your .htaccess file to modify it.'=>'我們找不到您的 .htaccess 檔案來修改它。','LOG:'=>'記錄：','ADMIN EMAIL: %s'=>'管理員電子郵件：%s','LICENSE KEY: %s'=>'授權金鑰：%s','WORDPRESS VERSION: %s'=>'WORDPRESS 版本：%s','PLUGIN VERSION: %s'=>'外掛版本：%s','SITE: %s'=>'網站：%s','Sorry but this feature is only available for paid customers.'=>'抱歉，此功能僅供付費客戶使用。','Scheduled Wordfence scan starting at %s'=>'排程的 Wordfence 掃描開始於 %s','Next scan in %1$s (%2$s)'=>'下次掃描於 %1$s 後 (%2$s)','Next scan is starting now'=>'下次掃描現在開始','No scan is scheduled'=>'未排程掃描','That user has already been removed from the list.'=>'該使用者已從清單中移除。','We could not find the user you are trying to activate. They may have been removed from the list of Cellphone Sign-in users. Please reload this page.'=>'我們無法找到您嘗試啟用的使用者。該使用者可能已被移除於手機登入使用者名單之外。請重新載入此頁面。','The code you entered is invalid. Cellphone sign-in will not be enabled for this user until you enter a valid code.'=>'您輸入的驗證碼無效。請輸入有效驗證碼後，此用戶的手機登入功能才會啟用。','Exceeded the maximum number of login failures which is: %1$s. The last username they tried to sign in with was: \'%2$s\''=>'已超過最大登入失敗次數限制：%1$s。最後嘗試登入的用戶名為：&#x27;%2$s&#x27;','Used an invalid username \'%s\' to try to sign in'=>'嘗試使用無效的使用者名稱 &#x27;%s&#x27; 登入','A user with username "%s" who has administrator access tried to sign in to your WordPress site. Access was denied because all administrator accounts are required to have Cellphone Sign-in enabled but this account does not.'=>'使用者名稱為「%s」且具備管理員權限的用戶嘗試登入您的 WordPress 網站。由於所有管理員帳戶皆須啟用手機登入功能，而此帳戶未啟用該功能，故存取遭拒絕。','Admin Login Blocked'=>'管理員登入遭封鎖','Rescheduled missing hourly cron'=>'重新排程的遺漏每小時定時任務','Rescheduled missing daily cron'=>'重新排程的每日定時任務遺漏','Unlock email requested'=>'解鎖電子郵件請求','You have used this form too much. Please wait 3 minutes and try again.'=>'您已過度使用此表單。請等待三分鐘後再試一次。','Please wait 3 minutes and try again'=>'請稍候3分鐘後再試一次','Exceeded the maximum number of tries to recover their password which is set at: %1$s. The last username or email they entered before getting locked out was: \'%2$s\''=>'已超過密碼重設的最大嘗試次數限制，該限制設定為：%1$s。最後一次登入前被鎖定帳戶的用戶名或電子郵件為：&#x27;%2$s&#x27;','2FA Migration Error: %s'=>'雙重驗證遷移錯誤：%s','Wordfence encountered an internal error executing that request.'=>'Wordfence 在執行該請求時發生內部錯誤。','Your browser sent an invalid security token to Wordfence. Please try reloading this page or signing out and in again.'=>'您的瀏覽器向 Wordfence 發送了無效的安全憑證。請嘗試重新載入此頁面，或登出後重新登入。','You appear to have logged out or you are not an admin. Please sign-out and sign-in again.'=>'您似乎已登出，或您並非管理員。請先登出再重新登入。','Fixing wp_mail from address: %s'=>'修復 wp_mail 寄件者地址：%s','wp_mail from address is incomplete, attempting to fix'=>'wp_mail 的寄件者地址不完整，正嘗試修復','Upgrade To Premium'=>'升級至高級版','Could not understand the response we received from the Wordfence servers when applying for a free license key.'=>'在申請免費授權金鑰時，無法理解從 Wordfence 伺服器收到的回應。','`runInstall` called with previous version = %s'=>'`runInstall` 調用時，先前版本為 %s','and '=>'和 ','An update is available for '=>'現有更新可用','%d theme'=>'%d 主題','%d plugin'=>'%d 外掛程式','WordPress (v%s)'=>'WordPress (v%s)','Could not verify Wordfence License: %s'=>'無法驗證 Wordfence 授權：%s','The license you were using has been removed from your account. Please reach out to billing@wordfence.com or create a Premium support case at https://support.wordfence.com/support/tickets for more information. Our staff is happy to help.'=>'您使用的授權已從帳戶中移除。如需進一步資訊，請聯繫 billing@wordfence.com 或於 https://support.wordfence.com/support/tickets 建立高級支援案件。我們的團隊樂意為您提供協助。','The Wordfence Premium License in use on this site has been removed from your account.'=>'您帳戶中本網站使用的 Wordfence 進階版授權已遭移除。','Your Wordfence Premium License has Expired!'=>'您的 Wordfence 進階版授權已過期！','Your Premium Wordfence License expires in 1 day.'=>'您的高級版 Wordfence 授權將於 1 天後到期。','Your Premium Wordfence License expires in 2 days.'=>'您的高級版 Wordfence 授權將於 2 天後到期。','Your Premium Wordfence License expires in less than a week.'=>'您的 Wordfence 進階版授權將於一週內到期。','Your Premium Wordfence License expires in less than 2 weeks.'=>'您的 Wordfence 進階版授權將於兩週內到期。','To update your license settings please visit https://www.wordfence.com/zz9/dashboard'=>'若要更新您的授權設定，請造訪 https://www.wordfence.com/zz9/dashboard','Your Premium Wordfence License is set to auto-renew in 10 days.'=>'您的高級版 Wordfence 授權將於 10 天後自動續訂。','To ensure uninterrupted Premium Wordfence protection on your site,
please renew your license by visiting https://www.wordfence.com/ Sign in, go to your dashboard,
