ed'=>'未指定','Response'=>'回應','IP Address'=>'IP位址','Page Visited'=>'已瀏覽頁面','Location'=>'位置','Type'=>'類型','%s hits'=>'%s 次點擊','Block IP'=>'封鎖IP','Unblock range'=>'解除封鎖範圍','Unblock IP'=>'解除IP封鎖','Last hit was %s ago.'=>'最後一次擊殺是在 %s 之前。','Last Hit:'=>'最後一擊：','Firewall Response:'=>'防火牆回應：','HTTP Response Code:'=>'HTTP回應代碼：','Username:'=>'使用者名稱：','An unknown location at IP'=>'IP位址的未知位置','Group By:'=>'分組依據：','To:'=>'致：','Clear'=>'清除','From:'=>'寄件人：','Add Filter'=>'新增篩選器','Invalid response from Wordfence servers.'=>'來自 Wordfence 伺服器的無效回應。','Got error response from Wordfence servers: %s'=>'從 Wordfence 伺服器收到錯誤回應：%s','getMaxExecutionTime() returning default of: 15'=>'getMaxExecutionTime() 返回預設值：15','getMaxExecutionTime() returning half ini value: %d'=>'getMaxExecutionTime() 返回值為設定值的一半：%d','ini value of %1$d is higher than value for WORDFENCE_SCAN_MAX_INI_EXECUTION_TIME (%2$d), reducing'=>'%1$d 的 INI 值高於 WORDFENCE_SCAN_MAX_INI_EXECUTION_TIME (%2$d) 的設定值，導致執行時間縮短。','Got max_execution_time value from ini: %s'=>'從 ini 檔案取得 max_execution_time 值：%s','getMaxExecutionTime() returning config value: %s'=>'getMaxExecutionTime() 返回設定值：%s','Got value from wf config maxExecutionTime: %s'=>'從工作流設定中取得值：最大執行時間為 %s','Starting cron via proxy at URL %s'=>'透過代理伺服器在網址 %s 啟動 cron','Scan process ended after forking.'=>'掃描程序在分叉後結束。','There was an unknown error starting the scan.'=>'啟動掃描時發生未知錯誤。','There was an error starting the scan: %s.'=>'啟動掃描時發生錯誤：%s。','Starting cron with normal ajax at URL %s'=>'透過標準 AJAX 在網址 %s 啟動 cron','Test result of scan start URL fetch: %s'=>'掃描啟動網址抓取測試結果：%s','A scan is already running. Use the stop scan button if you would like to terminate the current scan.'=>'掃描程序已開始執行。若要終止當前掃描，請使用停止掃描按鈕。','Entering start scan routine'=>'進入開始掃描例程','Scan was stopped on administrator request.'=>'掃描因管理員要求而停止。','Previous scan was stopped successfully.'=>'先前掃描已成功停止。','Checking for future GeoIP support'=>'檢查未來是否支援 GeoIP','This option contains a URL that is currently listed on Wordfence\'s domain blocklist. It may indicate your site is infected with malware. The URL is: %s'=>'此選項包含一個目前列於 Wordfence 網域封鎖清單中的網址。這可能表示您的網站已遭惡意軟體感染。該網址為：%s','Option contains a suspected malware URL: %s'=>'此選項包含疑似惡意軟體網址：%s','Examining URLs found in the options we scanned for dangerous websites'=>'檢視我們掃描危險網站時，在選項中發現的網址','Scanning for suspicious site options'=>'掃描可疑網站選項','Scanning for admin users not created through WordPress'=>'掃描未透過 WordPress 建立的管理員使用者','Your site is still using this plugin, but it is not currently available on wordpress.org. Plugins can be removed from wordpress.org for various reasons. This can include benign issues like a plugin author discontinuing development or moving the plugin distribution to their own site, but some might also be due to security issues. In any case, future updates may or may not be available, so it is worth investigating the cause and deciding whether to temporarily or permanently replace or remove the plugin.'=>'您的網站仍在使用此外掛程式，但該外掛目前已不在 wordpress.org 上提供。外掛程式可能因各種原因從 wordpress.org 下架，包括開發者停止維護、將外掛分發轉移至自有網站等無害狀況，但也可能涉及安全性問題。無論何種情況，未來更新都可能無法取得，因此建議您查明原因，並決定是否暫時或永久替換或移除此外掛程式。','It has unpatched security issues and may have compatibility problems with the current version of WordPress.'=>'它存在未修補的安全漏洞，且可能與當前版本的WordPress存在相容性問題。','It was last updated %s ago.'=>'最後更新於 %s 之前。','The Plugin "%1$s" appears to be abandoned (updated %2$s).'=>'外掛程式「%1$s」似乎已被棄用（最後更新於 %2$s）。','It was last updated %1$s ago and tested up to WordPress %2$s.'=>'最後更新於 %1$s 前，並已測試至 WordPress %2$s 版本。','The Plugin "%1$s" appears to be abandoned (updated %2$s, tested to WP %3$s).'=>'外掛程式「%1$s」似乎已被棄用（最後更新於 %2$s，測試相容於 WP %3$s）。','The Theme "%1$s" needs an upgrade (%2$s -> %3$s).'=>'主題「%1$s」需要升級（%2$s → %3$s）。','You need to upgrade "%s" to the newest version to ensure you have any security fixes the developer has released.'=>'您需要將「%s」升級至最新版本，以確保您能獲得開發者發布的所有安全性修補程式。','The Plugin "%1$s" needs an upgrade (%2$s -> %3$s).'=>'外掛程式「%1$s」需要升級（%2$s → %3$s）。','WordPress version %s is now available. Please upgrade immediately to get the latest security updates from WordPress.'=>'WordPress 版本 %s 現已推出。請立即升級以取得 WordPress 的最新安全更新。','Your WordPress version is out of date'=>'您的 WordPress 版本已過時','Scanning for old themes, plugins and core files'=>'掃描舊主題、外掛程式及核心檔案','Completed checking password strength of user \'%s\''=>'已完成檢查使用者 &#x27;%s&#x27; 的密碼強度','Adding issue %s'=>'新增問題 %s','A user with \'subscriber\' access has a password that is very easy to guess. Please either change it or ask the user to change their password.'=>'具有「訂閱者」權限的使用者，其密碼極易被猜中。請立即更改密碼，或請該使用者自行修改密碼。','User "%s" with \'subscriber\' access has a very easy password.'=>'使用者「%s」擁有「訂閱者」權限，其密碼過於簡單。','A user with the a role of \'%s\' has a password that is easy to guess. Please change this password yourself or ask the user to change it.'=>'具有「%s」角色的使用者，其密碼容易被猜中。請您自行變更此密碼，或請該使用者進行修改。','User "%1$s" with "%2$s" access has an easy password.'=>'使用者「%1$s」擁有「%2$s」存取權限，其密碼過於簡單。','Checking password strength of user \'%1$s\' with ID %2$d'=>'檢查使用者 &#x27;%1$s&#x27;（ID：%2$d）的密碼強度','Could not get username for user with ID %d when checking password strength.'=>'檢查密碼強度時，無法取得 ID 為 %d 的使用者名稱。','Total of %d users left to process in password strength check.'=>'密碼強度檢查尚餘 %d 名使用者待處理。','Starting password strength check on %d user.'=>'開始對 %d 位使用者執行密碼強度檢查。','We were unable to generate the user list for your password check.'=>'我們無法為您的密碼檢查生成用戶清單。','Scanning for weak passwords'=>'掃描弱密碼','Scanned comment with %s'=>'已掃描的評論，包含 %s','Marking comment as spam for containing a phishing URL. Comment has %s'=>'因評論包含釣魚網址，標記為垃圾訊息。該評論含有 %s','Marking comment as spam for containing a malware URL. Comment has %s'=>'將評論標記為垃圾訊息，因其包含惡意軟體網址。該評論含有 %s','Scanning comment with %s'=>'掃描帶有 %s 的評論','Source IP: %s'=>'來源 IP：%s','Email: %s'=>'電子郵件：%s','Author: %s'=>'作者：%s','%s contains a suspected malware URL.'=>'%s 包含疑似惡意軟體網址。','Scanning comments with %d left to scan.'=>'掃描評論中剩餘 %d 則待掃描。','Scanning comments for URLs on a domain blocklist'=>'掃描評論中的網址，以加入網域封鎖清單','Adding issue: %1$s'=>'新增問題：%1$s','This %1$s contains a URL that is currently listed on Wordfence\'s domain blocklist. The URL is: %2$s'=>'此 %1$s 包含一個目前列於 Wordfence 網域封鎖清單中的網址。該網址為：%2$s','%1$s contains a suspected malware URL: %2$s'=>'%1$s 包含疑似惡意軟體網址：%2$s','Done examining URLs'=>'已完成網址檢查','Examining URLs found in posts we scanned for dangerous websites'=>'檢視我們掃描的貼文中發現的URL，以找出危','This post contains code that is suspicious. Please check the title of the post and confirm that the code in the title is not malicious.'=>'此貼文包含可疑程式碼。請檢查貼文標題，並確認標題中的程式碼並非惡意程式碼。','Post title contains suspicious code'=>'文章標題包含可疑程式碼','Scanning posts with %d left to scan.'=>'正在掃描文章，還有 %d 篇待掃描。','Scanning posts for URLs on a domain blocklist'=>'正在掃描文章中網域封鎖清單上的 URL','Publicly accessible quarantined file found: %s'=>'發現可公開存取的隔離檔案：%s','Testing accessibility of: %s'=>'正在測試可存取性：%s','Scanning for publicly accessible quarantined files'=>'掃描公開可存取的隔離檔案','Adding issue: %s'=>'新增問題：%s','Done file contents scan'=>'已完成檔案內容掃描','Starting scan of file contents'=>'開始掃描檔案內容','Skipping scan of file contents for URLs on a domain blocklist'=>'略過掃描網域封鎖清單中網址的檔案內容','Scanning file contents for URLs on a domain blocklist'=>'掃描檔案內容以尋找網域封鎖清單中的網址','Skipping scan of file contents for infections and vulnerabilities'=>'略過掃描檔案內容中的感染及漏洞','Scanning file contents for infections and vulnerabilities'=>'掃描檔案內容以偵測感染與漏洞','Found %d theme'=>'找到 %d 個主題','Getting theme list from WordPress'=>'正在從 WordPress 取得佈景主題清單','Found %d plugin'=>'找到 %d 個外掛程式','Getting plugin list from WordPress'=>'從 WordPress 取得外掛清單','Including files that are outside the WordPress installation in the scan.'=>'將位於 WordPress 安裝目錄外的檔案納入掃描範圍。','Checking for paths skipped due to scan settings'=>'檢查因掃描設定而略過的路徑','Wordfence could not read the content of your WordPress directory. This usually indicates your permissions are so strict that your web server can\'t read your WordPress directory.'=>'Wordfence 無法讀取您的 WordPress 目錄內容。這通常表示您的權限設定過於嚴格，導致網頁伺服器無法讀取 WordPress 目錄。','Check if your site is being Spamvertized is for paid members only'=>'檢查您的網站是否遭到垃圾廣告攻擊僅限進階版會員使用','Checking if your site is being Spamvertised'=>'檢查您的網站是否遭到垃圾廣告攻擊','Directory listing provides an attacker with the complete index of all the resources located inside of the directory. The specific risks and consequences vary depending on which files are listed and accessible, but it is recommended that you disable it unless it is needed.'=>'目錄列舉功能會向攻擊者提供該目錄內所有資源的完整索引清單。具體風險與後果取決於列舉檔案的內容及存取權限，但除非確有必要，否則建議您停用此功能。','Directory listing is enabled'=>'目錄列舉功能已啟用','Full Path Disclosure (FPD) vulnerabilities enable the attacker to see the path to the webroot/file. e.g.: /home/user/htdocs/file/. Certain vulnerabilities, such as using the load_file() (within a SQL Injection) query to view the page source, require the attacker to have the full path to the file they wish to view.'=>'完整路徑揭露 (FPD) 漏洞使攻擊者得以查看網頁根目錄/檔案的路徑，例如：/home/user/htdocs/file/。某些漏洞 (如透過 SQL 隱碼攻擊中的 load_file() 查詢檢視頁面原始碼) 要求攻擊者必須掌握欲檢視檔案的完整路徑。','Web server exposes the document root'=>'網頁伺服器揭露了文件根目錄','Checking if your server discloses the path to the document root'=>'檢查您的伺服器是否揭露文件根目錄的路徑','<a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">%1$s</a> is publicly accessible and may expose source code or sensitive information about your site. Files such as this one are commonly checked for by scanners and should be made inaccessible. Alternately, some can be removed if you are certain your site does not need them. Sites using the nginx web server may need manual configuration changes to protect such files. <a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn more<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'<a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">%1$s</a> 可公開存取，且可能會洩漏您網站的原始碼或敏感資訊。掃描器通常會檢查此類檔案，因此應將其設為無法存取。或者，如果您確定網站不需要這些檔案，也可以將其移除。使用 Nginx 網頁伺服器的網站可能需要手動變更設定，以保護此類檔案。<a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">更多資訊<span class="screen-reader-text"> (','Publicly accessible config, backup, or log file found: %s'=>'發現公開可存取的設定檔、備份檔或記錄檔：%s','Check for publicly accessible configuration files, backup files and logs'=>'檢查公開可存取的設定檔、備份檔案及記錄檔','A test request to this website was detected on a different value for this setting. IP blocking and live traffic information may not be accurate. <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Get More Information<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'系統偵測到傳送至此網站的測試請求使用了與此設定不同的值。IP 封鎖與即時流量資訊可能不準確。<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">取得更多資訊<span class="screen-reader-text"> (','\'How does Wordfence get IPs\' is misconfigured'=>'「Wordfence 如何取得 IP」設定錯誤','This site appears to be behind Cloudflare, so using the Cloudflare "CF-Connecting-IP" HTTP header will resolve to the correct IPs.'=>'此網站似乎位於 Cloudflare 背後，因此使用 Cloudflare 的「CF-Connecting-IP」HTTP 標頭將可解析至正確的 IP 位址。','This site appears to be behind a front-end proxy, so using the X-Real-IP HTTP header will resolve to the correct IPs.'=>'此網站似乎位於前端 Proxy 之後，因此使用 X-Real-IP HTTP 標頭將能解析至正確的 IP 位址。','This site appears to be behind a front-end proxy, so using the X-Forwarded-For HTTP header will resolve to the correct IPs.'=>'此網站似乎位於前端 Proxy 之後，因此使用 X-Forwarded-For HTTP 標頭將可解析至正確的 IP 位址。','For maximum security use PHP\'s built in REMOTE_ADDR.'=>'為確保最高安全性，請使用 PHP 內建的 REMOTE_ADDR。','Wordfence was unable to validate a test request to your website. This can happen if your website is behind a proxy that does not use one of the standard ways to convey the IP of the request or it is unreachable publicly. IP blocking and live traffic information may not be accurate. <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Get More Information<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'Wordfence 無法驗證傳送至你網站的測試請求。如果你的網站位於代理伺服器後方，且該伺服器未使用標準方式傳送請求的 IP，或是網站無法從外部公開存取，就可能發生此情況。IP 封鎖與即時流量資訊可能不準確。<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">取得更多資訊<span class="screen-reader-text"> (','Unable to accurately detect IPs'=>'無法準確偵測 IP 位址','Checking for the most secure way to get IPs'=>'檢查取得 IP 位址的最安全方式','The URL is: %s'=>'網址為：%s','Your site is listed on a domain blocklist.'=>'您的網站已被列入網域封鎖清單。','The multisite blog with ID %d is listed on a domain blocklist.'=>'ID 為 %d 的多站網路網站已被列入網域封鎖清單。','The URL %s is on the blocklist.'=>'網址 %s 已列入封鎖清單。','Your site is listed on the Wordfence domain blocklist.'=>'您的網站已被列入 Wordfence 網域封鎖清單。','The multisite blog with ID %d is listed on the Wordfence domain blocklist.'=>'ID 為 %d 的多站網路網站已被列入 Wordfence 網域封鎖清單。','Error checking domain blocklists: %s'=>'檢查網域封鎖清單時發生錯誤：%s','Checking if your site is on a domain blocklist is for paid members only'=>'檢查您的網站是否被列入網域封鎖清單僅限進階版會員使用','Checking if your site is on a domain blocklist'=>'檢查您的網站是否被列入網域封鎖清單','Checking if your IP is generating spam is for paid members only'=>'檢查您的 IP 是否產生垃圾訊息僅限進階版會員使用','Checking if your site IP is generating spam'=>'檢查您的網站 IP 是否正在產生垃圾訊息','Scan complete. Congratulations, no new problems found.'=>'掃描完成。恭喜，未發現新問題。','See below.'=>'請參閱下文。','Scan complete. You have %d new issue to fix.'=>'掃描完成。您有 %d 個新問題需要修復。','%d ignored issue was also detected.'=>'亦偵測到 %d 個已忽略的問題。','Quick Scan Complete. Scanned in %s.'=>'快速掃描完成。耗時 %s。','Scan Complete. Scanned %1$d files, %2$d plugins, %3$d themes, %4$d posts, %5$d comments and %6$d URLs in %7$s.'=>'掃描完成。共掃描 %1$d 個檔案、%2$d 個外掛、%3$d 個佈景主題、%4$d 篇文章、%5$d 則留言及 %6$d 個網址，耗時 %7$s。','Wordfence used %1$s of memory for scan. Server peak memory usage was: %2$s'=>'Wordfence 掃描時使用了 %1$s 的記憶體。伺服器記憶體尖峰使用量為：%2$s','Calling startScan(true)'=>'呼叫 startScan(true)','Entered fork()'=>'進入 fork()','Forking during malware scan to ensure continuity.'=>'在惡意軟體掃描期間進行分支處理，以確保作業連續性。','Aborting scan because WordPress updated from version %1$s to %2$s. The scan will be reattempted later.'=>'因 WordPress 從版本 %1$s 更新至 %2$s，故中止掃描。掃描將於稍後重新嘗試。','Scan interrupted. No problems found prior to stopping.'=>'掃描中斷。停止前未發現任何問題。','Scan interrupted. You have %d new issue to fix. See below.'=>'掃描中斷。您有 %d 個新問題需要修復。詳見下方。','Scan interrupted. Scanned %1$d files, %2$d plugins, %3$d themes, %4$d posts, %5$d comments and %6$d URLs in %7$s.'=>'掃描中斷。已掃描 %1$d 個檔案、%2$d 個外掛、%3$d 個佈景主題、%4$d 篇文章、%5$d 則留言及 %6$d 個網址，耗時 %7$s。','Scan Time Limit Exceeded'=>'已超過掃描時間限制','The scan time limit of %1$s has been exceeded and the scan will be terminated. This limit can be customized on the options page. <a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Get More Information<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'已超過 %1$s 的掃描時間限制，掃描將會終止。此限制可以在選項頁面進行自訂。<a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">取得更多資訊<span class="screen-reader-text"> (','%d issue found in most recent scan'=>'最近一次掃描中發現 %d 個問題','The Wordfence scanning servers are currently unavailable. This may be for maintenance or a temporary outage. If this still occurs in an hour, please contact support. [%s]'=>'Wordfence 掃描伺服器目前無法使用。此狀況可能是因維護作業或暫時性中斷所致。若一小時後仍發生此問題，請聯絡支援團隊。[%s]','There was an unknown error connecting to the Wordfence scanning servers.'=>'連線至 Wordfence 掃描伺服器時發生不明錯誤。','There was an error connecting to the Wordfence scanning servers: %s'=>'連線至 Wordfence 掃描伺服器時發生錯誤：%s','Calling Wordfence API v%s:'=>'呼叫 Wordfence API v%s：','We received a data structure that is not the expected array when contacting the Wordfence scanning servers and calling the \'%s\' function.'=>'在聯絡 Wordfence 掃描伺服器並呼叫「%s」函式時，我們收到非預期陣列的資料結構。','The Wordfence license you\'re using does not match this site\'s address. Premium features are disabled.'=>'您使用的 Wordfence 授權與本網站位址不符。進階功能已停用。','We received an empty data response from the Wordfence scanning servers when calling the \'%s\' function.'=>'在呼叫「%s」函式時，我們從 Wordfence 掃描伺服器收到空資料回應。','SSL is not supported by your web server and is required to use this function. Please ask your hosting provider or site admin to install cURL with openSSL to use this feature.'=>'您的網頁伺服器不支援 SSL，而此功能需要 SSL 才能使用。請聯絡您的主機供應商或網站管理員，安裝附帶 OpenSSL 的 cURL 以啟用此功能。','&copy;&nbsp;%d to %d Wordfence &mdash; Visit <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/">Wordfence.com</a> for help, security updates and more.'=>'&copy;&nbsp;%d 至 %d Wordfence &mdash; 請造訪 <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/">Wordfence.com</a> 以獲取協助、安全性更新及其他資訊。','Wordfence System Info'=>'Wordfence 系統資訊','Done URL check.'=>'網址檢查完成。','Checking %1$d URLs from %2$d sources.'=>'正在檢查來自 %2$d 個來源的 %1$d 個網址。','Done host key check.'=>'已完成主機金鑰檢查。','Checking %d host keys against Wordfence scanning servers.'=>'正在檢查 %d 個主機金鑰與 Wordfence 掃描伺服器的對應關係。','Using MySQLi directly.'=>'直接使用 MySQLi。','Gathering host keys.'=>'正在收集主機金鑰。','Wordfence Full Activity Log'=>'Wordfence 完整活動記錄','Invalid response: %s'=>'無效的回應：%s','An error occurred: %s'=>'發生錯誤：%s','The malicious URL matched'=>'惡意網址相符','Wordfence found the following new issues on "%1$s" (%2$d existing issue was also found again).'=>'Wordfence 在「%1$s」上發現以下新問題 (同時也再次發現 %2$d 個現有問題)。','Location:'=>'位置：','User:'=>'使用者：','Full Browser ID:'=>'完整瀏覽器識別碼：','Referrer:'=>'參照位址：','Normal request'=>'正常請求','URL:'=>'網址：','Seconds since last hit:'=>'自上次點擊以來的秒數：','%1$s ago -- %2$s -- %3$s in Unixtime'=>'%1$s 前 -- %2$s -- %3$s (Unix 時間戳)','The view could not be loaded.'=>'無法載入檢視。','The view %s does not exist or is not readable.'=>'檢視 %s 不存在或無法讀取。','Analyzed %1$d files containing %2$s of data so far'=>'已分析 %1$d 個檔案，目前共包含 %2$s 的資料','This file belongs to theme "%1$s" version "%2$s" and has been modified from the original distribution. It is common for site owners to modify their theme files, so if you have modified this file yourself you can safely ignore this warning. <a href="%3$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'此檔案屬於佈景主題 「%1$s」 版本 「%2$s」，且已與原始發行版本不同。網站擁有者修改其佈景主題檔案相當常見，因此如果你曾親自修改過此檔案，可以放心地忽略此警告。<a href="%3$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">了解更多<span class="screen-reader-text"> (','Modified theme file: %s'=>'修改的佈景主題檔案：%s','This file belongs to plugin "%1$s" version "%2$s" and has been modified from the file that is distributed by WordPress.org for this version. Please use the link to see how the file has changed. If you have modified this file yourself, you can safely ignore this warning. If you see a lot of changed files in a plugin that have been made by the author, then try uninstalling and reinstalling the plugin to force an upgrade. Doing this is a workaround for plugin authors who don\'t manage their code correctly. <a href="%3$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'此檔案屬於外掛 「%1$s」 版本 「%2$s」，且已與 WordPress.org 為此版本所發佈的檔案不同。請透過連結查看檔案的變更情形。如果你曾親自修改過此檔案，可以放心地忽略此警告。如果你在外掛中看見許多由作者所進行的檔案變更，請嘗試解除安裝並重新安裝此外掛以強制升級。這是針對未正確管理其程式碼的外掛作者所採用的權宜措施。<a href="%3$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">了解更多<span class="screen-reader-text"> (','Modified plugin file: %s'=>'已修改的外掛檔案：%s','This WordPress core file has been modified and differs from the original file distributed with this version of WordPress.'=>'此 WordPress 核心檔案已進行修改，與本版本 WordPress 隨附的原始檔案有所不同。','WordPress core file modified: %s'=>'WordPress 核心檔案已修改：%s','Scanning: %s'=>'掃描中：%s','Scanning: %1$s (Mem:%2$s)'=>'掃描中：%1$s (記憶體：%2$s)','Skipping file larger than max size: %s'=>'略過超過最大尺寸的檔案：%s','Calling fork() from wordfenceHash with maxExecTime: %s'=>'從 wordfenceHash 呼叫 fork()，最大執行時間為：%s','Forking during indexing: %s'=>'索引期間發生分叉：%s','%d files indexed'=>'已索引 %d 個檔案','Skipping unneeded hash: %s'=>'略過不必要的雜湊值：%s','Found .suspected file: %s'=>'發現可疑檔案：%s','This file\'s signature matches a known malware file. The title of the malware is \'%s\'. Immediately inspect this file using the \'View\' option below and consider deleting it from your server.'=>'此檔案的簽名與已知惡意軟體檔案相符。該惡意軟體名稱為「%s」。請立即透過下方「檢視」選項檢查此檔案，並考慮從伺服器中刪除它。','This file is suspected malware: %s'=>'此檔案疑似惡意軟體：%s','Invalid response from Wordfence API during check_possible_malware'=>'在 check_possible_malware 期間從 Wordfence API 收到無效回應','Analyzed %1$d files containing %2$s of data.'=>'已分析 %1$d 個檔案，包含 %2$s 資料。','Processing pending issues'=>'正在處理待解決事項','Beginning file hashing'=>'開始檔案雜湊運算','Index time: %s'=>'索引時間：%s','Wordfence file scanner detected a possible infinite loop. Exiting on file: %s'=>'Wordfence 檔案掃描器偵測到可能的無窮迴圈。將於檔案：%s 結束掃描','The core files scan will not be run because this version of WordPress is not currently indexed by Wordfence. This may be due to using a prerelease version or because the servers are still indexing a new release. If you are using an official WordPress release, this issue will automatically dismiss once the version is indexed and another scan is run.'=>'核心檔案掃描將不會執行，因為此版本的 WordPress 目前尚未被 Wordfence 索引。這可能是由於使用了預先發佈版本，或是伺服器仍在索引新版本所致。若您使用的是官方 WordPress 版本，待該版本完成索引並重新執行掃描後，此問題將自動解除。','Unknown WordPress core version: %s'=>'未知的 WordPress 核心版本：%s','Skipping unknown core file scan'=>'略過未知核心檔案掃描','Scanning for unknown files in wp-admin and wp-includes'=>'掃描 wp-admin 和 wp-includes 中的未知檔案','Skipping malware scan'=>'略過惡意軟體掃描','Scanning for known malware files'=>'掃描已知惡意軟體檔案','Skipping plugin scan'=>'略過外掛掃描','Comparing plugins against WordPress.org originals'=>'將外掛與 WordPress.org 原版進行比較','Skipping theme scan'=>'略過佈景主題掃描','Comparing open source themes against WordPress.org originals'=>'將開源佈景主題與 WordPress.org 原創主題進行比較','Skipping core scan'=>'略過核心掃描','Comparing core WordPress files against originals in repository'=>'將核心 WordPress 檔案與存放庫中的原始檔案進行比對','Core hashes data received from Wordfence servers was not valid.'=>'從 Wordfence 伺服器接收的核心雜湊資料無效。','Could not fetch core hashes from Wordfence servers.'=>'無法從 Wordfence 伺服器取得核心雜湊值。','Fetching fresh core hashes'=>'正在擷取新的核心雜湊值','Using cached core hashes'=>'使用快取的核心雜湊值','Fetching list of known core files from Wordfence'=>'從 Wordfence 取得已知核心檔案清單','Malware data received from Wordfence servers was not valid.'=>'從 Wordfence 伺服器接收到的惡意軟體資料無效。','Could not fetch malware signatures from Wordfence servers.'=>'無法從 Wordfence 伺服器取得惡意軟體簽名檔。','Fetching fresh malware prefixes'=>'正在擷取新的惡意軟體前置詞','Using cached malware prefixes'=>'使用快取的惡意軟體前置詞','Fetching list of known malware files from Wordfence'=>'從 Wordfence 取得已知惡意軟體檔案清單','Fetching core, theme and plugin file signatures from Wordfence'=>'從 Wordfence 取得核心、佈景主題及外掛檔案簽名','Need help from the WordPress security experts?'=>'需要 WordPress 安全專家的協助嗎？','Allowlisted URLs'=>'允許清單中的網址','Allowlist Entry Exists'=>'允許清單項目已存在','allowlisted'=>'已列入允許清單','Allowlisted 404 URLs'=>'允許清單中的 404 網址','Disable WordPress application passwords'=>'停用 WordPress 應用程式密碼','Allowlisted services'=>'允許清單服務','Application passwords have been disabled by Wordfence.'=>'應用程式密碼已由 Wordfence 停用。','Allowlisted hosts'=>'允許清單中的主機','Since you have High Sensitivity scanning enabled, there is a very high likelihood that your results will include false positives. If you think you have indeed been hacked, our team of security experts can help.'=>'由於您已啟用高靈敏度掃描功能，檢測結果極可能包含誤報。若您確信網站已遭駭客入侵，我們的資安專家團隊可提供協助。','Repair'=>'修復','Go To Option'=>'前往選項','Skipped Paths'=>'略過的路徑','Since you have the beta threat defense feed enabled, there is a high likelihood that your results could include false positives. If you think you have indeed been hacked, our team of security experts can help.'=>'由於您啟用了測試版 (Beta) 威脅防禦資訊提供，您的檢測結果極可能包含誤報。若您確信已遭駭客入侵，我們的資安專家團隊可提供協助。','The results of your scan may indicate that you could benefit from Wordfence Site Cleaning'=>'您的掃描結果顯示，您可能需要使用 Wordfence 網站清理服務','As a free Wordfence user, you are currently using the Community version of the Threat Defense Feed. Premium users are protected by additional firewall rules and malware signatures as well as the Wordfence real-time IP blocklist. Upgrade to Premium today to improve your protection.'=>'身為免費的 Wordfence 使用者，您目前使用的是威脅防禦資訊提供的社群版。進階版使用者則享有額外的防火牆規則、惡意軟體簽名檔，以及 Wordfence 即時 IP 封鎖清單的保護。立即升級至進階版，提升您的防護等級。','Wordfence Scan Enabled'=>'Wordfence 掃描已啟用','Enable Automatic Scans'=>'啟用自動掃描','A Wordfence scan examines all files, posts, pages, and comments on your WordPress website looking for malware, known malicious URLs, and known patterns of infections. It also does several other reputation and server checks.'=>'Wordfence 掃描會檢查您 WordPress 網站上的所有檔案、文章、頁面及留言，以偵測惡意軟體、已知惡意網址及已知感染模式。同時還會執行多項信譽評估與伺服器檢測。','Wordfence Scan Deactivated'=>'Wordfence 掃描功能已停用','Wordfence Scan &amp; Premium Enabled'=>'Wordfence 掃描與進階版功能已啟用','Changelog'=>'變更記錄','New Plugin Version'=>'新版外掛','Ignore Update'=>'忽略更新','Plugin Upgrade'=>'外掛升級','Plugin Vulnerable'=>'外掛存在漏洞','Publicly Accessible Config/Backup/Log'=>'公開可存取的設定/備份/記錄檔','Plugin Removed'=>'外掛已移除','Time Limit'=>'時間限制','Delete Option'=>'刪除選項','View Option'=>'檢視選項','Ignore Value'=>'忽略值','Option'=>'選項','0 for default. Must be %d or greater and 10-20 or higher is recommended for most servers'=>'預設值為 0。必須為 %d 或更大數值，且建議多數伺服器設定為 10-20 或更高值。','Maximum execution time for each scan stage '=>'每個掃描階段的最大執行時間 ','Memory size in megabytes'=>'記憶體容量 (單位：MB)','0 or empty means the default of %s will be used'=>'0 或留空表示將使用預設值 %s','0 or empty means unlimited issues will be sent'=>'0 或留空表示將傳送無限量的問題','Performance Options'=>'效能選項','Quarantined File'=>'隔離檔案','WAF Status'=>'WAF 狀態','Option Name'=>'選項名稱','Ignore Option'=>'忽略選項','Ignore URL'=>'忽略網址','Use Recommended Value'=>'使用建議值','Space Remaining'=>'剩餘空間','Disk Space'=>'磁碟空間','Directory Listing Enabled'=>'目錄列舉功能已啟用','Stop Ignoring'=>'停止忽略','Full Path Disclosure'=>'完整路徑揭露','Selected automatically when General Options have been customized for this website.'=>'當此網站的「一般選項」已自訂時，將自動選取。','Custom Scan'=>'自訂掃描','For site owners who think they may have been hacked. More thorough but may produce false positives.'=>'針對懷疑網站可能遭駭的網站擁有者。檢測更徹底，但可能產生誤報。','Our recommendation for all websites. Provides the best detection capability in the industry.'=>'我們對所有網站的推薦方案。提供業界頂尖的偵測能力。','Standard Scan'=>'標準掃描','For entry-level hosting plans. Provides limited detection capability with very low resource utilization.'=>'針對入門級主機方案。提供有限的偵測能力，且資源使用率極低。','Limited Scan'=>'有限掃描','Show log'=>'顯示記錄','Hide log'=>'隱藏記錄','View<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> full</span> log'=>'檢視<span class="wf-hidden-xs">完整</span>記錄','Email<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> activity</span> log'=>'電子郵件<span class="wf-hidden-xs">活動</span>記錄','Upgrade'=>'升級','Ignore Only this Title'=>'僅忽略此標題','Post'=>'文章','Ignore Until Version Changes'=>'忽略直至版本變更','Always Ignore Version'=>'永遠忽略版本','Unknown Core File'=>'未知核心檔案','Spam'=>'垃圾訊息','Server Update'=>'伺服器更新','Hide File'=>'隱藏檔案','Severity: %s'=>'嚴重程度：%s','Issue Found: %s'=>'發現問題：%s','ago'=>'前','Issue First Detected'=>'首次偵測到問題','Ignored'=>'已忽略','New'=>'新','Found '=>'發現 ','Issue Found '=>'發現問題 ','Type:'=>'類型：','Get Help'=>'尋求協助','Theme URL'=>'佈景主題網址','New Theme Version'=>'新佈景主題版本','Current Theme Version'=>'目前佈景主題版本','Theme Name'=>'佈景主題名稱','Ignore '=>'忽略 ','Theme Upgrade'=>'佈景主題升級','This is your main configuration file and cannot be deleted. It must be cleaned manually.'=>'此為您的主要設定檔，不可刪除。必須手動清理。','WordPress Configuration File'=>'WordPress 設定檔','Check if this website is being "Spamvertised"'=>'檢查此網站是否正遭受「垃圾廣告」攻擊','<em>Reputation check</em>'=>'<em>信譽檢查</em>','General Options'=>'一般選項','User & Option Audit'=>'使用者與選項稽核','Vulnerability Scan'=>'漏洞掃描','Password Strength'=>'密碼強度','Public Files'=>'公開檔案','Content Safety'=>'內容安全','Malware Scan'=>'惡意軟體掃描','File Changes'=>'檔案變更','Server State'=>'伺服器狀態','Blocklist Check'=>'封鎖清單檢查','Spam Check'=>'垃圾訊息檢查','Spamvertising Checks'=>'垃圾廣告檢查','Full Name'=>'全名','User Email'=>'使用者電子郵件','Login Name'=>'登入名稱','Ignore Only this Password'=>'僅忽略此密碼','Ignore All for User'=>'忽略此使用者的所有項目','Insecure Password'=>'不安全的密碼','Revoke Capabilities'=>'撤銷權限','Delete User'=>'刪除使用者','Unknown Administrator'=>'未知的管理員','Author'=>'作者','Manage Plugins'=>'管理外掛','Repository URL'=>'存放庫網址','Plugin URL'=>'外掛網址','Plugin has unpatched security issues.'=>'此外掛存在未修補的安全漏洞。','Last Updated'=>'最後更新','Current Plugin Version'=>'目前外掛版本','Plugin Name'=>'外掛名稱','Plugin Abandoned'=>'外掛已棄用','Multisite Blog Path'=>'多站網路網站路徑','Multisite Blog Domain'=>'多站網路網站網域','Multisite Blog ID'=>'多站網路網站 ID','Posted on'=>'發佈於','Title'=>'標題','Ignore this URL'=>'忽略此網址','Additional scan signatures (one per line)'=>'額外的掃描簽名 (每行一個)','Exclude files from scan that match these wildcard patterns (one per line)'=>'排除符合以下萬用字元模式的檔案 (每行一個)','Advanced Scan Options'=>'進階掃描選項','Delete File'=>'刪除檔案','View Differences'=>'檢視差異','View File'=>'檢視檔案','Bad URL'=>'錯誤網址','Not a core, theme, or plugin file from wordpress.org'=>'並非來自 wordpress.org 的核心、佈景主題或外掛檔案','File Type'=>'檔案類型','Filename'=>'檔案名稱','Ignore Until File Changes'=>'忽略直至檔案變更','Always Ignore'=>'永遠忽略','Basic Scan Type Options'=>'基本掃描類型選項','Vulnerability Status'=>'漏洞狀態','View Updates'=>'檢視更新','Mark as Fixed'=>'標記為已修復','View'=>'檢視','Click here to update now'=>'點擊此處立即更新','Details'=>'詳細資料','New WordPress Version'=>'新版 WordPress','Current WordPress Version'=>'目前 WordPress 版本','Ignore'=>'忽略','Core Upgrade'=>'核心升級','Results Found'=>'搜尋結果','URLs Checked'=>'已檢查網址','Users Checked'=>'已驗證使用者','Themes &amp; Plugins'=>'佈景主題與外掛','Posts, Comments, &amp; Files'=>'文章、留言與檔案','Repair All Repairable Files'=>'修復所有可修復的檔案','Delete All Deletable Files'=>'刪除所有可刪除檔案','Ignored<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Results</span>'=>'被忽略的<span class="wf-hidden-xs">結果</span>','Results<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Found</span>'=>'<span class="wf-hidden-xs">搜尋</span>結果','We failed to send a termination request.'=>'我們未能成功傳送終止請求。','A termination request has been sent to stop any running scans.'=>'已傳送終止請求以停止所有正在執行的掃描作業。','Stop Failed'=>'停止失敗','Scan Stopping'=>'正在停止掃描','Stop Scan'=>'停止掃描','Start New Scan'=>'開始新掃描','Scan Scheduling'=>'掃描排程','The error returned was:'=>'傳回的錯誤訊息為：','Scan Failed'=>'掃描失敗','Edit'=>'編輯','Sunday'=>'星期日','Saturday'=>'星期六','Friday'=>'星期五','Thursday'=>'星期四','Wednesday'=>'星期三','Tuesday'=>'星期二','Monday'=>'星期一','PM'=>'下午','AM'=>'上午','Start time'=>'開始時間','Use preferred start time'=>'使用偏好的開始時間','Odd Days & Weekends'=>'奇數日與週末','Weekends'=>'週末','Weekdays'=>'平日','Every Other Day'=>'每隔一天','Twice Daily'=>'每日兩次','Once Daily'=>'每日一次','Manually schedule scans'=>'手動排程掃描','Let Wordfence choose when to scan my site (recommended)'=>'讓 Wordfence 決定何時掃描我的網站 (建議)','Agree'=>'同意','Wordfence\'s terms of service and privacy policy have changed'=>'Wordfence 的服務條款與隱私權政策已變更','Review'=>'檢閱','0 means unlimited alerts will be sent.'=>'0 表示將發送無限量的警示。','Alert when someone is blocked from logging in for using a password found in a breach'=>'當有人因使用外洩密碼而被阻止登入時發出警示','Alert me with scan results of this severity level or greater:'=>'當掃描結果達到此嚴重程度或更高時通知我：','Low'=>'低','Medium'=>'中','High'=>'高','Critical'=>'嚴重','If you have automatic updates enabled (see above), you\'ll get an email when an update occurs.'=>'若您已啟用自動更新功能 (參見上文)，每當有更新時，您將收到一封電子郵件通知。','Email Alert Preferences'=>'電子郵件警示偏好設定','Use the Cloudflare "CF-Connecting-IP" HTTP header to get a visitor IP. Only use if you\'re using Cloudflare.'=>'使用 Cloudflare 的「CF-Connecting-IP」HTTP 標頭獲取訪客 IP。僅限使用 Cloudflare 時採用。','Let Wordfence use the most secure method to get visitor IP addresses. Prevents spoofing and works with most sites.'=>'讓 Wordfence 使用最安全的技術獲取訪客 IP 位址。防止位址偽造，並適用於大多數網站。','Display "Live Traffic" menu item'=>'顯示「即時流量」選單項目','Display "Blocking" menu item'=>'顯示「封鎖」選單項目','Display "All Options" menu item'=>'顯示「所有選項」選單項目','View Customization'=>'檢視自訂設定','Install License'=>'安裝授權','License Status:'=>'授權狀態：','Your Wordfence License'=>'您的 Wordfence 授權','Wordfence License'=>'Wordfence 授權','Note: This does not include Login Security settings and tables. An option to delete those must be selected separately on the Login Security settings page.'=>'注意：此操作不包含登入安全性設定及資料表。若需刪除這些項目，必須在登入安全性設定頁面另行勾選刪除選項。','Setting higher will reduce browser traffic but slow scan starts, live traffic &amp; status updates.'=>'設定較高值將減少瀏覽器流量，但會減緩掃描啟動、即時流量及狀態更新的速度。','Separate multiple addresses with commas'=>'以逗號分隔多個位址','Please read this article in our FAQ to make an important change that will ensure your site stability during an update.'=>'請閱讀我們常見問題集中的這篇文章，以進行一項重要變更，確保您的網站在更新期間保持穩定。','<span class="wf-red-dark">Warning:</span> You are running the LiteSpeed web server and Wordfence can\'t determine whether "noabort" is set. Please verify that the environmental variable "noabort" is set for the local site, or the server\'s global External Application Abort is set to "No Abort".'=>'<span class="wf-red-dark">警告：</span>您正在執行 LiteSpeed 網頁伺服器，而 Wordfence 無法判定「noabort」是否已設定。請確認本機網站已設定環境變數「noabort」，或伺服器的全域外部應用程式中止設定為「No Abort」。','Automatically updates Wordfence to the newest version within 24 hours of a new release.'=>'在新版發佈後的 24 小時內，自動將 Wordfence 更新至最新版本。','General Wordfence Options'=>'Wordfence 一般選項','Wordfence Protection Activated'=>'Wordfence 防護已啟用','Error during Import'=>'匯入過程中發生錯誤','We successfully imported the site options.'=>'我們已成功匯入網站選項。','Import Successful'=>'匯入成功','Error during Export'=>'匯出過程中發生錯誤','We successfully exported your site options. To import your site options on another site, copy and paste the token below into the import text box on the destination site. Keep this token secret &mdash; it is like a password. If anyone else discovers the token it will allow them to import your options excluding your license.'=>'我們已成功匯出您的網站選項。若要在其他網站匯入這些選項，請將下方權杖複製貼上至目標網站的匯入文字方塊。請嚴格保密此權杖 &mdash; 它如同密碼般重要。若他人取得此權杖，將能匯入您的選項 (但不包含授權資訊)。','Export Successful'=>'匯出成功','Import<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Wordfence</span> Options'=>'匯入<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Wordfence</span> 選項','Export<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Wordfence</span> Options'=>'匯出<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Wordfence</span> 選項','Once a month'=>'每月一次','Once a week'=>'每週一次','Once a day'=>'每日一次','Activity Report'=>'活動報告','Dashboard notifications will also be displayed for Security Alerts, Promotions, Blog Highlights, and Product Updates. These notifications can be disabled by upgrading to a premium license.'=>'控制台通知亦將顯示以下類別：安全性警示、促銷活動、部落格精選及產品更新。您可透過升級至進階版授權來停用這些通知。','Dashboard Notification Options'=>'控制台通知選項','Job'=>'工作','Run Time'=>'執行時間','Status'=>'狀態','Name'=>'名稱','Setting Name'=>'設定名稱','If you would like to sign-in to <a href="%1$s">%1$s</a> please <a href="%2$s">click here</a> now. You can change the frequency of this email or turn it on and off by visiting your <a href="%3$s">Wordfence options page</a>.'=>'若您希望登入 <a href="%1$s">%1$s</a>，請立即<a href="%2$s">點擊此處</a>。您可透過造訪 <a href="%3$s">Wordfence 選項頁面</a>，變更此電子郵件的傳送頻率或啟用/停用該功能。','<strong>This update includes security-related fixes.</strong>'=>'<strong>本次更新包含與安全性相關的修正。</strong>','This list may include WordPress core/plugin/theme updates, error logs, cache files, and other normal changes.'=>'此清單可能包含 WordPress 核心/外掛/佈景主題更新、錯誤記錄檔、快取檔案及其他正常變更。','Modified'=>'修改','Recently Modified Files'=>'最近修改的檔案','View Recent Traffic'=>'檢視近期流量','and %d additional attacks'=>'以及額外的 %d 次攻擊','No blocked attacks yet.'=>'目前尚未有任何被阻擋的攻擊。','IP / Action'=>'IP / 動作','Recently Blocked Attacks'=>'最近被阻擋的攻擊','Top 10 Failed Logins'=>'前 10 名登入失敗','Top 10 Countries Blocked'=>'前 10 名被封鎖的國家','No data currently.'=>'目前沒有資料。','Top 10 IPs Blocked'=>'前 10 名遭封鎖的 IP 位址','NOTE: You are using the free version of Wordfence and are missing out on features like real-time firewall rule and malware signature updates, country blocking, and detecting if your site IP is sending spam. <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/zz6/">Click here to upgrade to Wordfence Premium now</a>.'=>'注意：您目前使用的是 Wordfence 免費版，將無法享有即時防火牆規則與惡意軟體簽名更新、國家封鎖功能，以及偵測網站 IP 是否發送垃圾訊息等功能。<a href="https://www.wordfence.com/zz6/">立即點擊此處升級至 Wordfence 進階版</a>。','This email was sent from your website <a href="%1$s">%1$s</a> and is a summary of security related activity that Wordfence monitors for the period %2$s to %3$s.'=>'此電子郵件由您的網站 <a href="%1$s">%1$s</a> 發送，內容為 Wordfence 在 %2$s 至 %3$s 期間監控到的安全相關活動摘要。','Wordfence activity from <br><strong>%1$s</strong> to <strong>%2$s</strong>'=>'Wordfence 活動記錄：從 <br><strong>%1$s</strong> 至 <strong>%2$s</strong>','Generated in %.4f seconds'=>'產生耗時 %.4f 秒','No updates are available at this time.'=>'目前沒有可用的更新。','Update Now'=>'立即更新','A new version of the theme "%s" is available.'=>'佈景主題「%s」的新版本已可供使用。','A new version of the plugin "%s" is available.'=>'外掛「%s」的新版本已可供使用。','Plugins'=>'外掛','A new version of WordPress (v%s) is available.'=>'WordPress 的新版本 (v%s) 已可供使用。','Core'=>'核心','Updates Needed'=>'需要更新','Update Login Security Options'=>'更新登入安全性選項','No failed logins yet.'=>'目前尚未發生登入失敗的情況。','Existing User'=>'現有使用者','Login Attempts'=>'登入嘗試','Username'=>'使用者名稱','Top %d Failed Logins'=>'前 %d 次登入失敗','Update Blocked Countries'=>'更新被封鎖的國家','No requests blocked yet.'=>'目前尚未封鎖任何請求。','Total IPs Blocked'=>'總計封鎖的 IP 位址','Top %d Countries Blocked'=>'前 %d 個被封鎖的國家','Update Blocked IPs'=>'更新被封鎖的 IP 位址','No IPs blocked yet.'=>'目前尚未封鎖任何 IP 位址。','(Unknown)'=>'(未知)','Top %d IPs Blocked'=>'前 %d 個被封鎖的 IP','Collapse All'=>'收合全部','Expand All'=>'展開全部','Save<span class="wf-hidden-xs wf-hidden-sm"> Changes</span>'=>'儲存<span class="wf-hidden-xs wf-hidden-sm">變更</span>','Cancel<span class="wf-hidden-xs wf-hidden-sm"> Changes</span>'=>'取消<span class="wf-hidden-xs wf-hidden-sm">變更</span>','<span class="wf-hidden-xs">Restore </span>Defaults'=>'<span class="wf-hidden-xs">還原</span>預設值','Wordfence installation is incomplete'=>'Wordfence 安裝不完整','Error Installing License'=>'安裝授權時發生錯誤','You have successfully installed Wordfence %s'=>'您已成功安裝 Wordfence %s','Wordfence - Securing your WordPress Website'=>'Wordfence - 保護您的 WordPress 網站','Free License Installed'=>'免費版授權已安裝','Go To Dashboard'=>'前往控制台','If you don\'t have one, you can purchase one now.'=>'若您尚未擁有，現在即可購買。','Install'=>'安裝','Enter Premium Key'=>'輸入高級版金鑰','Enter your premium license key to enable real-time protection for your website.'=>'輸入您的進階版授權金鑰，為您的網站啟用即時防護功能。','Activate Premium'=>'啟用進階版','Please Complete Wordfence Installation'=>'請完成 Wordfence 安裝','Uninstallation from this site was successful! The Wordfence Firewall is still active because it is installed in another WordPress installation.'=>'從本網站的解除安裝已成功完成！Wordfence 防火牆仍處於啟用狀態，因為它安裝在另一個 WordPress 網站中。','Uninstallation was successful!'=>'解除安裝成功！','HTML tags will be stripped prior to output and line breaks will be converted into the appropriate tags.'=>'HTML 標籤將在輸出前被移除，分行符號將轉換為對應的標籤。','Prevent discovery of usernames through \'/?author=N\' scans, the oEmbed API, the WordPress REST API, and WordPress XML Sitemaps'=>'防止使用者名稱透過 \'/?author=N\' 掃描、oEmbed API、WordPress REST API 及 WordPress XML Sitemap 被發現','Prevent users registering \'admin\' username if it doesn\'t exist'=>'若使用者名稱「admin」不存在，則禁止使用者註冊該名稱','Force all members to use strong passwords'=>'強制所有成員使用強式密碼','Force admins and publishers to use strong passwords (recommended)'=>'強制管理員和發佈者使用強式密碼（建議）','Additional Options'=>'其他選項','For all users with "publish posts" capability'=>'所有具備「發佈文章」權限的使用者','For admins only'=>'僅限管理員','Hit enter to add a username'=>'按下 Enter 鍵以新增使用者名稱','This option enables all "Brute Force Protection" options, including strong password enforcement and invalid login throttling. You can modify individual options below.'=>'此選項將啟用所有「暴力密碼破解防護」功能，包括強制執行強密碼與無效登入頻率限制。您可以在下方個別調整各項選項。','Once you have downloaded the files, click Continue to complete uninstallation.'=>'下載完畢後，請點擊「繼續」以完成解除安裝程序。','We\'ve preselected your server configuration based on our tests, but if you know your web server\'s configuration, please select it now.'=>'我們已根據測試結果預先選取您的伺服器組態，但若您清楚自身網頁伺服器的設定，請立即進行選取。','Before this file can be deleted, the configuration for the <code>auto_prepend_file</code> setting needs to be removed.'=>'在刪除此檔案之前，必須先移除 <code>auto_prepend_file</code> 的組態設定。','Extended Protection Mode of the Wordfence Web Application Firewall uses the PHP ini setting called <code>auto_prepend_file</code> in order to ensure it runs before any potentially vulnerable code runs. This PHP setting currently refers to the Wordfence file at:'=>'Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆的延長保障模式採用名為 <code>auto_prepend_file</code> 的 PHP 設定，以確保其能在任何具漏洞的程式碼執行前啟動。此 PHP 設定目前指向以下路徑的 Wordfence 檔案：','Uninstall Wordfence Firewall'=>'解除安裝 Wordfence 防火牆','Once you have downloaded the files, click Continue to complete the setup.'=>'下載完畢後，請點擊「繼續」以完成設定。','Download %s'=>'下載 %s','Please download a backup of the following files before we make the necessary changes:'=>'在我們進行必要的變更之前，請先下載下列檔案的備份：','If you are using a web server not listed in the dropdown or if file permissions prevent the installer from completing successfully, you will need to perform the change manually. Click Continue below to create the required file and view manual installation instructions.'=>'若您使用的網頁伺服器未列於下拉選單中，或檔案權限導致安裝程式無法順利完成，則需要手動執行變更。請點擊下方「繼續」以建立所需檔案並查看手動安裝說明。','Part of the Firewall configuration procedure for NGINX depends on creating a <code>%1$s</code> file in the root of your WordPress installation. This file can contain sensitive information and public access to it should be restricted. We have <a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">instructions on our documentation site<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a> on what directives to put in your nginx.conf to fix this.'=>'NGINX 的防火牆組態程序的一部分需要在 WordPress 安裝根目錄下建立 <code>%1$s</code> 檔案。此檔案可能包含敏感性資訊，應限制其公開存取權限。我們的<a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">說明文件網站<span class="screen-reader-text"> (在新分頁開啟)</span></a>提供指引，說明應在 nginx.conf 檔案中加入哪些指示詞以解決此問題。','We\'ve preselected your server configuration based on our tests, but if you know your web server\'s configuration, please select it now. You can also choose "Manual Configuration" for alternate installation details.'=>'我們已根據測試結果預先選取您的伺服器組態，但若您熟悉自身網頁伺服器的設定，請立即進行選取。您亦可選取「手動組態」以輸入其他安裝細節。','If you know your web server\'s configuration, please select it from the list below.'=>'若您了解您的網頁伺服器組態，請從下方清單中選取。','Manual Configuration'=>'手動組態','Windows (IIS)'=>'Windows (IIS)','NGINX'=>'NGINX','LiteSpeed/lsapi'=>'LiteSpeed/lsapi','Apache + CGI/FastCGI'=>'Apache + CGI/FastCGI','Apache + suPHP'=>'Apache + suPHP','Apache + mod_php'=>'Apache + mod_php','If you have separate WordPress installations with Wordfence installed within a subdirectory of this site, it is recommended that you perform the Firewall installation procedure on those sites before this one.'=>'若您在此網站的子目錄中安裝了獨立的 WordPress 並啟用 Wordfence，建議先在那些網站上執行防火牆安裝程序，再進行本網站的安裝。','NOTE:'=>'注意：','Override'=>'覆寫','Include'=>'包含','You can proceed with the installation and we will include this from within our <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> file which should maintain compatibility with your site, or you can opt to override the existing PHP setting.'=>'您可以繼續進行安裝，我們將在我們的 <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> 檔案中包含此內容，這應能維持與網站的相容性；您亦可選擇覆寫現有的 PHP 設定。','To make your site as secure as possible, the Wordfence Web Application Firewall is designed to run via a PHP setting called <code>auto_prepend_file</code>, which ensures it runs before any potentially vulnerable code runs. This PHP setting is currently in use, and is including this file:'=>'為確保網站盡可能安全，Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆設計為透過名為 <code>auto_prepend_file</code> 的 PHP 設定來執行，確保其在任何可能具漏洞的程式碼執行前啟動。此 PHP 設定目前已啟用，並包含此檔案：','To make your site as secure as possible, the Wordfence Web Application Firewall is designed to run via a PHP setting called <code>auto_prepend_file</code>, which ensures it runs before any potentially vulnerable code runs.'=>'為確保網站盡可能安全，Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆設計為透過名為 <code>auto_prepend_file</code> 的 PHP 設定來執行，確保其在任何可能具漏洞的程式碼執行前先行運作。','Optimize Wordfence Firewall'=>'最佳化 Wordfence 防火牆','then'=>'接著','This feature blocks all traffic from IPs with a high volume of recent malicious activity using Wordfence\'s real-time blocklist.'=>'此功能會透過 Wordfence 的即時封鎖清單，封鎖所有來自近期惡意活動量高的 IP 位址之流量。','Premium Feature:'=>'高級版功能：','The plugin will load as a regular plugin after WordPress has been loaded, and while it can block many malicious requests, some vulnerable plugins or WordPress itself may run vulnerable code before all plugins are loaded.'=>'此外掛將在 WordPress 載入後以一般外掛的形式載入，雖然它能封鎖多數惡意要求，但某些具漏洞的外掛或 WordPress 本身，可能在所有外掛載入完成前就執行了具漏洞的程式碼。','Basic WordPress Protection:'=>'WordPress 基礎防護：','Optimize the Wordfence Firewall'=>'最佳化 Wordfence 防火牆','You are currently running the Wordfence Web Application Firewall from another WordPress installation. Please configure the firewall to run correctly on this site.'=>'您目前正在從另一個 WordPress 安裝環境執行 Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆。請將防火牆組態為在此網站上正確運行。','Existing WAF Installation Detected:'=>'偵測到現有的 WAF 安裝：','Remove Extended Protection'=>'移除延長保障','If you\'re moving to a new host or a new installation location, you may need to temporarily disable extended protection to avoid any file not found errors. Use this action to remove the configuration changes that enable extended protection mode or you can <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">remove them manually<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>.'=>'若您正在遷移至新主機或新安裝位置，可能需要暫時停用擴展保護功能，以避免發生檔案未找到的錯誤。請使用此操作移除啟用擴展保護模式的設定變更，或可<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">手動移除這些設定<span class="screen-reader-text">（在新分頁開啟）</span></a>。','All PHP requests will be processed by the firewall prior to running.'=>'所有 PHP 要求將在執行前由防火牆先行處理。','Extended Protection:'=>'延長保障：','Protection Level'=>'保護等級','Automatically enable on'=>'自動啟用於','Enabled and Protecting'=>'已啟用並保護中','In this mode, the Wordfence Web Application Firewall is functionally turned off and does not run any of its rules or analyze the request in any way.'=>'在此模式下，Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆的功能將被關閉，不會執行任何規則，也不會以任何方式分析要求。','Disabled:'=>'已停用：','When you first install the Wordfence Web Application Firewall, it will be in learning mode. This allows Wordfence to learn about your site so that we can understand how to protect it and how to allow normal visitors through the firewall. We recommend you let Wordfence learn for a week before you enable the firewall. <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'初次安裝 Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆時，系統將處於學習模式。這讓 Wordfence 逐步掌握您的網站運作模式，以便了解如何保護網站，並允許正常訪客通過防火牆。我們建議讓 Wordfence 學習一週後再啟用防火牆。<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">了解更多<span class="screen-reader-text"> (在新分頁開啟)</span></a>','Learning Mode:'=>'學習模式：','In this mode, the Wordfence Web Application Firewall is actively blocking requests matching known attack patterns and is actively protecting your site from attackers.'=>'在此模式下，Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆正主動封鎖符合已知攻擊模式的要求，並積極保護您的網站免受攻擊者侵害。','Enabled and Protecting:'=>'已啟用並保護中：','Basic Firewall Options'=>'基本防火牆選項','SHOW ALL RULES'=>'顯示所有規則','<a href="#" onclick="WFAD.wafUpdateRules();return false;" role="button">Click here</a> to pull down the latest from the Wordfence servers.'=>'<a href="#" onclick="WFAD.wafUpdateRules();return false;" role="button">點擊此處</a>從 Wordfence 伺服器下載最新內容。','No rules currently set.'=>'目前尚未設定任何規則。','Description'=>'描述','Category'=>'分類','Ignored IPs must be separated by commas or placed on separate lines. These addresses will be ignored from any alerts about increased attacks and can be used to ignore things like standalone website security scanners.'=>'被忽略的 IP 位址必須以逗號分隔或置於獨立行。這些位址將在攻擊增加的警示中被排除，可用於忽略獨立網站安全性掃描器等項目。','Separate multiple URLs with commas or place them on separate lines. Asterisks are wildcards, but use with care. If you see an attacker repeatedly probing your site for a known vulnerability you can use this to immediately block them. All URLs must start with a "/" without quotes and must be relative. e.g. /badURLone/, /bannedPage.html, /dont-access/this/URL/, /starts/with-*'=>'多個網址請以逗號分隔或分開列於不同行。星號為萬用字元，但請謹慎使用。若發現攻擊者反覆針對已知漏洞探測您的網站，可立即運用此功能封鎖其行為。所有網址必須以「/」開頭（不含引號），且必須為相對路徑。例如：/badURLone/、/bannedPage.html、/dont-access/this/URL/、/starts/with-*','Allowlisted IPs must be separated by commas or placed on separate lines. You can specify ranges using the following formats: 127.0.0.1/24, 127.0.0.[1-100], or 127.0.0.1-127.0.1.100<br/>Wordfence automatically allowlists <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Private_network" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">private networks<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a> because these are not routable on the public Internet.'=>'允許清單中的 IP 位址必須以逗號分隔或置於獨立行。您可以使用以下格式指定範圍：127.0.0.1/24、127.0.0.[1-100] 或 127.0.0.1-127.0.1.100。<br/>Wordfence 會自動將<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Private_network" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">私有網路</a>加入允許清單<span class="screen-reader-text"> (在新分頁開啟)</span>，因為這些網路在公共網際網路上不可路由。','You are currently running the WAF from another WordPress installation. This option can be changed once you configure the firewall to run correctly on this site.'=>'您目前正在從另一個 WordPress 安裝環境執行 WAF。此選項可在您將防火牆正確組態為在此網站運行後進行變更。','Advanced Firewall Options'=>'進階防火牆選項','No allowlisted URLs currently set.'=>'目前尚未設定任何允許清單中的網址。','Toggle row ${idx}'=>'切換第 ${idx} 列','Select row ${idx}'=>'選取第 ${idx} 列','Created'=>'建立時間','Select/deselect all'=>'全部選取/取消全選','Monitor background requests from an administrator\'s web browser for false positives'=>'監控網站管理員網頁瀏覽器中的背景要求以防止誤報','Admin Panel'=>'管理面板','Front-end Website'=>'前端網站','You are currently running the Wordfence Web Application Firewall from another WordPress installation. Please <a href="%s">click here</a> to configure the Firewall to run correctly on this site.'=>'您目前正在從另一個 WordPress 安裝執行 Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆。請<a href="%s">點擊此處</a>設定防火牆，使其能在此網站上正確運作。','The required file has been created. You\'ll need to insert the following code into your <code>php.ini</code> to finish installation:'=>'所需的檔案已建立。您需要將以下程式碼插入您的 <code>php.ini</code> 檔案以完成安裝：','The changes have not yet taken effect. If you are using LiteSpeed or IIS as your web server or CGI/FastCGI interface, you may need to wait a few minutes for the changes to take effect since the configuration files are sometimes cached. You also may need to select a different server configuration in order to complete this step, but wait for a few minutes before trying. You can try refreshing this page.'=>'變更尚未生效。若您使用 LiteSpeed 或 IIS 作為網頁伺服器，或採用 CGI/FastCGI 介面，由於設定檔有時會被快取，您可能需要等待數分鐘讓變更生效。此外，您可能需要選擇不同的伺服器設定才能完成此步驟，但請先等待數分鐘再嘗試。您可嘗試重新整理此頁面。','Nice work! The firewall is now optimized.'=>'做得好！防火牆現已完成最佳化。','Premium Protection Enabled'=>'高級版防護已啟用','<i class="wf-fa wf-fa-lightbulb-o wf-tip" aria-hidden="true"></i> When you first install the Wordfence Web Application Firewall, it will be in learning mode. This allows Wordfence to learn about your site so that we can understand how to protect it and how to allow normal visitors through the firewall. We recommend you let Wordfence learn for a week before you enable the firewall.'=>'<i class="wf-fa wf-fa-lightbulb-o wf-tip" aria-hidden="true"></i> 初次安裝 Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆時，系統將處於學習模式。這讓 Wordfence 逐步掌握您網站的特性，以便我們了解如何保護網站，並識別正常訪客以允許其通過防火牆。我們建議讓 Wordfence 進行為期一週的學習後再啟用防火牆。','Learning Mode Until %s'=>'學習模式持續至 %s','Learning Mode Enabled'=>'學習模式已啟用','Wordfence Firewall Activated'=>'Wordfence 防火牆已啟用','Enable Firewall'=>'啟用防火牆','The Wordfence Web Application Firewall is a PHP-based, application-level firewall that filters out malicious requests to your site. It is designed to run at the beginning of WordPress\' initialization to filter any attacks before plugins or themes can run any potentially vulnerable code.'=>'Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆是一款基於 PHP 的應用程式層級防火牆，能過濾針對您網站的惡意要求。其設計是在 WordPress 初始化階段啟動，在任何外掛或佈景主題執行可能具安全性漏洞的程式碼之前攔截攻擊。','Wordfence Firewall Deactivated'=>'Wordfence 防火牆已停用','Wordfence Firewall &amp; Premium Enabled'=>'Wordfence 防火牆與進階版已啟用','These URL patterns will be excluded from the throttling rules used to limit crawlers.'=>'這些網址模式將被排除在限制檢索器的節流規則之外。','block it'=>'封鎖','throttle it'=>'限制流量','%d per minute'=>'每分鐘 %d 次','Treat Google like any other Crawler'=>'將 Google 視為任何其他檢索器','Anyone claiming to be Google will not be rate-limited'=>'任何自稱是 Google 的實體皆不會受到速率限制','Verified Google crawlers will not be rate-limited'=>'經過驗證的 Google 檢索器將不受速率限制','NOTE: This checkbox enables ALL blocking/throttling functions including IP, country and advanced blocking, and the "Rate Limiting Rules" below.'=>'注意：此核取方塊將啟用所有封鎖/節流功能，包括 IP 封鎖、國家封鎖、進階封鎖，以及下方的「速率限制規則」。','Manually Refresh Rules'=>'手動重新整理規則','You are currently running the WAF from another WordPress installation. These rules can be disabled or enabled once you configure the firewall to run correctly on this site.'=>'您目前正在從另一個 WordPress 安裝環境執行 WAF。在您將防火牆正確組態為在此網站運行後，即可啟用或停用這些規則。','Rules'=>'規則','Filter Value'=>'篩選值','IP'=>'IP','User'=>'使用者','Source'=>'來源','Param'=>'參數','Disable'=>'停用','Delete'=>'刪除','Allowlisted via Firewall Options page'=>'透過防火牆選項頁面加入允許清單','An allowlist entry for this URL and parameter already exists.'=>'此網址與參數的允許清單項目已存在。','Add'=>'新增','Param Name'=>'參數名稱','Query String'=>'查詢字串','Header'=>'標頭','File Name'=>'檔案名稱','Cookie'=>'Cookie','POST Body'=>'POST 本文','URL'=>'網址','The URL/parameters in this table will not be tested by the firewall. They are typically added while the firewall is in Learning Mode or by an admin who identifies a particular action/request is a false positive.'=>'此表格中的網址/參數將不會被防火牆檢測。這些項目通常是在防火牆處於學習模式時加入，或是由網站管理員標記特定的操作/要求為誤判結果時加入。','Add Allowlisted URL/Param'=>'新增允許清單中的網址/參數','<br><strong>This setting will be ignored because the PHP configuration option <code>output_buffering</code> is off.</strong>'=>'<br><strong>此設定將被忽略，因為 PHP 組態選項 <code>output_buffering</code> 已關閉。</strong>','<strong>Enable Separate Prompt for Two-Factor Code<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wfhelp wf-inline-help"><span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a></strong><br><em>Note:</em> This setting changes the behavior for obtaining the two-factor authentication code from using the password field to showing a separate prompt. If your theme overrides the default login page, you may not be able to use this option.'=>'<strong>啟用兩步驟驗證碼獨立提示視窗<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wfhelp wf-inline-help"><span class="screen-reader-text"> (在新分頁開啟)</span></a></strong><br><em>注意：</em>此設定將變更取得兩步驟驗證碼的方式，從使用密碼欄位改為顯示獨立提示視窗。若您的佈景主題覆寫了預設登入頁面，可能無法使用此選項。','<strong>Require Cellphone Sign-in for all Administrators<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wfhelp wf-inline-help"><span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a></strong><br><em>Note:</em> This setting requires at least one administrator to have Cellphone Sign-in enabled. On multisite, this option applies only to super admins.'=>'<strong>要求所有網站管理員使用手機登入<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wfhelp wf-inline-help"><span class="screen-reader-text"> (在新分頁開啟)</span></a></strong><br><em>注意：</em>此設定需要至少一位網站管理員啟用手機登入。在多站網路中，此選項僅適用於多站網路管理員。','Two-Factor Authentication Options'=>'兩步驟驗證選項','Display Live Traffic menu option'=>'顯示即時流量選單項目','Maximum days to keep Live Traffic data (1-30 days)'=>'即時流量資料的最大保留天數 (1-30 天)','All Traffic'=>'所有流量','Security Only'=>'僅限安全性','Traffic logging mode'=>'流量記錄模式','Are you sure you want to restore the default Live Traffic settings? This will undo any custom changes you have made to the options on this page.'=>'確定要還原即時流量的預設設定嗎？此操作將撤銷您在此頁面所做的所有自訂變更。','These options let you choose which traffic to log and to ignore certain types of visitors, based on their level of access, usernames, IP address, or browser type. If you run a high-traffic website where it is not feasible to see your visitors in real-time, simply change the <strong>Traffic logging mode</strong> to "Security Only."'=>'這些選項可讓您根據訪客的存取層級、使用者名稱、IP 位址或瀏覽器類型，選取要記錄哪些流量並忽略特定類型的訪客。若您經營的是高流量網站，無法即時查看所有訪客，只需將<strong>流量記錄模式</strong>切換為「僅安全性」即可。','Live Traffic Options'=>'即時流量選項','Block<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Visitors Matching this</span> Pattern'=>'封鎖<span class="wf-hidden-xs">符合此</span>模式的訪客','Enter a reason'=>'輸入原因','<span class="wf-hidden-xs">Block </span>Reason'=>'<span class="wf-hidden-xs">封鎖</span>原因','e.g., *badwebsite.example.com*'=>'範例：*badwebsite.example.com*','e.g., *badRobot*, *MSIE*, or *browserSuffix'=>'範例：*badRobot*、*MSIE* 或 *browserSuffix*','<span class="wf-hidden-xs">Browser </span>User Agent'=>'<span class="wf-hidden-xs">瀏覽器</span>使用者代理程式','e.g., *.amazonaws.com or *.linode.com'=>'範例：*.amazonaws.com 或 *.linode.com','e.g., 192.168.200.200 - 192.168.200.220 or 192.168.200.0/24'=>'範例：192.168.200.200 - 192.168.200.220 或 192.168.200.0/24','IP<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Address</span> Range'=>'IP <span class="wf-hidden-xs">位址</span>範圍','Enter an IP address'=>'輸入 IP 位址','IP<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Address to Block</span>'=>'<span class="wf-hidden-xs">要封鎖的 </span>IP 位址','Pick<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> from List</span>'=>'<span class="wf-hidden-xs">從清單中</span>選取','Countries<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> to Block</span>'=>'<span class="wf-hidden-xs">要封鎖的</span>國家','<span class="wf-hidden-xs">Block access to the rest of the site</span><span class="wf-visible-xs">Rest of site</span>'=>'<span class="wf-hidden-xs">封鎖存取網站其餘部分</span><span class="wf-visible-xs">網站其餘部分</span>','Login Form'=>'登入表單','<span class="wf-hidden-xs">What to </span>Block'=>'<span class="wf-hidden-xs">要封鎖的</span>對象','Enter a duration (default is forever)'=>'輸入持續時間（預設為永久）','Block Duration'=>'封鎖持續時間','Country Blocking'=>'國家封鎖','<span class="wf-hidden-xs">Custom </span>Pattern'=>'<span class="wf-hidden-xs">自訂</span>模式','Block<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Visitors Matching this Pattern</span>'=>'封鎖<span class="wf-hidden-xs">符合此模式的訪客</span>','Country'=>'國家/地區','Update<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Block</span>'=>'更新<span class="wf-hidden-xs">封鎖</span>','Block<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> the Selected Countries</span>'=>'封鎖<span class="wf-hidden-xs">所選國家</span>','IP<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Address</span>'=>'IP<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> 位址</span>','Block<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> this IP Address</span>'=>'封鎖<span class="wf-hidden-xs">此 IP 位址</span>','Wordfence country blocking is designed to stop an attack, prevent content theft, or end malicious activity that originates from a geographic region in less than 1/300,000th of a second. Blocking countries who are regularly creating failed logins, a large number of page not found errors, and are clearly engaged in malicious activity is an effective way to protect your site during an attack.'=>'Wordfence 國家封鎖功能旨在以低於 1/300,000 秒的速度，阻擋源自特定地理區域的攻擊、防止內容竊取或終止惡意活動。針對經常產生登入失敗、大量「找不到頁面」錯誤且明顯從事惡意行為的國家實施封鎖，是在受攻擊期間保護網站的有效方式。','Put Geographic Protection In Place With Country Blocking'=>'透過國家封鎖功能實施地理位置保護','Enter a full URL (e.g., http://example.com/blocked/)'=>'請輸入完整網址 (範例：http://example.com/blocked/)','URL to redirect blocked users to'=>'將遭封鎖使用者重新導向至的網址','What to do when we block someone'=>'當我們封鎖某人時該怎麼做','Advanced Country Blocking Options'=>'進階國家封鎖選項','Are you sure you want to stop blocking the ${count} selected IPs, ranges, and countries?'=>'您確定要停止封鎖已選取的 ${count} 個 IP、範圍及國家嗎？','Are you sure you want to stop blocking the selected IP, range, or country?'=>'您確定要停止封鎖所選的 IP、範圍或國家嗎？','Unblocking'=>'解除封鎖中','Change Filter'=>'變更篩選器','Clear Filter'=>'清除篩選器','No blocks match the current filter.'=>'沒有符合當前篩選條件的封鎖。','No blocks are currently active.'=>'目前沒有生效的封鎖。','Last Attempt'=>'最後嘗試','Block Count'=>'封鎖次數','Expiration'=>'到期日','Reason'=>'原因','Rule Added'=>'已新增規則','Detail'=>'詳細資訊','Block Type'=>'封鎖類型','Export<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> All IPs</span>'=>'匯出<span class="wf-hidden-xs">所有 IP</span>','Make Permanent'=>'永久化','Unblock'=>'解除封鎖','Filter'=>'篩選器','Filter by Type, Detail, or Reason'=>'依類型、詳細資訊或原因篩選','Show<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Wordfence</span> Automatic<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Blocks</span>'=>'顯示<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Wordfence</span> 自動<span class="wf-hidden-xs">封鎖</span>','Current blocks<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> for %s</span>'=>'目前<span class="wf-hidden-xs">針對 %s 的</span>封鎖','Save'=>'儲存','Back'=>'返回','Unblock All'=>'全部解除封鎖','Block All'=>'全部封鎖','Select Countries to Block from List'=>'從清單中選取要封鎖的國家','then set a cookie that will bypass country blocking in the future in case that user hits the site from a blocked country.'=>'接著設定一個 Cookie，以便未來當該使用者從受限國家存取網站時，能繞過國家封鎖機制。','/set-country-bypass/'=>'/set-country-bypass/','If user who is allowed to access the site views the relative URL'=>'若獲准存取該網站的使用者檢視相對網址','Bypass Cookie'=>'繞過 Cookie','Manage global blocking options.'=>'管理全球封鎖選項。','and set a cookie that will bypass all country blocking.'=>'並設定一個能繞過所有國家封鎖的 Cookie。','/page-name/'=>'/page-name/','then redirect that user to'=>'接著將該使用者重新導向至','/bypassurl/'=>'/bypassurl/','If user hits the relative URL'=>'若使用者點擊相對網址','Bypass Redirect'=>'繞過重新導向','Done'=>'完成','Wordfence now includes the option to enable Google reCaptcha v3 on your WordPress login and registration pages. This adds a powerful new layer of protection against password guessing and credential stuffing attacks from bots without slowing down real users.'=>'Wordfence 現在新增了選項，可在您的 WordPress 登入與註冊頁面啟用 Google reCaptcha v3。這為防禦漫遊器發動的密碼猜測與認證填充攻擊增添了強大防護層，同時不會拖慢真實使用者的速度。','New Login Page Captcha Feature'=>'新版登入頁面驗證碼功能','Two-factor authentication now has its own IP allowlist. If necessary, you can allow specific IP addresses or ranges to skip 2FA when logging in.'=>'兩步驟驗證現在擁有專屬的 IP 允許清單。如有需要，您可以允許特定 IP 位址或範圍在登入時跳過 2FA。','Individual Allowlisting'=>'個別允許清單','We are excited to announce the release of a completely rebuilt two-factor authentication (2FA) feature within Wordfence. 2FA is an important layer of security that protects you from password guessing and credential stuffing attacks. Previously a Premium-only feature, it is now available for sites running the free version of Wordfence. You are now able to enable 2FA for any role, we’ve added a number of important security features, and we’ve significantly improved the admin interface.'=>'我們很高興宣布 Wordfence 內建的兩步驟驗證 (2FA) 功能已完成全面重建並正式推出。2FA 是重要的安全性防護層，能保護您免受密碼猜測與認證填充攻擊。此功能原為高級版專屬，現已開放給使用免費版 Wordfence 的網站。您現在可以為任何角色啟用 2FA，我們也新增了多項重要安全性功能並大幅優化管理介面。','Introducing the New Wordfence 2FA'=>'全新 Wordfence 兩步驟驗證功能登場','How do I get to 100%?'=>'我該如何達到 100%？','How does Wordfence determine this?'=>'Wordfence 是如何判斷這一點的？','<strong>Congratulations!</strong> You\'ve optimized configurations for this feature! If you want to learn more about how this score is determined, click the link below.'=>'<strong>恭喜！</strong>您已完成此功能的設定最佳化！若想進一步了解評分機制，請點擊下方連結。','Please confirm the unsubscribe request for %s.'=>'請確認 %s 的取消訂閱要求。','Please enter an email address to unsubscribe from alerts. If this email address exists on the alert email list, it will receive a confirmation link to unsubscribe.'=>'請輸入電子郵件地址以取消訂閱警示。若此電子郵件地址存在於警示郵件清單中，將會收到確認取消訂閱的連結。','If the email address provided was on the alert email list, it has been sent an unsubscribe link.'=>'若提供的電子郵件地址已加入警示郵件清單，系統已向該地址傳送取消訂閱連結。','The email address provided has been unsubscribed from future alert emails.'=>'提供的電子郵件地址已從未來警示郵件的訂閱名單中移除。','Confirm Unsubscribe'=>'確認取消訂閱','Unsubscribe Successful'=>'取消訂閱成功','Unsubscription Confirmation Sent'=>'取消訂閱確認信已傳送','Unsubscribe from Security Alerts'=>'取消訂閱安全警報','Your computer\'s time: '=>'您的電腦時間： ','Generated by Wordfence at '=>'由 Wordfence 產生於 ','Please enter the license to install.'=>'請輸入要安裝的授權。','The Wordfence license could not be installed.'=>'無法安裝 Wordfence 授權。','Return to the <a href="%s">Wordfence Admin Page</a>'=>'返回 <a href="%s">Wordfence 管理頁面</a>','The Wordfence license provided has been installed.'=>'提供的 Wordfence 授權已安裝。','Install Wordfence License'=>'安裝 Wordfence 授權','Wordfence License Installation Failed'=>'Wordfence 授權安裝失敗','Wordfence License Installation Successful'=>'Wordfence 授權安裝成功','User defined scan pattern'=>'使用者自訂掃描模式','Enable scan option to check if your website is on a domain blocklist.'=>'啟用掃描選項，檢查您的網站是否被列入網域封鎖名單。','Enable scan option to check if your website IP is generating spam.'=>'啟用掃描選項以檢查您的網站 IP 是否正在產生垃圾訊息。','Enable scan option to check if this website is being "Spamvertised".'=>'啟用掃描選項以檢查此網站是否正遭受「垃圾廣告推廣」。','Enable Premium Reputation Checks.'=>'啟用進階版信譽檢查。','Standard detection capability'=>'標準檢測能力','Custom scan options selected'=>'已選取自訂掃描選項','Standard detection capability, chance of false positives'=>'標準檢測能力，有誤判機率','Low resource utilization, limited detection capability'=>'低資源使用率，偵測能力有限','Standard'=>'標準','Custom'=>'自訂','High Sensitivity'=>'高靈敏度','Limited'=>'有限','Quick'=>'快速','No block parameters provided.'=>'未提供封鎖參數。','Invalid hostname.'=>'主機名稱無效。','Invalid IP range.'=>'無效的 IP 範圍。','Ranges mixing IPv4 and IPv6 addresses are not supported.'=>'不支援混合使用 IPv4 和 IPv6 位址的範圍。','An invalid country was selected.'=>'選取的國家無效。','No countries selected.'=>'尚未選取國家。','Nothing selected to block.'=>'未選取任何要封鎖的項目。','This IP address is in a range of addresses that Wordfence does not block. The IP range may be internal or belong to a service that is always allowed. Allowlisting of external services can be disabled. <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'此 IP 位址位於 Wordfence 不進行封鎖的位址範圍內。該 IP 範圍可能是內部網路，或屬於始終允許存取的服務。外部服務的允許清單功能可被停用。<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">了解更多<span class="screen-reader-text"> (在新分頁開啟)</span></a>','Invalid IP address.'=>'無效的 IP 位址。','A block reason must be provided.'=>'必須提供封鎖原因。','Invalid block duration.'=>'無效的封鎖持續時間。','Invalid block type.'=>'無效的封鎖類型。','Advanced Block'=>'進階封鎖','Country Block'=>'國家封鎖','Lockout'=>'鎖定','IP Throttled'=>'IP 流量限制','IP Block'=>'IP 封鎖','Support'=>'支援','Dashboard'=>'控制台','Enable Brute Force Protection.'=>'啟用暴力破解防護。','Disable Author Scanning.'=>'停用作者掃描功能。','Enable Block Admin Registration.'=>'啟用封鎖管理員註冊功能。','Enable Mask Login Errors.'=>'啟用隱藏登入錯誤。','Enforce Strong Passwords.'=>'強制使用強密碼。','Enable Real-Time Wordfence Security Network.'=>'啟用即時 Wordfence 安全防護網路。','Enable Real-Time IP Blocklist.'=>'啟用即時 IP 封鎖清單。','Enable Firewall.'=>'啟用防火牆。','Repair the Wordfence Firewall configuration.'=>'修復 Wordfence 防火牆設定。','Enable Rate Limiting and Advanced Blocking.'=>'啟用速率限制與進階封鎖功能。','Optimize the Wordfence Firewall.'=>'最佳化 Wordfence 防火牆。','Enable Premium Rules.'=>'啟用付費版規則。','Enable firewall.'=>'啟用防火牆。','Basic Protection'=>'基本防護','Extended Protection'=>'延伸防護','Learning Mode'=>'學習模式','Skip'=>'略過','Reminder: If you lose access to your authenticator device, you can use recovery codes to log in. If you have not saved a copy of your recovery codes, we recommend downloading them now.'=>'提醒：若您遺失驗證器裝置，可使用復原代碼登入。若您尚未儲存復原代碼的備份，建議立即下載。','An error was encountered while trying to activate two-factor authentication. Please try again.'=>'在嘗試啟用兩步驟驗證時發生錯誤。請重新嘗試。','Error Activating 2FA'=>'啟用兩步驟驗證時發生錯誤','For help on setting up an app, visit our help article.'=>'如需應用程式設定協助，請參閱我們的說明文章。','Enter the code from your authenticator app below to verify and activate two-factor authentication for this account.'=>'請在下方輸入驗證器應用程式的代碼，以驗證並啟用此帳戶的兩步驟驗證功能。','Optional'=>'選填','Download Recovery Codes'=>'下載復原代碼','2. Enter Code from Authenticator App'=>'2. 輸入驗證器應用程式的代碼','An error was encountered while trying to deactivate two-factor authentication. Please try again.'=>'嘗試停用兩步驟驗證時發生錯誤。請重新嘗試。','Error Deactivating 2FA'=>'停用兩步驟驗證時發生錯誤','Are you sure you want to deactivate two-factor authentication?'=>'您確定要停用兩步驟驗證嗎？','Deactivate 2FA'=>'停用兩步驟驗證','Deactivate'=>'停用','Wordfence two-factor authentication is currently active on the account <strong>%s</strong>. You may deactivate it by clicking the button below.'=>'Wordfence 兩步驟驗證目前已在帳戶 <strong>%s</strong> 上啟用。您可點擊下方按鈕停用此功能。','Wordfence two-factor authentication is currently active on your account. You may deactivate it by clicking the button below.'=>'您的帳戶目前已啟用 Wordfence 兩步驟驗證功能。您可點擊下方按鈕停用此功能。','Wordfence 2FA Active'=>'Wordfence 兩步驟驗證已啟用','1. Scan Code or Enter Key'=>'1. 掃描條碼或輸入金鑰','An error was encountered while trying to generate new recovery codes. Please try again.'=>'嘗試產生新的復原代碼時發生錯誤。請稍後再試。','New Recovery Codes'=>'新的復原代碼','Each line of %d letters and numbers is a single recovery code, with optional spaces for readability. To use a recovery code, after entering your username and password, enter the code like "1234 5678 90AB CDEF" at the 2FA prompt. If your site has a custom login prompt and does not show a 2FA prompt, you can use the single-step method by entering your password and the code together in the Password field, like "mypassword1234 5678 90AB CDEF". Your recovery codes are:'=>'每一行由 %d 個字母與數字組成的字串即為單一復原代碼，其中包含可選的空格以提升可讀性。使用復原代碼時，請於輸入使用者名稱與密碼後，在兩步驟驗證 (2FA) 提示欄位輸入完整代碼（例如：&quot;1234 5678 90AB CDEF&quot;）。 若您的網站採用自訂登入介面且未顯示 2FA 提示，可採用單步驟驗證方式：在密碼欄位同時輸入密碼與代碼，例如「mypassword1234 5678 90AB CDEF」。您的復原代碼如下：','Two-Factor Authentication Recovery Codes - %s (%s)'=>'兩步驟驗證復原代碼 - %s (%s)','Use one of these %d codes to log in if you lose access to your authenticator device. Codes are %d characters long plus optional spaces. Each one may be used only once.'=>'若您遺失驗證器裝置，請使用這 %d 組代碼的其中一組登入。每個代碼長度為 %d 個字元（含可選空格），且僅限使用一次。','Error Generating New Codes'=>'生成新代碼時發生錯誤','Generate'=>'產生','Are you sure you want to generate new recovery codes? Any remaining unused codes will be disabled.'=>'您確定要產生新的復原代碼嗎？任何剩餘未使用過的代碼都將被停用。','Generate New Recovery Codes'=>'產生新的復原代碼','Generate New Codes'=>'產生新代碼','Recovery Codes'=>'復原代碼','If enabled, all settings and 2FA records will be deleted on deactivation. If later reactivated, all users that previously had 2FA active will need to set it up again.'=>'若啟用此設定，停用時所有設定與兩步驟驗證記錄將被刪除。若後續重新啟用，先前曾啟用兩步驟驗證的所有使用者皆需重新設定。','Delete Login Security tables and data on deactivation'=>'停用時刪除登入安全資料表及資料','While in test mode, reCAPTCHA will score login and registration requests but not actually block them. The scores will be recorded and can be used to select a human/bot threshold value.'=>'在測試模式下，reCAPTCHA 會對登入和註冊請求進行評分，但不會實際封鎖這些請求。評分結果將被記錄，可用於設定人類/機器人閾值。','Run reCAPTCHA in test mode'=>'以測試模式執行 reCAPTCHA','Allowlisted IPs must be placed on separate lines. You can specify ranges using the following formats: 127.0.0.1/24, 127.0.0.[1-100], or 127.0.0.1-127.0.1.100.'=>'允許清單中的 IP 位址必須分開列於不同行。您可使用以下格式指定範圍：127.0.0.1/24、127.0.0.[1-100] 或 127.0.0.1-127.0.1.100。','Disable XML-RPC authentication'=>'停用 XML-RPC 驗證','Required'=>'必填','Skipped'=>'略過','If enabled, XML-RPC calls that require authentication will also require a valid 2FA code to be appended to the password. You must choose the "Skipped" option if you use the WordPress app, the Jetpack plugin, or other services that require XML-RPC.'=>'若啟用此設定，所有需要驗證的 XML-RPC 呼叫都必須在密碼後附加有效的兩步驟驗證代碼。若您使用 WordPress 應用程式、Jetpack 外掛程式或其他需要 XML-RPC 的服務，請務必選擇「略過」選項。','Require 2FA for XML-RPC call authentication'=>'XML-RPC 呼叫驗證要求使用兩步驟驗證 (2FA)','If enabled, users with 2FA enabled may choose to be prompted for a code only once every 30 days per device.'=>'若啟用此功能，已啟用兩步驟驗證的使用者可選擇每台裝置每 30 天僅提示輸入驗證碼一次。','Allow remembering device for 30 days'=>'允許記憶裝置存留 30 天','Super Administrator'=>'超級管理員','Save<span class="wfls-visible-sm-inline"> Changes</span>'=>'儲存<span class="wfls-visible-sm-inline">變更</span>','Cancel<span class="wfls-visible-sm-inline"> Changes</span>'=>'取消<span class="wfls-visible-sm-inline">變更</span>','* User counts currently only reflect the main site on multisite installations.'=>'* 使用者計數目前僅反映多站網路安裝中的主網站。','Total Users'=>'總使用者數','Role'=>'角色','Manage Users'=>'管理使用者','User Summary'=>'使用者摘要','Detected IP:'=>'偵測到的 IP 位址：','Corrected Time (WF):'=>'修正時間 (WF)：','Corrected Time (NTP):'=>'校正時間 (NTP)：','Browser Time:'=>'瀏覽器時間：','Server Time:'=>'伺服器時間：','(you)'=>'（您）','Editing User:&nbsp;&nbsp;%s <span class="wfls-text-plain">%s</span>'=>'編輯使用者： %s <span class="wfls-text-plain">%s</span>','Two-Factor Authentication, or 2FA, significantly improves login security for your website. Wordfence 2FA works with a number of TOTP-based apps like Google Authenticator, FreeOTP, and Authy. For a full list of tested TOTP-based apps, <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">click here</a>.'=>'兩步驟驗證（或稱 2FA）能顯著提升網站登入安全性。Wordfence 兩步驟驗證支援多種基於 TOTP 的應用程式，例如 Google Authenticator、FreeOTP 及 Authy。如需完整測試過的 TOTP 應用程式清單，<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">請點擊此處</a>。','The request was flagged as suspicious, and we need verification that you attempted to log in to allow it to proceed. This verification link <b>will be valid for 15 minutes</b> from the time it was sent. If you did not attempt this login, please change your password immediately.'=>'此請求已被標記為可疑，我們需要您進行驗證以確認您確實嘗試登入，方能繼續處理。此驗證連結自發送時起 <b>15 分鐘內有效</b>。若您未曾嘗試此登入操作，請立即變更密碼。','IP:'=>'IP：','Request Time:'=>'請求時間：','Count'=>'計數','reCAPTCHA Score History'=>'reCAPTCHA 分數歷史記錄','Requests'=>'請求','Reset Score Statistics'=>'重設分數統計','A reCAPTCHA score equal to or higher than this value will be considered human. Anything lower will be treated as a bot and require additional verification for login and registration.'=>'reCAPTCHA 分數等於或高於此值時，將被視為真人。低於此值的任何請求都將被視為機器人，且在登入與註冊時需要進行額外驗證。','reCAPTCHA human/bot threshold score'=>'reCAPTCHA 人類/機器人閾值分數','0.2'=>'0.2','0.3'=>'0.3','0.4'=>'0.4','0.5 (probably a human)'=>'0.5（可能是人類）','0.6'=>'0.6','0.7'=>'0.7','0.8'=>'0.8','0.9'=>'0.9','1.0 (definitely a human)'=>'1.0（絕對是人類）','reCAPTCHA v3 Secret'=>'reCAPTCHA v3 秘密金鑰','reCAPTCHA v3 Site Key'=>'reCAPTCHA v3 網站金鑰','reCAPTCHA v3 does not make users solve puzzles or click a checkbox like previous versions. The only visible part is the reCAPTCHA logo. If a visitor\'s browser fails the CAPTCHA, Wordfence will send an email to the user\'s address with a link they can click to verify that they are a user of your site. You can read further details <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">in our documentation</a>.'=>'reCAPTCHA v3 不像先前版本要求使用者解謎題或點擊核取方塊。唯一可見的部分是 reCAPTCHA 標誌。若訪客的瀏覽器未能通過驗證碼，Wordfence 將寄送電子郵件至使用者的地址，內含可點擊的連結以確認其為您網站的合法使用者。您可參閱<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">我們的文件以獲取</a>更多詳細資訊。','Enable reCAPTCHA on the login and user registration pages'=>'在登入及使用者註冊頁面啟用 reCAPTCHA','These IPs (or CIDR ranges) will be ignored when determining the requesting IP via the X-Forwarded-For HTTP header. Enter one IP or CIDR range per line.'=>'這些 IP（或 CIDR 範圍）在透過 X-Forwarded-For HTTP 標頭判斷請求來源 IP 時將被忽略。請每行輸入一個 IP 或 CIDR 範圍。','How to get IPs'=>'如何取得 IP 位址','Use the X-Real-IP HTTP header. Only use if you have a front-end proxy or spoofing may result.'=>'使用 X-Real-IP HTTP 標頭。僅當您擁有前端 Proxy 伺服器時才使用，否則可能導致偽造行為。','Use the X-Forwarded-For HTTP header. Only use if you have a front-end proxy or spoofing may result.'=>'使用 X-Forwarded-For HTTP 標頭。僅在您擁有前端 Proxy 伺服器時使用，否則可能導致偽造行為。','Use PHP\'s built in REMOTE_ADDR and don\'t use anything else. Very secure if this is compatible with your site.'=>'請使用 PHP 內建的 REMOTE_ADDR 功能，切勿採用其他替代方案。若此設定與您的網站相容，將能提供極高的安全性。','(Recommended)'=>'（建議）','Use the most secure method to get visitor IP addresses. Prevents spoofing and works with most sites.'=>'採用最安全的訪客 IP 位址取得方式。可防止偽造行為，並適用於多數網站。','Premium Feature'=>'進階版功能','An error was encountered while trying to send the notification. Please try again.'=>'在嘗試發送通知時發生錯誤。請重試。','Notification Sent'=>'通知已發送','Error Sending Notification'=>'發送通知時發生錯誤','If you\'re looking for a more comprehensive solution, the <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">full Wordfence plugin</a> includes all of the features in this plugin as well as a full-featured WordPress firewall, a security scanner, live traffic, and more. The standard installation includes a robust set of free features that can be upgraded via a Premium license key.'=>'若您尋求更全面的解決方案，<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">完整版 Wordfence 外掛</a>不僅包含此外掛的所有功能，更整合了功能齊全的 WordPress 防火牆、安全掃描器、即時流量監控等進階工具。標準安裝版本已內建強大的免費功能集，您可透過付費版授權金鑰進行升級。','You have just installed the Wordfence Login Security plugin. It contains a subset of the functionality found in the full Wordfence plugin: Two-factor Authentication, XML-RPC Protection and Login Page CAPTCHA.'=>'您剛安裝了 Wordfence 登入安全外掛。此外掛包含完整版 Wordfence 外掛的部分功能：兩步驟驗證、XML-RPC 防護及登入頁面驗證碼。','Wordfence Login Security Installed'=>'Wordfence 登入安全功能已安裝','<a class="wfls-btn wfls-btn-default wfls-btn-sm wfls-dismiss-link" href="#" onclick="GWFLS.dismiss_notice(\'%s\'); return false;">Dismiss</a>'=>'<a class="wfls-btn wfls-btn-default wfls-btn-sm wfls-dismiss-link" href="#" onclick="GWFLS.dismiss_notice(\'%s\'); return false;">關閉</a>','Learn more<span class="wfls-hidden-xs"> about Login Security</span>'=>'深入了解<span class="wfls-hidden-xs">登入安全性</span>','Login Security Settings'=>'登入安全設定','Settings'=>'設定','Learn more<span class="wfls-hidden-xs"> about Two-Factor Authentication</span>'=>'深入了解<span class="wfls-hidden-xs">兩步驟驗證</span>','Login Security'=>'登入安全','Email verification invalid or expired. Please try again.'=>'電子郵件驗證無效或已過期。請重新嘗試。','Email verification succeeded. Please continue logging in.'=>'電子郵件驗證成功。請繼續登入。','<strong>REGISTRATION BLOCKED</strong>: The registration request was blocked because it was flagged as spam. Please try again or contact the site owner for help.'=>'<strong>註冊遭封鎖</strong>：您的註冊請求因被標記為垃圾訊息而遭封鎖。請重新嘗試或聯絡網站擁有者尋求協助。','<strong>REGISTRATION BLOCKED</strong>: The registration request was blocked because it was flagged as spam. Please try again or <a href="#" class="wfls-registration-captcha-contact" data-token="%s">contact the site owner</a> for help.'=>'<strong>註冊遭封鎖</strong>：您的註冊請求因被標記為垃圾訊息而遭封鎖。請重新嘗試或<a href="#" class="wfls-registration-captcha-contact" data-token="%s">聯絡網站擁有者</a>尋求協助。','<strong>REGISTRATION ATTEMPT BLOCKED</strong>: The security token for the login attempt was invalid or expired. Please reload the page and try again.'=>'<strong>註冊嘗試遭封鎖</strong>：本次登入嘗試的安全性憑證無效或已過期。請重新載入頁面並再次嘗試。','<strong>REGISTRATION ATTEMPT BLOCKED</strong>: This site requires a security token created when the page loads for all registration attempts. Please ensure JavaScript is enabled and try again.'=>'<strong>註冊嘗試遭阻擋</strong>：本網站要求所有註冊嘗試均須使用頁面載入時產生的安全性憑證。請確保已啟用 JavaScript 並重新嘗試。','You do not currently have two-factor authentication active on your account, which will be required beginning %s. <a href="%s">Configure 2FA</a>'=>'您的帳戶目前未啟用兩步驟驗證功能，此功能將於 %s 起強制實施。<a href="%s">設定兩步驟驗證</a>','<strong>CODE REQUIRED</strong>: Please provide your 2FA code when prompted.'=>'<strong>需要驗證碼</strong>：請於系統提示時輸入您的兩步驟驗證碼。','<strong>CODE REQUIRED</strong>: Please enter your 2FA code immediately after your password in the same field.'=>'<strong>需要驗證碼</strong>：請在輸入密碼後，立即於同一欄位中輸入您的兩步驟驗證碼。','<strong>CODE INVALID</strong>: The 2FA code provided is either expired or invalid. Please try again.'=>'<strong>驗證碼無效</strong>：您提供的兩步驟驗證碼已過期或無效。請重新嘗試。','Login Verification Required'=>'需進行登入驗證','Manage 2FA Settings'=>'管理兩步驟驗證設定','Two-factor authentication is not currently enabled for this account type. To enable it, visit the Wordfence 2FA Settings page.'=>'此帳戶類型目前未啟用兩步驟驗證功能。若要啟用此功能，請前往 Wordfence 兩步驟驗證設定頁面。','Activate 2FA'=>'啟用兩步驟驗證','Manage 2FA'=>'管理兩步驟驗證','Wordfence 2FA is inactive.'=>'Wordfence 兩步驟驗證功能已停用。','Wordfence 2FA is active.'=>'Wordfence 兩步驟驗證功能已啟用。','Wordfence Login Security'=>'Wordfence 登入安全防護','reCAPTCHA test mode is enabled. While enabled, login and registration requests will be checked for their score but will not be blocked if the score is below the minimum score. <a href="%s">Manage Settings</a>'=>'reCAPTCHA 測試模式已啟用。啟用期間，系統將檢查登入與註冊請求的分數，但若分數低於最低門檻，仍會允許請求通過。<a href="%s">管理設定</a>','XML-RPC authentication is disabled. Jetpack is currently active and requires XML-RPC authentication to work correctly. <a href="%s">Manage Settings</a>'=>'XML-RPC 驗證功能已停用。Jetpack 目前處於啟用狀態，需透過 XML-RPC 驗證方能正常運作。<a href="%s">管理設定</a>','Login Security options are available on the Login Security options page'=>'登入安全性選項可於「登入安全性選項」頁面中設定','Login Security Options'=>'登入安全選項','Login Security: Enable reCAPTCHA on the login and user registration pages'=>'登入安全性：在登入及使用者註冊頁面啟用 reCAPTCHA','Login Security: Disable XML-RPC authentication'=>'登入安全性：停用 XML-RPC 驗證','Login Security: Require 2FA for XML-RPC call authentication'=>'登入安全性：XML-RPC 呼叫驗證要求使用兩步驟驗證 (2FA)','Login Security: Allow remembering device for 30 days'=>'登入安全性：允許裝置記憶功能持續 30 天','Login Security: Enable 2FA for these roles'=>'登入安全性：為以下角色啟用兩步驟驗證','An error was encountered while validating the reCAPTCHA site key: %s'=>'驗證 reCAPTCHA 網站金鑰時發生錯誤：%s','Unable to validate the reCAPTCHA site key. Please check the key and try again.'=>'無法驗證 reCAPTCHA 網站金鑰。請檢查金鑰並重新嘗試。','An invalid IP source was provided.'=>'提供了無效的 IP 來源。','The IP/range %s is invalid.'=>'IP/範圍 %s 無效。','A reminder to activate two-factor authentication was sent to %d user.'=>'已向 %d 位使用者發送啟用兩步驟驗證的提醒通知。','A reminder to activate two-factor authentication was sent to %d users.'=>'已向 %d 位使用者發送啟用兩步驟驗證的提醒通知。','2FA will soon be required on %s'=>'%s 即將強制啟用兩步驟驗證 (2FA)','You do not have permission to generate new recovery codes.'=>'您沒有權限生成新的復原代碼。','You do not have permission to generate new recovery codes for the given user.'=>'您無權限為指定使用者產生新的復原代碼。','The user specified does not have two-factor authentication active.'=>'指定的使用者未啟用兩步驟驗證功能。','You do not have permission to deactivate 2FA.'=>'您沒有權限停用兩步驟驗證。','The user does not exist.'=>'該使用者不存在。','You do not have permission to deactivate the given user.'=>'您沒有權限停用指定的使用者。','%d unused recovery codes remain. You may generate a new set by clicking below.'=>'尚餘 %d 個未使用之復原代碼。您可點擊下方按鈕生成新的一組。','%d unused recovery code remains. You may generate a new set by clicking below.'=>'尚餘 %d 個未使用之復原代碼。您可點擊下方按鈕生成新的一組。','The code provided does not match the expected value. Please verify that the time on your authenticator device is correct and that this server\'s time is correct.'=>'提供的驗證碼與預期值不符。請確認您的驗證器裝置時間設定正確，且本伺服器時間設定無誤。','The given user already has two-factor authentication active.'=>'該使用者已啟用兩步驟驗證功能。','You do not have permission to activate 2FA.'=>'您沒有權限啟用兩步驟驗證。','The given user does not exist.'=>'指定的使用者不存在。','You do not have permission to activate the given user.'=>'您沒有權限啟用指定的使用者。','<strong>ERROR</strong>: An error occurred while sending the message. Please try again.'=>'<strong>錯誤</strong>：傳送訊息時發生錯誤。請重試。','<strong>MESSAGE SENT</strong>: Your message was sent to the site owner.'=>'<strong>訊息已發送</strong>：您的訊息已傳送至網站擁有者。','A visitor blocked from registration sent the following message.

----------------------------------------

IP: %s
Username: %s
Email: %s
reCAPTCHA Score: %f

----------------------------------------

%s'=>'一名被禁止註冊的訪客發送了以下訊息。

----------------------------------------

IP: %s
使用者名稱: %s
電子郵件: %s
reCAPTCHA 分數: %f

