%s','Blocked User Registration Contact Form'=>'遭封鎖使用者註冊聯絡表單','<strong>ERROR</strong>: Unable to send message. You have exceeded the maximum number of messages that may be sent at this time. Please try again later.'=>'<strong>錯誤</strong>：無法發送訊息。您已超過當前可發送的最大訊息數量。請稍後再試。','<strong>ERROR</strong>: Unable to send message. Please refresh the page and try again.'=>'<strong>錯誤</strong>：無法發送訊息。請重新整理頁面並再次嘗試。','<strong>ERROR</strong>: The username or password you entered is incorrect. <a href="%s" title="Password Lost and Found">Lost your password</a>?'=>'<strong>錯誤</strong>：您輸入的使用者名稱或密碼不正確。<a href="%s" title="Password Lost and Found">忘記密碼了嗎</a>？','<strong>ERROR</strong>: A username and password must be provided. <a href="%s" title="Password Lost and Found">Lost your password</a>?'=>'<strong>錯誤</strong>：必須提供使用者名稱和密碼。<a href="%s" title="Password Lost and Found">忘記密碼了嗎</a>？','Your browser sent an invalid security token. Please try reloading this page.'=>'您的瀏覽器傳送了無效的安全性憑證。請嘗試重新載入此頁面。','An expected parameter was not provided.'=>'未提供預期的參數。','An unknown action was provided.'=>'提供了未知的動作。','You do not have permission to reset reCAPTCHA statistics.'=>'您沒有權限重設 reCAPTCHA 統計資料。','You do not have permission to send notifications.'=>'您沒有發送通知的權限。','You do not have permission to change options.'=>'您沒有變更選項的權限。','2FA Inactive'=>'兩步驟驗證未啟用','2FA Active'=>'兩步驟驗證已啟用','2FA'=>'兩步驟驗證','Edit two-factor authentication for %s'=>'編輯 %s 的兩步驟驗證設定','Not Allowed'=>'不允許','Last CAPTCHA'=>'最後 CAPTCHA','Last Login'=>'最後登入','2FA Status'=>'兩步驟驗證狀態','Blocklist'=>'封鎖清單','Brute Force'=>'暴力破解','Complex'=>'複雜','Learn more<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> about the Firewall</span>'=>'深入了解<span class="wf-hidden-xs">防火牆</span>','Are you sure you want to restore the default Firewall settings? This will undo any custom changes you have made to the options on this page. If you have manually disabled any rules or added any custom allowlisted URLs, those changes will not be overwritten.'=>'您確定要還原防火牆的預設設定嗎？此操作將復原您在此頁面所做的所有自訂變更。若您曾手動停用任何規則或新增自訂允許清單網址，這些變更將不會被覆寫。','Scanned contents of %1$d additional files at %2$.2f per second'=>'已掃描 %1$d 個額外檔案的內容，速度為每秒 %2$.2f 個','Finalizing malware scan results'=>'完成惡意程式碼掃描結果','This file contains a URL that is currently listed on Wordfence\'s domain blocklist. The URL is: '=>'此檔案包含目前列於 Wordfence 網域封鎖清單中的網址。該網址為： ','File contains suspected malware URL: '=>'檔案包含疑似惡意程式碼網址： ','Asking Wordfence to check URLs against malware list.'=>'要求 Wordfence 將網址與惡意程式碼清單進行比對檢查。','This file is a PHP executable file and contains the word "eval" (without quotes) and the word "%s" (without quotes). The eval() function along with an encoding function like the one mentioned are commonly used by hackers to hide their code. If you know about this file you can choose to ignore it to exclude it from future scans. This file was detected because you have enabled HIGH SENSITIVITY scanning. This option is more aggressive than the usual scans, and may cause false positives.'=>'此檔案為 PHP 可執行檔，其中包含單詞「eval」（不含引號）與「%s」（不含引號）。 eval() 函式搭配如前述的編碼函式，常被駭客用於隱藏程式碼。若您知悉此檔案，可選擇忽略它以排除於未來掃描。此檔案被偵測到是因為您啟用了高敏感度掃描。此選項比常規掃描更為積極，可能導致誤判。','This file may contain malicious executable code: '=>'此檔案可能包含惡意可執行程式碼： ','Forking during malware scan (%s) to ensure continuity.'=>'惡意程式碼掃描期間進行分支處理 (%s)，以確保連續性。','The matched text in this file is: %s'=>'此檔案中的相符文字為：%s','File appears to be malicious or unsafe: %s'=>'檔案似乎具有惡意或不安全：%s','This file appears to be installed or modified by a hacker to perform malicious activity. If you know about this file you can choose to ignore it to exclude it from future scans.'=>'此檔案似乎是由駭客安裝或修改，用於執行惡意活動。若您知悉此檔案，可選擇忽略它，使其從未來的掃描中排除。','Resuming malware scan at rule %s.'=>'於規則 %s 處恢復惡意程式碼掃描。','This file was detected because you have enabled HIGH SENSITIVITY scanning. This option is more aggressive than the usual scans, and may cause false positives.'=>'此檔案被偵測到是因為您已啟用「高靈敏度」掃描。此選項比常規掃描更為積極，可能導致誤報。','This file was detected because you have enabled "Scan images, binary, and other files as if they were executable", which treats non-PHP files as if they were PHP code. This option is more aggressive than the usual scans, and may cause false positives.'=>'此檔案被偵測到是因為您已啟用「將圖片、二進位檔及其他檔案視為可執行檔進行掃描」選項，該功能會將非 PHP 檔案視為 PHP 程式碼進行處理。此選項比常規掃描更為嚴格，可能導致誤判。','Scanning contents: %1$s (Size: %2$s)'=>'掃描內容：%1$s（大小：%2$s）','Scanning contents: %1$s (Size: %2$s Mem: %3$s)'=>'掃描內容：%1$s (大小：%2$s 記憶體：%3$s)','Encountered file that is too large: %s - Skipping.'=>'遇到過大的檔案：%s - 略過。','No files remaining for malware scan.'=>'已無檔案可供惡意程式碼掃描。','Detected loop in malware scan, aborting.'=>'偵測到惡意程式碼掃描中的迴圈，中止掃描。','Backtrack limit is %d, reducing to 1000000'=>'回溯限制為 %d，將減少至 1000000','Wordfence received malformed attack signature patterns from the scanning server.'=>'Wordfence 從掃描伺服器接收到了格式錯誤的攻擊特徵碼模式。','Wordfence could not get the attack signature patterns from the scanning server.'=>'Wordfence 無法從掃描伺服器取得攻擊特徵碼模式。','Security token has expired. Click <a href="%s">here</a> to return to the scan page.'=>'安全性憑證已過期。請點擊<a href="%s">此處</a>返回掃描頁面。','File System Credentials Required'=>'需要檔案系統憑證','Back to Scan'=>'返回掃描','Last Updated: %s ago'=>'最後更新時間：%s 前','30 Days'=>'30 天','24 Hours'=>'24 小時','Blocked attack counts not available yet.'=>'遭封鎖的攻擊次數尚未提供。','Total Attacks Blocked:'=>'已封鎖的攻擊總數：','Disconnect'=>'中斷連線','Are you sure you want to disconnect your site from Wordfence Central?'=>'您確定要中斷網站與 Wordfence Central 的連線嗎？','Confirm Disconnect'=>'確認中斷連線','Disconnected by %1$s on %2$s'=>'由 %1$s 於 %2$s 中斷連線','Connected by %1$s on %2$s'=>'由 %1$s 於 %2$s 建立連線','How are these categorized?'=>'這些是如何分類的？','Month'=>'月','Week'=>'週','Today'=>'今日','Total'=>'總計','<span class="wf-hidden-xs">Block </span>Type'=>'<span class="wf-hidden-xs">封鎖</span>類型','No blocks have been recorded.'=>'尚未記錄任何封鎖。','Attacks Blocked for %s'=>'已封鎖針對 %s 的攻擊','Firewall Summary:'=>'防火牆摘要：','No Data Available During Learning Mode'=>'學習模式期間無可用資料','Learn more<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> about Scanning</span>'=>'深入了解<span class="wf-hidden-xs">掃描技術</span>','Are you sure you want 