ure contains a status percentage reminding you at a high level of what\'s enabled, disabled, or needing your attention. The Notifications section highlights actions you need to take.'=>'每個功能皆包含狀態百分比，概括提醒您哪些已啟用、停用或需要留意。通知區段會反白顯示您需要採取的動作。','Monitor Your Wordfence Protection'=>'監控您的 Wordfence 防護','We welcome your feedback and comments at <a href="mailto:feedback@wordfence.com">feedback@wordfence.com</a>. For a deeper dive on all of the changes, <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/blog/2018/01/introducing-wordfence-7/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">click here<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>.'=>'我們歡迎您透過 <a href="mailto:feedback@wordfence.com">feedback@wordfence.com</a> 提供意見與評論。欲深入了解所有變更，<a href="https://www.wordfence.com/blog/2018/01/introducing-wordfence-7/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">請點擊此處<span class="screen-reader-text"> (在新分頁開啟)</span></a>。','This update includes a number of significant interface changes. We\'d like to walk you through  some of them, but you can bypass the tour for a section at any time by closing the dialogs.'=>'本次更新包含多項重大的介面變更。我們想為您逐步說明其中的一部分，但您隨時可以透過關閉對話方塊  跳過該部分的導覽。','You have successfully updated to Wordfence %s'=>'您已成功更新至 Wordfence %s','You\'ll find this icon throughout the plugin. Clicking it will show you the options and features for each section of Wordfence. From the dashboard, you can find the <strong>Global Options</strong> for Wordfence such as alerts, automatic updates, and managing your site\'s Premium License.'=>'您會在整個外掛中看到此圖示。點擊它將顯示 Wordfence 各部分的選項與功能。在控制台中，您可以找到 Wordfence 的<strong>全球選項</strong>，如警示、自動更新，以及管理您網站的高級版授權。','Global Wordfence Options'=>'Wordfence 全球選項','Each feature contains a status that reminds you what\'s enabled, disabled or needs attention. The Notifications section will highlight actions you need to take.'=>'每個功能皆包含狀態提醒，讓您知道哪些已啟用、停用或需要留意。通知區段會反白顯示您需要採取的動作。','Easily Monitor Your Wordfence Protection'=>'輕鬆監控您的 Wordfence 防護','The Wordfence Dashboard provides valuable insights into the current state of your site\'s security. You\'ll find useful data summarized here as well as important status updates and notifications.'=>'Wordfence 控制台提供關於您網站目前安全性狀態的寶貴見解。您將在此處看到實用資料的摘要，以及重要的狀態更新與通知。','This is your Dashboard'=>'這是您的控制台','Manage global options for Wordfence such as alerts, premium status, and more'=>'管理 Wordfence 的全域選項，如警示、高級版狀態等','Global Options'=>'全球選項','Live Traffic, Whois Lookup, Import/Export, and Diagnostics'=>'即時流量、Whois 查詢、匯入/匯出及診斷','Tools'=>'工具','Learn more<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> about the Dashboard</span>'=>'了解更多<span class="wf-hidden-xs">關於控制台的資訊</span>','Wordfence Dashboard'=>'Wordfence 控制台','To clone one site\'s configuration to another, use the import/export tools below.'=>'若要將某個站點的設定複製到另一個站點，請使用以下匯入/匯出工具。','Connect Site'=>'連接網站','To connect your site your site to Wordfence Central, use the link below:'=>'要將您的網站連接到 Wordfence Central，請使用以下連結：','Disconnect Site'=>'斷開網站','Resume Installation'=>'恢復安裝','It looks like you\'ve tried to connect this site to Wordfence Central, but the installation did not finish.'=>'您似乎嘗試將此網站連線到 Wordfence Central，但安裝程序尚未完成。','Wordfence Central Installation Process'=>'Wordfence 中央安裝流程','Disconnect This Site'=>'中斷此網站連線','Activated - connected by %1$s on %2$s'=>'已啟用 - 由 %1$s 於 %2$s 建立連線','Wordfence Central Status'=>'Wordfence Central 狀態','Visit Wordfence Central'=>'造訪 Wordfence Central','Wordfence Central allows you to manage Wordfence on multiple sites from one location. It makes security monitoring and configuring Wordfence easier.'=>'Wordfence Central 讓您能從單一位置管理多個網站的 Wordfence。這讓安全性監控與設定 Wordfence 更為簡便。','Wordfence Central'=>'Wordfence Central','Redirecting back to Wordfence Central.'=>'重新導向回 Wordfence 中央。','Retrieving access token using authorization grant.'=>'使用授權授予方式檢索存取權杖。','Testing that Wordfence Central is able to communicate with this site.'=>'測試 Wordfence Central 能否與此網站進行通訊。','Testing public key authentication with Wordfence Central.'=>'使用 Wordfence Central 測試公開金鑰驗證。','Passing public key to Wordfence Central.'=>'將公鑰傳遞至 Wordfence Central。','Testing initial communication with Wordfence Central.'=>'測試與 Wordfence Central 的初始通訊。','Wordfence Network'=>'Wordfence 網路','NTP'=>'NTP','Should be: '=>'應為： ','We cannot read $_SERVER[%s]'=>'無法讀取 $_SERVER[%s]','This additional info may help you diagnose the issue. The response headers we received were:'=>'這些額外資訊可能有助於您診斷問題。收到的回應標頭如下：','wp_remote_post() test back to this server failed! Response was: '=>'連回此伺服器的 wp_remote_post() 測試失敗！回應為： ','This likely means that your hosting provider is blocking requests to noc1.wordfence.com or has set up a proxy that is not behaving itself.'=>'這很可能代表您的主機服務供應商正封鎖對 noc1.wordfence.com 的要求，或是設置了運作異常的代理伺服器。','wp_remote_post() test to noc1.wordfence.com failed! Response was: '=>'針對 noc1.wordfence.com 執行的 wp_remote_post() 測試失敗！回應為： ','Unknown'=>'未知','Unavailable'=>'無法使用','0660 - using default'=>'0660 - 使用預設值','%s - using template'=>'%s - 使用範本','%s - using constant'=>'%s - 使用常數','(default)'=>'(預設)','Serialized config writing'=>'序列化組態寫入','Basic config writing'=>'基本組態寫入','File "%s" is unwritable'=>'檔案「%s」無法寫入','No files writable'=>'無可寫入檔案','File "%s" is unreadable'=>'檔案「%s」無法讀取','File "%s" does not exist'=>'檔案「%s」不存在','No files readable'=>'無可讀取檔案','Normal'=>'正常','%d Job Overdue'=>'%d 項工作逾期','WordPress Time Zone'=>'WordPress 時區','TOTP Time Source'=>'TOTP 時間來源','NTP Time Offset'=>'NTP 時間位移','Wordfence Network Time Offset'=>'Wordfence 網路時間位移','Server Time'=>'伺服器時間','Wordfence Network Time'=>'Wordfence 網路時間','Server time accuracy and applied offsets.'=>'伺服器時間精確度與套用的位移 [cite: 9]。','IP(s) used by this server'=>'此伺服器使用的 IP 位址','Connecting back to this site'=>'連線回此網站','Connecting to Wordfence servers (https)'=>'連線至 Wordfence 伺服器 (https)','Ability to connect to the Wordfence servers and your own site.'=>'連線至 Wordfence 伺服器與自身網站的能力。','cURL libz Version'=>'cURL libz 版本','cURL SSL Version'=>'cURL SSL 版本','cURL Support Protocols'=>'cURL 支援的通訊協定','cURL Host'=>'cURL 主機','cURL Features Code'=>'cURL 功能程式碼','Checking for cURL support'=>'檢查 cURL 支援狀況','Checking OpenSSL version'=>'檢查 OpenSSL 版本','Checking for OpenSSL support'=>'檢查 OpenSSL 支援','Process Owner'=>'處理序擁有者','PHP version, important PHP extensions.'=>'PHP 版本與重要的 PHP 擴充功能 [cite: 16]。','Checking if MySQL user has <code>TRUNCATE</code> privilege'=>'檢查 MySQL 使用者是否具有 <code>TRUNCATE</code> 權限','Checking if MySQL user has <code>DROP</code> privilege'=>'檢查 MySQL 使用者是否具有 <code>DROP</code> 權限','Checking if MySQL user has <code>ALTER TABLE</code> privilege'=>'檢查 MySQL 使用者是否具有 <code>ALTER TABLE</code> 權限','Checking if MySQL user has <code>CREATE TABLE</code> privilege'=>'檢查 MySQL 使用者是否具有 <code>CREATE TABLE</code> 權限','Checking if MySQL user has <code>SELECT</code> privilege'=>'檢查 MySQL 使用者是否具有 <code>SELECT</code> 權限','Checking if MySQL user has <code>UPDATE</code> privilege'=>'檢查 MySQL 使用者是否具有 <code>UPDATE</code> 權限','Checking if MySQL user has <code>INSERT</code> privilege'=>'檢查 MySQL 使用者是否具有 <code>INSERT</code> 權限','Checking if MySQL user has <code>DELETE</code> privilege'=>'檢查 MySQL 使用者是否具有 <code>DELETE</code> 權限','Database Version'=>'資料庫版本','Database version and privileges.'=>'資料庫版本與權限。','Recently removed wflogs files'=>'最近移除的 wflogs 檔案','WAF File Permissions'=>'WAF 檔案權限','wordfence-waf.php path'=>'wordfence-waf.php 路徑','WAF subdirectory installation'=>'WAF 子目錄安裝','WAF log path'=>'WAF 記錄路徑','WAF auto prepend active'=>'WAF 自動前置功能已啟用','Current WAF configuration.'=>'目前的 WAF 組態 。','Checking serialized config reading/writing'=>'檢查序列化組態  讀取與寫入','Checking basic config reading/writing'=>'檢查基本組態讀寫功能','Ability to save Wordfence settings to the database.'=>'將 Wordfence 設定儲存至資料庫的功能。','Checking if web server can write to <code>~/wp-content/wflogs</code>'=>'檢查網頁伺服器能否寫入 <code>~/wp-content/wflogs</code>','Checking if web server can read from <code>~/wp-content/wflogs</code>'=>'檢查網頁伺服器能否讀取 <code>~/wp-content/wflogs</code>','Checking if web server can write to <code>~/plugins/wordfence</code>'=>'檢查網頁伺服器能否寫入 <code>~/plugins/wordfence</code>','Checking if web server can read from <code>~/plugins/wordfence</code>'=>'檢查網頁伺服器能否讀取 <code>~/plugins/wordfence</code>','Ability to read/write various files.'=>'讀取與寫入各類檔案的能力。','Cron Status'=>'Cron 狀態','GeoIP Version'=>'GeoIP 版本','Wordfence Version'=>'Wordfence 版本','General information about the Wordfence installation.'=>'關於 Wordfence 安裝的一般資訊。','Importing and exporting of options is available on the Tools page'=>'選項的匯入與匯出功能可在「工具」頁面中使用','Tool Options'=>'工具選項','Scan Options'=>'掃描選項','Blocking Options'=>'封鎖選項','These options are also available throughout the plugin pages, in the relevant sections. This page is provided for easier setup for experienced Wordfence users.'=>'這些選項亦可在插件頁面的相關區段中找到。本頁面旨在為經驗豐富的 Wordfence 用戶提供更便捷的設定方式。','Are you sure you want to restore the default settings? This will undo any custom changes you have made to the options on this page. If you have manually disabled any rules or added any custom allowlisted URLs, those changes will not be overwritten.'=>'確定要還原預設設定嗎 [cite: 126]？此操作將復原您在此頁面所做的所有自訂變更。若您曾手動停用任何規則或新增自訂允許清單網址，這些變更將不會被覆寫。','Enable Separate Prompt for Two Factor Code'=>'啟用雙重驗證碼獨立提示功能','Require Cellphone Sign-in for all Administrators'=>'要求所有管理員使用手機登入','Import Wordfence options from another site using a token'=>'使用代幣從其他網站匯入 Wordfence 設定選項','Export this site\'s Wordfence options for import on another site'=>'將此網站的 Wordfence 設定匯出，以便在其他網站上匯入','Maximum days to keep Live Traffic data'=>'即時流量 [cite: 12] 資料的最大保留天數','Amount of Live Traffic data to store (number of rows)'=>'需儲存的即時流量數據量（行數）','Browser user-agent to ignore'=>'瀏覽器用戶代理程式（需忽略）','List of comma separated IP addresses to ignore'=>'以逗號分隔的需忽略IP位址清單','List of comma separated usernames to ignore'=>'以逗號分隔的忽略使用者名稱清單','Don\'t log signed-in users with publishing access'=>'請勿記錄具備發佈權限的已登入使用者','Traffic logging mode (Live Traffic)'=>'交通記錄模式（即時交通）','Additional scan signatures'=>'額外的掃描簽名','Exclude files from scan that match these wildcard patterns'=>'排除符合以下通配符模式的檔案進行掃描','Maximum execution time for each scan stage'=>'每個掃描階段的最大執行時間','How much memory should Wordfence request when scanning'=>'Wordfence 在掃描時應要求多少記憶體？','Time limit that a scan can run in seconds'=>'掃描可執行的時間限制（以秒為單位）','Limit the number of issues sent in the scan results email'=>'限制掃描結果電子郵件中發送的問題數量','Use low resource scanning (reduces server load by lengthening the scan duration)'=>'使用低資源掃描（透過延長掃描時間來降低伺服器負載）','Scan images, binary, and other files as if they were executable'=>'掃描影像、二進位檔及其他檔案，如同它們是可執行檔','Scan files outside your WordPress installation'=>'掃描 WordPress 安裝目錄外的檔案','Monitor Web Application Firewall status'=>'監控網頁應用程式防火牆狀態','Monitor disk space'=>'監控磁碟空間','Check the strength of passwords'=>'檢查密碼強度','Scan for suspicious admin users created outside of WordPress'=>'掃描在 WordPress 外部建立的可疑管理員使用者','Scan for out of date, abandoned, and vulnerable plugins, themes, and WordPress versions'=>'掃描過期、棄用及存在漏洞的外掛程式、佈景主題與 WordPress 版本','Scan WordPress core, plugin, and theme options for known dangerous URLs and suspicious content'=>'掃描 WordPress 核心、外掛程式及佈景主題選項，以偵測已知的危險網址與可疑內容','Scan comments for known dangerous URLs and suspicious content'=>'掃描評論中的已知危險網址及可疑內容','Scan posts for known dangerous URLs and suspicious content'=>'掃描貼文以偵測已知危險網址及可疑內容','Scan file contents for malicious URLs'=>'掃描檔案內容以偵測惡意網址','Scan file contents for backdoors, trojans and suspicious code'=>'掃描檔案內容以偵測後門程式、木馬程式及可疑程式碼','Scan for signatures of known malicious files'=>'掃描已知惡意檔案的簽名','Scan wp-admin and wp-includes for files not bundled with WordPress'=>'掃描 wp-admin 和 wp-includes 目錄，尋找未隨 WordPress 一起打包的檔案','Scan plugin files against repository versions for changes'=>'掃描插件檔案與儲存庫版本以檢查變更','Scan theme files against repository versions for changes'=>'掃描主題檔案與儲存庫版本以檢查變更','Scan core files against repository versions for changes'=>'根據存放庫 [cite: 201] 版本掃描核心檔案 [cite: 207] 是否遭到變更','Scan for publicly accessible quarantined files'=>'掃描公開可存取的隔離檔案','Scan for publicly accessible configuration, backup, or log files'=>'掃描公開可存取的設定檔、備份檔或日誌檔','Scan for misconfigured How does Wordfence get IPs'=>'掃描錯誤設定的IP位址Wordfence如何取得IP位址','Check if this website IP is generating spam'=>'檢查此網站IP是否正在產生垃圾郵件','Check if this website is being &quot;Spamvertised&quot;'=>'檢查此網站是否正遭受「垃圾廣告」攻擊','Check if this website is on a domain blocklist'=>'檢查此網站是否在網域封鎖清單中','Scan Type'=>'掃描類型','Schedule Wordfence Scans'=>'排程 Wordfence 掃描','If user who is allowed to access the site views the relative URL ____ then set a cookie that will bypass country blocking in future in case that user hits the site from a blocked country'=>'若獲准存取網站的使用者瀏覽相對網址 ____，則設定一個Cookie，以便該使用者未來從受限國家存取網站時能繞過國家封鎖機制。','If user from a blocked country hits the relative URL ____ then redirect that user to ____ and set a cookie that will bypass all country blocking'=>'若來自受封鎖國家的用戶點擊相關網址 ____，則將該用戶重定向至 ____，並設定一個可繞過所有國家封鎖的 Cookie。','Block countries even if they are logged in'=>'即使已登入，仍需封鎖這些國家','URL to redirect blocked countries to'=>'將受限國家重定向至的網址','What to do when we block someone visiting from a blocked country'=>'當我們封鎖某個被禁止國家的訪客時該怎麼辦','Monitor background requests from an administrator\'s web browser for false positives (Admin Panel)'=>'監控管理員網頁瀏覽器發出的背景請求，以偵測誤報（管理員控制台）','Monitor background requests from an administrator\'s web browser for false positives (Front-end Website)'=>'監控管理員網頁瀏覽器中的背景請求，以防誤報（前端網站）','Web Application Firewall Allowlisted URLs'=>'網頁應用程式防火牆允許清單網址','How long is an IP address blocked when it breaks a rule'=>'違反規則時，IP位址會被封鎖多久？','If a human\'s pages not found (404s) exceed'=>'若人類的頁面未找到（404）超過','If a human\'s page views exceed'=>'若人類的頁面瀏覽量超過','If a crawler\'s pages not found (404s) exceed'=>'若爬蟲的頁面未找到（404）超過','If a crawler\'s page views exceed'=>'若爬蟲的頁面瀏覽量超過','If anyone\'s requests exceed'=>'若任何人的要求超過','How should we treat Google\'s crawlers'=>'我們該如何處理 Google 的檢檢索器 [cite: 127, 129]？','Enable Rate Limiting and Advanced Blocking'=>'啟用速率限制與進階封鎖功能','Participate in the Real-Time Wordfence Security Network'=>'參與即時 Wordfence 安全網絡','Check password strength on profile update'=>'在個人資料更新時檢查密碼強度','Custom text shown on block pages'=>'區塊頁面顯示的自訂文字','Block IPs who send POST requests with blank User-Agent and Referer'=>'封鎖發送帶有空白 User-Agent 和 Referer 的 POST 請求之 IP','Prevent discovery of usernames through "/?author=N" scans, the oEmbed API, the WordPress REST API, and WordPress XML Sitemaps'=>'防止使用者名稱透過「/?author=N」掃描、oEmbed API、WordPress REST API 及 WordPress XML 網站地圖被發現','Prevent users registering "admin" username if it doesn\'t exist'=>'若使用者名稱「admin」不存在，則禁止使用者註冊該名稱','Don\'t let WordPress reveal valid users in login errors'=>'請勿讓 WordPress 在登入錯誤訊息中透露有效使用者','Prevent the use of passwords leaked in data breaches'=>'防止使用在資料外洩事件中遭洩露的密碼','Enforce strong passwords'=>'強制執行強密碼','Immediately block the IP of users who try to sign in as these usernames'=>'立即封鎖嘗試以這些使用者名稱登入的 IP','Immediately lock out invalid usernames'=>'立即鎖定無效的使用者名稱','Amount of time a user is locked out'=>'使用者被鎖定的時間長度','Count failures over what time period'=>'在多長的時間週期內計算失敗次數','Lock out after how many forgot password attempts'=>'忘記密碼嘗試幾次後鎖定','Lock out after how many login failures'=>'登入失敗幾次後鎖定','Enable brute force protection'=>'啟用暴力密碼破解防護','Web Application Firewall Rules'=>'網頁應用程式防火牆規則','Ignored IP addresses for Wordfence Web Application Firewall alerting'=>'Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆警示忽略的 IP 位址','Immediately block IPs that access these URLs'=>'立即封鎖存取這些網址的 IP','Allowlisted IP addresses that bypass all rules'=>'可繞過所有規則的允許清單 IP 位址','Delay IP and Country blocking until after WordPress and plugins have loaded (only process firewall rules early)'=>'將 IP 與國家封鎖延遲至 WordPress 與外掛載入後執行 (僅早期處理防火牆規則)','Real-Time IP Blocklist'=>'即時 IP 封鎖清單','Web Application Firewall Protection Level'=>'網頁應用程式防火牆保護等級','Enable activity report widget on the WordPress dashboard'=>'在 WordPress 控制台啟用活動報告小工具','List of directories to exclude from recently modified file list'=>'排除在最近修改檔案清單之外的目錄清單','Enable email summary'=>'啟用電子郵件摘要','Maximum email alerts to send per hour'=>'每小時傳送警示郵件的最大數量','Alert me when there\'s a large increase in attacks detected on 