向至繞過網址','Advanced blocking in effect.'=>'進階封鎖已生效。','Exceeded the maximum number of page not found errors per minute for humans.'=>'已超過人類每分鐘的「找不到頁面」錯誤數上限。','Exceeded the maximum number of page requests per minute for humans.'=>'已超過人類每分鐘的頁面要求數上限。','Exceeded the maximum number of page not found errors per minute for a crawler.'=>'已超過檢索器每分鐘的「找不到頁面」錯誤數上限。','Exceeded the maximum number of requests per minute for crawlers.'=>'已超過檢索器 [cite: 4] 每分鐘的要求數上限。','Exceeded the maximum global requests per minute for crawlers or humans.'=>'檢索器  或人類每分鐘的全球要求數已超過上限。','<strong>WARNING: </strong> Your site is using a WordPress version (%1$s) that is no longer supported by Wordfence and needs to be updated. We recommend using the newest version of WordPress but will currently support WordPress versions as old as %2$s. Version checks are run regularly, so if you have successfully updated, you can dismiss this notice or check that the update has taken effect later.'=>'<strong>警告：</strong>您的網站正使用已不再受 Wordfence 支援的 WordPress 版本 (%1$s)，需要更新。建議使用最新版本的 WordPress，目前仍支援舊至 %2$s 的版本。系統會定期執行版本檢查，若已成功更新，您可以關閉此通知，或稍後確認更新是否生效。','Your site is using a WordPress version (%1$s) that is no longer supported by Wordfence and needs to be updated. We recommend using the newest version of WordPress but will currently support WordPress versions as old as %2$s. Version checks are run regularly, so if you have successfully updated, you can dismiss this notice or check that the update has taken effect later.'=>'您的網站正使用已不再受 Wordfence 支援的 WordPress 版本 (%1$s)，需要更新。建議使用最新版本的 WordPress，目前仍支援舊至 %2$s 的版本。系統會定期執行版本檢查，若已成功更新，您可以關閉此通知，或稍後確認更新是否生效。','<strong>WARNING: </strong> Your site is using a WordPress version (%1$s) that will no longer be supported by Wordfence in an upcoming release and needs to be updated. We recommend using the newest version of WordPress but will currently support WordPress versions as old as %2$s. Version checks are run regularly, so if you have successfully updated, you can dismiss this notice or check that the update has taken effect later.'=>'<strong>警告：</strong>您的網站正使用即將不被 Wordfence 支援的 WordPress 版本 (%1$s)，需要立即更新。建議使用最新版本的 WordPress，目前仍支援舊至 %2$s 的版本。系統會定期執行版本檢查，若已成功更新，您可以關閉此通知，或稍後確認更新是否生效。','Your site is using a WordPress version (%1$s) that will no longer be supported by Wordfence in an upcoming release and needs to be updated. We recommend using the newest version of WordPress but will currently support WordPress versions as old as %2$s. Version checks are run regularly, so if you have successfully updated, you can dismiss this notice or check that the update has taken effect later.'=>'您的網站正使用即將不被 Wordfence 支援的 WordPress 版本 (%1$s)，需要更新。建議使用最新版本的 WordPress，目前仍支援舊至 %2$s 的版本。系統會定期執行版本檢查，若已成功更新，您可以關閉此通知，或稍後確認更新是否生效。','WordPress version too old'=>'WordPress 版本過舊','<strong>WARNING: </strong> Your site is using a PHP version (%1$s) that is no longer supported by Wordfence and needs to be updated. We recommend using the newest version of PHP available but will currently support PHP versions as old as %2$s. Version checks are run regularly, so if you have successfully updated, you can dismiss this notice or check that the update has taken effect later.'=>'<strong>警告：</strong>您的網站正使用已不再受 Wordfence 支援的 PHP 版本 (%1$s)，需要更新。建議使用最新的 PHP 版本，目前仍支援最高至 %2$s 的舊版 PHP。系統會定期執行版本檢查，若已成功更新，您可以關閉此通知，或稍後確認更新是否生效。','Your site is using a PHP version (%1$s) that is no longer supported by Wordfence and needs to be updated. We recommend using the newest version of PHP available but will currently support PHP versions as old as %2$s. Version checks are run regularly, so if you have successfully updated, you can dismiss this notice or check that the update has taken effect later.'=>'您的網站正使用已不再受 Wordfence 支援的 PHP 版本 (%1$s)，需要更新。建議使用最新的 PHP 版本，但目前仍支援舊至 %2$s 的版本。系統會定期執行版本檢查，若已成功更新，您可以關閉此通知，或稍後確認更新是否生效。','<strong>WARNING: </strong> Your site is using a PHP version (%1$s) that will no longer be supported by Wordfence in an upcoming release and needs to be updated. We recommend using the newest version of PHP available but will currently support PHP versions as old as %2$s. Version checks are run regularly, so if you have successfully updated, you can dismiss this notice or check that the update has taken effect later.'=>'<strong>警告：</strong>您的網站正使用即將不被 Wordfence 支援的 PHP 版本 (%1$s)，需要更新。建議使用最新的 PHP 版本，但目前仍支援舊至 %2$s 的版本。系統會定期執行版本檢查，若已成功更新，您可以關閉此通知，或稍後確認更新是否生效。','Learn More: %s'=>'了解更多：%s','Your site is using a PHP version (%1$s) that will no longer be supported by Wordfence in an upcoming release and needs to be updated. We recommend using the newest version of PHP available but will currently support PHP versions as old as %2$s. Version checks are run regularly, so if you have successfully updated, you can dismiss this notice or check that the update has taken effect later.'=>'您的網站正使用即將不被 Wordfence 支援的 PHP 版本 (%1$s)，需要更新。建議使用最新的 PHP 版本，但目前仍支援舊至 %2$s 的版本。系統會定期執行版本檢查，若已成功更新，您可以關閉此通知，或稍後確認更新是否生效。','PHP version too old'=>'PHP 版本過舊','Wordfence scan failed because of license site URL conflict'=>'Wordfence 掃描失敗，原因是授權網站網址衝突','Scan can\'t continue - stored data not found after a fork.'=>'掃描無法繼續：分支後找不到儲存的資料。','Checking cronkey: %1$s (expecting %2$s)'=>'檢查 Cronkey：%1$s (應為 %2$s)','[none]'=>'[無]','[invalid]'=>'[無效]','The signature on the request to start a scan is invalid. Please try again.'=>'啟動掃描要求的簽章無效。請再試一次。','Invalid response received from Wordfence Central when fetching token.'=>'從 Wordfence Central 擷取權杖  時收到無效回應。','Invalid response received from Wordfence Central when fetching nonce.'=>'從 Wordfence Central 擷取單次有效隨機碼  時收到無效回應。','Wordfence Central secret key has not been created yet.'=>'Wordfence Central 的秘密金鑰尚未建立。','Wordfence Central site ID has not been created yet.'=>'Wordfence Central 網站 ID 尚未建立。','Unable to authenticate with Wordfence Central.'=>'無法透過 Wordfence Central 進行驗證。','HTTP %1$d received from Wordfence Central: %2$s'=>'從 Wordfence 中央伺服器接收的 HTTP %1$d：%2$s','Your site is now using the legacy two-factor authentication system.'=>'您的網站目前正在使用舊版雙重驗證系統。','Legacy Two-Factor Authentication Active'=>'傳統雙因素驗證已啟用','Revert'=>'還原','All two-factor authentication settings and users\' codes will revert to your older settings. If any users had set up two-factor authentication after the update, they will no longer have 2FA enabled until you switch to the new version again.'=>'所有雙重驗證設定及用戶驗證碼將恢復至舊版設定。若任何用戶在更新後啟用雙重驗證，在您重新切換至新版之前，其雙重驗證功能將保持停用狀態。','Revert back to legacy two-factor authentication?'=>'恢復使用舊版雙重驗證？','Automatic migration of the 2FA-enabled accounts failed. Please verify that your server is reachable via the internet and try again.'=>'已啟用雙重驗證的帳戶自動遷移失敗。請確認您的伺服器可透過網際網路連線，並重新嘗試。','Migration Failed'=>'遷移失敗','One or more users with two-factor authentication active are using SMS, which is unsupported in the new login security module. Please either deactivate two-factor authentication for those users or change them to use an authenticator app prior to migration.'=>'一位或多位啟用雙重驗證的使用者正在使用簡訊驗證，此方式不適用於新版登入安全模組。請於遷移前為這些使用者停用雙重驗證功能，或將其驗證方式切換為驗證程式應用程式。','Migration Cannot Proceed'=>'遷移無法繼續','Go To New 2FA'=>'前往新的雙重驗證','Your site is now using the new login security module and two-factor authentication. Before logging out, we recommend testing your login in a different browser or a private/incognito window. If any plugins or your theme cause conflicts with logging in, you can revert to the old 2FA method.'=>'您的網站現已啟用新版登入安全模組及雙重驗證功能。建議您在登出前，先於其他瀏覽器或隱私/無痕視窗測試登入功能。若發現任何外掛程式或佈景主題導致登入衝突，可隨時切換回舊版雙重驗證方式。','New Two-Factor Authentication Active'=>'全新雙重驗證功能已啟用','Switch'=>'切換','Migrate'=>'遷移','Use the buttons below to migrate to the new two-factor authentication system or switch without migration. Migration will copy all existing authenticator-based user activations over to the new system while switching will use only users already set up in the new system. Existing SMS-based two-factor authentication activations must be disabled prior to migration.'=>'請使用下方按鈕遷移至新的雙重驗證系統，或選擇無需遷移的切換方式。遷移操作將複製所有現有基於驗證器的用戶啟用設定至新系統；切換操作則僅使用已在新系統中設定的用戶。現有的基於簡訊的雙重驗證啟用設定必須在遷移前停用。','Migrate or switch to new two-factor authentication?'=>'遷移或切換至新的雙重驗證？','Revert to Legacy 2FA'=>'恢復使用舊版雙重驗證','If you have a conflict with the new 2FA method, you can temporarily switch back to the Legacy version.'=>'若您與新的雙重驗證方法發生衝突，可暫時切換回舊版版本。','Legacy support for SMS-based two-factor authentication is being phased out, as it is less secure than using a modern authenticator app.'=>'基於簡訊的雙重驗證功能將逐步停用，因其安全性低於現代驗證應用程式。','2FA Mode: Normal'=>'雙重驗證模式：正常','No users currently have cellphone sign-in enabled.'=>'目前沒有任何用戶啟用手機登入功能。','Activate'=>'啟動','Code'=>'代碼','Enter activation code:'=>'輸入啟用代碼：','Cellphone Sign-in Enabled'=>'手機登入功能已啟用','Authenticator'=>'驗證器','Phone (%s)'=>'電話號碼 (%s)','Two-Factor Authentication Users'=>'雙重驗證使用者','+1 (000) 000 0000'=>'+1 (000) 000 0000','Send code to a phone number:'=>'將代碼發送至手機號碼：','Use authenticator app'=>'使用驗證器應用程式','Enter username to enable Two-Factor Authentication for'=>'輸入使用者名稱以啟用雙重驗證','Enable Two-Factor Authentication'=>'啟用雙重驗證','<strong>Note:</strong> Two-Factor Authentication is disabled when the option "Enable Brute Force Protection" is off.'=>'<strong>注意：</strong>當「啟用暴力破解防護」選項關閉時，雙重驗證功能將被停用。','Are you sure you want to restore the default Two-Factor Authentication settings? This will undo any custom changes you have made to the options on this page. If you have configured any users to use two-factor authentication, they will not be changed.'=>'您確定要還原雙重驗證的預設設定嗎？此操作將撤銷您在此頁面所做的所有自訂變更。若您已為任何使用者設定雙重驗證，其設定將不受影響。','With Two-Factor Authentication enabled, an attacker needs to know your username, password <em>and</em> have control of your phone to log in to your site. We recommend you enable Two-Factor Authentication for all Administrator level accounts.'=>'啟用雙重驗證後，攻擊者必須同時掌握您的使用者名稱、密碼<em>，並</em>控制您的手機，才能登入您的網站。我們建議您為所有管理員級別帳戶啟用雙重驗證。','Used by banks, government agencies, and military worldwide, two-factor authentication is one of the most secure forms of remote system authentication available. With it enabled, an attacker needs to know your username, password, <em>and</em> have control of your phone to log into your site. Upgrade to Premium now to enable this powerful feature.'=>'雙重驗證技術被全球銀行、政府機構及軍事單位廣泛採用，是當前最安全的遠端系統驗證方式之一。啟用此功能後，攻擊者必須同時掌握您的使用者名稱、密碼，<em>並</em>控制您的手機，才能登入您的網站。立即升級至高級版，啟用這項強大功能。','Take Login Security to the next level with Two-Factor Authentication'=>'透過雙重驗證，將登入安全性提升至全新境界','Switch to New 2FA'=>'切換至新版雙重驗證','Two-factor authentication is using legacy support, which enables SMS-based codes but is less compatible. An improved interface and use by non-administrators is available by activating the new login security module.'=>'雙重驗證目前採用舊版支援機制，此機制雖可啟用簡訊驗證碼功能，但相容性較低。若啟用新版登入安全模組，即可獲得改良版介面，並允許非管理員使用者進行操作。','2FA Mode: Legacy'=>'雙重驗證模式：傳統模式','Learn more<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> about Two-Factor Authentication</span>'=>'深入了解<span class="wf-hidden-xs">雙重驗證</span>','Two-Factor Authentication'=>'雙重驗證','Your options have been saved. However we tried to verify your license key with the Wordfence servers and received an error: '=>'您的選項已儲存。不過，我們嘗試透過 Wordfence 伺服器驗證您的授權金鑰時收到錯誤： ','Your options have been saved. However we noticed you changed your license key, and we tried to verify it with the Wordfence servers but received an error: '=>'您的選項已儲存。不過，我們注意到您變更了授權金鑰，我們嘗試透過 Wordfence 伺服器進行驗證，但收到錯誤： ','Your options have been saved, but you left your license key blank, so we tried to get you a free license key from the Wordfence servers. There was a problem fetching the free key: '=>'您的選項已儲存，但您未填寫授權金鑰，因此我們嘗試從 Wordfence 伺服器為您取得免費授權金鑰。取得免費金鑰時發生問題： ','A wildcard cannot be used to exclude all files from the scan.'=>'萬用字元  無法用於排除所有檔案的掃描。','An empty license key was entered.'=>'輸入了空的授權金鑰 。','The following IPs/ranges you selected to trust as proxies are not valid: '=>'您選取要信任為 Proxy 的下列 IP/範圍無效： ','The following IPs you selected to ignore in live traffic reports are not valid: '=>'您在即時流量報告中選取要忽略的下列 IP 無效： ','The following users you selected to ignore in live traffic reports are not valid on this system: '=>'您在即時流量報告中選取要忽略的下列使用者在此系統上無效： ','Please make sure you separate your IP addresses with commas or newlines. The following allowlisted IP addresses are invalid: '=>'請確保使用逗號或換行符號分隔您的 IP 位址。下列允許清單中的 IP 位址無效： ','"%s" is not a valid regular expression.'=>'「%s」不是有效的規則運算式 。','The following emails are invalid: '=>'下列電子郵件地址無效： ','Unknown firewall mode.'=>'未知的防火牆模式。','The grace period end time must be in the future.'=>'寬限期 [cite: 201] 結束時間必須設定在未來。','To preserve the integrity of your website we are not running Wordfence auto-update.
You are running the LiteSpeed web server which has been known to cause a problem with Wordfence auto-update.
Please go to your website now and make a minor change to your .htaccess to fix this.
You can find out how to make this change at:
%s

Alternatively you can disable auto-update on your website to stop receiving this message and upgrade Wordfence manually.
'=>'為維護網站完整性，我們暫停執行 Wordfence 自動更新功能。
您目前使用的 LiteSpeed 網頁伺服器已知會與 Wordfence 自動更新產生相容性問題。
請立即前往您的網站，對 .htaccess 檔案進行微調以解決此問題。
您可參閱以下連結了解操作方式：
%s

您亦可選擇停用網站的自動更新功能，停止接收此通知，並手動升級 Wordfence。
','Wordfence Upgrade not run. Please modify your .htaccess'=>'Wordfence 升級程序未執行。請修改您的 .htaccess 檔案。','Increased Attack Rate'=>'攻擊率增加','A user with username "%1$s" tried to sign in to your WordPress site. Access was denied because the password being used exists on lists of passwords leaked in data breaches. Attackers use such lists to break into sites and install malicious code. Please change or reset the password (%2$s) to reactivate this account. Learn More: %3$s'=>'使用者名稱為「%1$s」的用戶嘗試登入您的 WordPress 網站。由於該密碼存在於資料外洩事件中洩漏的密碼清單，系統已拒絕其存取權限。攻擊者常利用此類清單入侵網站並植入惡意程式碼。請變更或重設密碼 (%2$s) 以重新啟用此帳戶。了解更多：%3$s','User login blocked for insecure password'=>'使用者登入因密碼安全性不足而遭封鎖','A non-admin user with username "%s" signed in to your WordPress site.'=>'一名非管理員用戶，其用戶名為「%s」，已登入您的 WordPress 網站。','User login'=>'使用者登入','A user with username "%s" who has administrator access signed in to your WordPress site.'=>'一位使用者名稱為「%s」且具備管理員權限的使用者已登入您的 WordPress 網站。','Admin Login'=>'管理員登入','User locked out from signing in'=>'使用者被鎖定無法登入','The duration of the lockout is %s.'=>'鎖定狀態的持續時間為 %s。','A user with IP address %1$s has been locked out from signing in or using the password recovery form for the following reason: %2$s.'=>'IP 位址為 %1$s 的使用者因下列原因遭鎖定，無法登入或使用密碼重設表單：%2$s。','Someone tried to recover the password for user with email address: %s'=>'有人嘗試為電子郵件地址為 %s 的使用者重設密碼。','Password recovery attempted'=>'嘗試密碼重設','A user with username "%s" deactivated Wordfence on your WordPress site.'=>'使用者名稱為「%s」的用戶已停用您 WordPress 網站上的 Wordfence 防護功能。','Wordfence Deactivated'=>'Wordfence 已停用','A user with username "%s" deactivated the Wordfence Web Application Firewall on your WordPress site.'=>'使用者名稱為「%s」的用戶已停用您 WordPress 網站上的 Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆。','Wordfence WAF Deactivated'=>'Wordfence WAF 已停用','Your Wordfence installation has been upgraded to version %s'=>'您的 Wordfence 安裝已升級至版本 %s','Wordfence Upgraded to version %s'=>'Wordfence 已升級至版本 %s','Blocking IP %s'=>'封鎖 IP %s','The duration of the block is %s.'=>'區塊的持續時間為 %s。','The reason is: "%s".'=>'原因如下：「%s」。','Wordfence has blocked IP address %s.'=>'Wordfence 已封鎖 IP 位址 %s。','All blocking rules you create will show here. You can manage them as well as remove or modify them from the same location.'=>'所有您建立的封鎖規則都會顯示於此。您可以在同一個位置管理、移除或修改這些規則。','All of the blocking rules you create are now in one central location. Simply choose the block type and enter the details for the rule you want to create. Premium users have access to advanced country blocking options, found via the <strong>Options</strong> link.'=>'您建立的所有封鎖規則現在都集中在單一位置。只需選取封鎖類型並輸入要建立的規則詳情即可。高級版使用者可以透過<strong>選項</strong>連結存取進階國家封鎖選項。','Here\'s where you\'ll see all the blocking rules you\'ve created. You can also manage them as well as remove or modify them from this table.'=>'您可以在此處看到所有建立的封鎖規則。您也可以從此表格管理、移除或修改這些規則。','Manage Blocking Rules'=>'管理封鎖規則','All of your blocking rules are in one central location. Choose the Block Type, then enter the details for the rule. Once it has been added, you\'ll see it saved as a rule for your site.'=>'您所有的封鎖規則都集中在單一位置。選取封鎖類型，然後輸入規則詳情。加入後，您會看到它被儲存為網站的規則。','Blocking Builder'=>'封鎖建構器','Wordfence lets you take control of protecting your site with powerful blocking features. Block traffic based on IP, IP range, hostname, browser, or referrer. Country blocking is available for Premium customers.'=>'Wordfence 讓您能透過強大的封鎖功能掌控網站保護。可根據 IP、IP 範圍、主機名稱、瀏覽器或參照網址封鎖流量。高級版客戶可使用國家封鎖功能。','Edit Blocking Rule'=>'編輯封鎖規則','Create a Blocking Rule'=>'建立封鎖規則','More Information'=>'更多資訊','<strong>Note:</strong> The GeoIP database that is required for country blocking has been updated to a new format. This new format requires sites to run PHP 5.4 or newer, and this site is on PHP %s. To ensure country blocking continues functioning, please update PHP.'=>'<strong>注意：</strong>國家封鎖所需的 GeoIP 資料庫已更新為新格式。此新格式要求網站執行 PHP 5.4 或更新版本，而本網站目前使用 PHP %s。為確保國家封鎖功能持續運作，請更新 PHP 版本。','Turn On'=>'開啟','<strong>Note:</strong> Blocking is disabled when the option "Enable Rate Limiting and Advanced Blocking" is off.'=>'<strong>注意：</strong>當「啟用速率限制與進階封鎖」選項關閉時，封鎖功能會被停用。','SUM_KILLED:A request was received to stop the previous scan from Wordfence Central.'=>'SUM_KILLED：收到來自 Wordfence Central 的請求，要求停止先前掃描。','Scan stop request received from Wordfence Central.'=>'收到來自 Wordfence Central 的掃描停止請求。','Wordfence scan starting at %s from Wordfence Central'=>'Wordfence 掃描將於 %s 從 Wordfence Central 開始執行','Number of scan results to return.'=>'要返回的掃描結果數量。','Offset of scan results to return.'=>'掃描結果的偏移量以返回。','Scan result group or all results.'=>'掃描結果群組或所有結果。','Authorization header format is invalid.'=>'授權標頭格式無效。','Token is invalid.'=>'權杖無效 。','Admin user with this email address not found.'=>'找不到此電子郵件地址的系統管理員使用者。','Email address is invalid.'=>'電子郵件地址無效。','Signature is invalid.'=>'簽名無效。','Nonce is invalid.'=>'單次有效隨機碼無效 。','Site ID is invalid.'=>'網站識別碼無效。','Nonce format is invalid.'=>'隨機數格式無效。','Data is invalid.'=>'資料無效。','Site is not connected to Wordfence Central.'=>'此網站未連接到 Wordfence 中央伺服器。','Validation error: \'fields\' parameter is empty or not an array.'=>'驗證錯誤：&#x27;fields&#x27; 參數為空或非陣列。','A server error occurred while saving the configuration: %s'=>'儲存設定時發生伺服器錯誤：%s','Specific config options to set.'=>'需設定的特定配置選項。','Specific config options to return.'=>'需返回的特定設定選項。','Importing and exporting of options has moved to the Tools page'=>'選項的匯入與匯出功能已移至「工具」頁面','Import/Export Options'=>'匯入/匯出選項','Review Payment Method'=>'檢閱付款方式','in 1 day'=>'1 天後','Update Payment Method'=>'更新付款方式','License renews %s'=>'授權將於 %s 續訂','in %d days'=>'%d 天後','tomorrow'=>'明天','today'=>'今天','Payment Method Invalid'=>'付款方式無效','Payment Method Missing'=>'缺少付款方式','Payment Method Expired'=>'付款方式已過期','Payment Method Expiring'=>'付款方式即將到期','Auto-renew is disabled'=>'自動續訂已停用','As a free Wordfence user, you are currently using the Community version of the Threat Defense Feed. Premium users are protected by additional firewall rules and malware signatures. Upgrade to Premium today to improve your protection.'=>'身為 Wordfence 免費版使用者，您目前使用的是威脅防禦資訊的社群版。高級版使用者享有額外的防火牆規則與惡意程式碼特徵碼保護。立即升級至高級版以提升您的保護能力。','Renew License'=>'續訂授權','License is expired'=>'授權已過期','Premium Protection Disabled'=>'高級版防護已停用','Reset License'=>'重設授權','License already in use'=>'授權已在使用中','Premium License Conflict'=>'高級版授權衝突','Detection of security issues'=>'安全性問題偵測','https://www.wordfence.com/help/dashboard/#dashboard-status'=>'https://www.wordfence.com/help/dashboard/#dashboard-status','Firewall Status'=>'防火牆狀態','Manage Firewall'=>'管理防火牆','Protection from known and emerging threats'=>'防範已知與新興威脅','WAF Currently in Learning Mode'=>'WAF 目前處於學習模式','Firewall'=>'防火牆','Learn more<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> about Global Options</span>'=>'了解更多<span class="wf-hidden-xs">關於全球選項的資訊</span>','Are you sure you want to restore the default global settings? This will undo any custom changes you have made to the options on this page. Your configured license key and alert emails will not be changed.'=>'確定要還原預設的全球設定嗎？此操作將撤銷您在此頁面所做的所有自訂變更。您組態的授權金鑰與警示電子郵件將不會變動。','Back<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> to Dashboard</span>'=>'返回<span class="wf-hidden-xs">控制台</span>','Wordfence Global Options'=>'Wordfence 全球選項','No longer an administrator for this site? <a href="%s" target="_blank">Click here</a> to stop receiving security alerts.'=>'不再是此網站的管理員？<a href="%s" target="_blank">點擊此處</a>停止接收安全警報。','Auth grant not found.'=>'找不到授權。','Invalid response from Wordfence Central.'=>'來自 Wordfence Central 的無效回應。','Access token not found.'=>'找不到存取權杖 。','Invalid response from Wordfence Central. Parameter %s not found in response.'=>'來自 Wordfence Central 的無效回應。回應中找不到參數 %s。','Invalid response from Wordfence Central: %s'=>'來自 Wordfence Central 的無效回應：%s','Auth grant is invalid.'=>'授權無效。','Dismiss'=>'關閉','Click here to configure'=>'點擊此處進行組態  設定','To make your site as secure as possible, take a moment to optimize the Wordfence Web Application Firewall:'=>'為了讓網站盡可能安全，請花點時間優化 Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆：','Uninstallation Failed'=>'解除安裝失敗','Uninstallation Complete'=>'解除安裝完成','Unable to Uninstall'=>'無法解除安裝','Try Again'=>'再試一次','Retrying Failed.'=>'重試失敗。','Extended Protection Mode has not been disabled. This may be because <code>auto_prepend_file</code> is configured somewhere else or the value is still cached by PHP.'=>'擴展保護模式尚未停用。這可能是因為 <code>auto_prepend_file</code> 在其他位置有組態設定，或 PHP 仍保留其快取 [cite: 2]。','Waiting for Changes'=>'等待變更','Waiting for it to take effect. This may take up to %s.'=>'正在等待生效。這可能需要長達 %s 的時間。','Any previous value for <code>auto_prepend_file</code> will need to be re-enabled manually if still needed.'=>'若仍需要，任何先前的 <code>auto_prepend_file</code> 數值都必須手動重新啟用。','The <code>auto_prepend_file</code> setting has been successfully removed from <code>.htaccess</code> and <code>.user.ini</code>. Once this change takes effect, Extended Protection Mode will be disabled.'=>'已成功從 <code>.htaccess</code> 與 <code>.user.ini</code> 移除 <code>auto_prepend_file</code> 設定。此變更生效後，擴展保護模式將被停用。','Once you have entered credentials, click Continue to complete uninstallation.'=>'輸入認證後，點擊「繼續」以完成解除安裝。','Installation Failed'=>'安裝失敗','Installation Successful'=>'安裝成功','Manual Installation Instructions'=>'手動安裝說明','Filesystem Permission Error'=>'檔案系統權限錯誤','Once you have entered credentials, click Continue to complete the setup.'=>'輸入認證後，點擊「繼續」以完成設定。','Filesystem Credentials Required'=>'需要檔案系統認證 [cite: 3]','A valid server configuration was not provided.'=>'未提供有效的伺服器組態 。','<strong>ERROR</strong>: Incorrect username or password.'=>'<strong>錯誤</strong>：使用者名稱或密碼不正確。','Invalid email address provided'=>'提供的電子郵件地址無效','No longer an administrator for this site? Click here to stop receiving security alerts: %s'=>'不再是此網站的管理員 [cite: 1]？點擊此處停止接收安全性警示：%s','User location: '=>'使用者位置： ','User hostname: %s
'=>'使用者主機名稱：%s
','User IP: %s
'=>'使用者 IP：%s
','You may wait for the next automatic attempt or log into the parent site to manually update by clicking the "Manually Refresh Rules" button below the Rules list.'=>'您可以等待下次自動嘗試，或登入上層網站點擊規則清單下方的「手動重新整理規則」按鈕進行手動更新。','You may wait for the next automatic attempt at %s or log into the parent site to manually update by clicking the "Manually Refresh Rules" button below the Rules list.'=>'您可以等待在 %s 的下次自動嘗試，或登入上層 [cite: 9] 網站點擊規則清單下方的「手動重新整理規則」按鈕進行手動更新。','You may wait for the next automatic attempt or try to <a href="%s">Manually Update</a> by clicking the "Manually Refresh Rules" button below the Rules list.'=>'您可以等待下次自動嘗試，或點擊規則清單下方的「手動重新整理規則」按鈕嘗試<a href="%s">手動更新</a>。','You may wait for the next automatic attempt at %1$s or try to <a href="%2$s">Manually Update</a> by clicking the "Manually Refresh Rules" button below the Rules list.'=>'您可以等待在 %1$s 的下次自動嘗試，或點擊規則清單下方的「手動重新整理規則」按鈕嘗試<a href="%2$s">手動更新</a>。','The last rules update for the Wordfence Web Application Firewall was unsuccessful. The last successful update check was %s, so this site may be missing new rules added since then.'=>'Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆的最後一次規則更新不成功。上次成功的更新檢查是在 %s，因此網站可能缺少在那之後新增的規則。','The Wordfence Web Application Firewall is in read-only mode.'=>'Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆目前處於唯讀模式。','The Wordfence Web Application Firewall needs a configuration update.'=>'Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆需要更新組態 。','The Wordfence Web Application Firewall cannot run.'=>'Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆無法執行。','Reload'=>'重新載入','An invalid file was requested for deletion.'=>'要求刪除的檔案無效。','Could not delete file because that issue does not appear to be a file related issue.'=>'無法刪除檔案，因為該問題似乎與檔案無關。','Could not delete file because we could not find that issue.'=>'無法刪除檔案，因為找不到該問題。','Invalid bulk operation selected'=>'選取了無效的批次操作 [cite: 2]','We didn\'t repair anything and no errors were found.'=>'未修復任何內容，也未發現任何錯誤。','We didn\'t delete anything and no errors were found.'=>'未刪除任何內容，也未發現任何錯誤。','Nothing done'=>'未執行任何操作','We could not repair any of the files you selected. We encountered the following errors: %s'=>'無法修復選取的任何檔案。遇到下列錯誤：%s','We could not delete any of the files you selected. We encountered the following errors: %s'=>'無法刪除選取的任何檔案。遇到下列錯誤：%s','Could not repair files'=>'無法修復檔案','Could not delete files'=>'無法刪除檔案','Repaired %d files successfully. No errors were encountered.'=>'成功修復 %d 個檔案，未遇到任何錯誤。','Deleted %d files successfully. No errors were encountered.'=>'成功刪除 %d 個檔案，未遇到任何錯誤。','Repaired %d files successfully'=>'成功修復 %d 個檔案','Deleted %d files successfully'=>'成功刪除 %d 個檔案','Repaired %1$d files but we encountered the following errors with other files: %2$s'=>'已修復 %1$d 個檔案，但在處理其他檔案時遇到下列錯誤：%2$s','Deleted %1$d files but we encountered the following errors with other files: %2$s'=>'已刪除 %1$d 個檔案，但在處理其他檔案時遇到下列錯誤：%2$s','Repaired some files with errors'=>'已修復部分有錯誤的檔案','Deleted some files with errors'=>'已刪除部分有錯誤的檔案','We could not write to that file. You may not have permission to modify files on your WordPress server.'=>'無法寫入該檔案。您可能沒有修改 WordPress 伺服器上檔案的權限。','We could not write to %1$s. The error was: %2$s'=>'無法寫入 %1$s。錯誤為：%2$s','You don\'t have permission to repair %s. You need to either fix the file manually using FTP or change the file permissions and ownership so that your web server has write access to repair the file.'=>'您沒有權限修復 %s。您需要透過 FTP  手動修復檔案，或變更檔案權限與擁有權 [cite: 18]，讓網頁伺服器具備寫入權限。','An invalid file %s was specified for repair.'=>'指定了無效的檔案 %s 進行修復。','We could not retrieve the original file of %s to do a repair.'=>'無法擷取 [cite: 16] %s 的原始檔案以進行修復。','Could not delete file %1$s. Error was: %2$s'=>'無法刪除檔案 %1$s。錯誤為：%2$s','Deleting an infected wp-config.php file must be done outside of Wordfence. The wp-config.php file contains your database credentials, which you will need to restore normal site operations. Your site will NOT function once the wp-config.php file has been deleted.'=>'刪除受感染的 wp-config.php 檔案必須在 Wordfence 以外進行。wp-config.php 檔案包含您的資料庫憑證，恢復網站運作需要這些憑證。一旦刪除此檔案，網站將無法運作。','The scan has failed because we received an unexpected response from the Wordfence servers. This may be a temporary error, though some sites may need adjustments to run scans reliably.'=>'掃描失敗，因為收到 Wordfence 伺服器的非預期回應。這可能是暫時性錯誤，但部分網站可能需要調整設定。','The scan has failed because we were unable to contact the Wordfence servers. Some sites may need adjustments to run scans reliably.'=>'掃描失敗，因為無法聯絡 Wordfence 伺服器。部分網站可能需要調整才能穩定執行掃描。','Scans are not functional because SSL is unavailable.'=>'由於 SSL 無法使用，掃描功能無法運作。','A scan stage has failed to start. This is often because the site either cannot make outbound requests or is blocked from connecting to itself.'=>'掃描階段啟動失敗。這通常是因為網站無法發出對外要求 ，或是被阻斷與自身的連線。','The previous scan has terminated because we detected an update occurring during the scan.'=>'先前的掃描已終止，因為偵測到掃描期間有更新動作。','The previous scan has terminated because the time limit of %s was reached. This limit can be customized on the options page.'=>'先前的掃描因達到 %s 的時限而終止。您可以在選項頁面自訂此限制。','The previous scan has failed. Some sites may need adjustments to run scans reliably.'=>'先前的掃描已失敗。部分網站可能需要進行調整，才能穩定執行掃描。','Cancel Scan'=>'取消掃描','Click here for steps you can try.'=>'點擊此處查看您可以嘗試的步驟。','The current scan looks like it has failed. Its last status update was <span id="wf-scan-failed-time-ago">%s</span> ago. You may continue to wait in case it resumes or stop and restart the scan. Some sites may need adjustments to run scans reliably.'=>'目前的掃描似乎已失敗。上次狀態更新是在 <span id="wf-scan-failed-time-ago">%s</span> 前。您可以繼續等待掃描恢復，或停止並重新開始掃描。部分網站可能需要調整設定才能穩定執行掃描。','Last scan failed'=>'上次掃描失敗','Scan completed on %s'=>'掃描已於 %s 完成','Idle'=>'閒置','Manual permanent block by admin'=>'管理員 [cite: 1] 手動永久封鎖','No configuration changes were provided to save.'=>'未提供要儲存的組態變更。','An error occurred while saving the configuration.'=>'儲存組態時發生錯誤。','Errors occurred while saving the configuration.'=>'儲存設定時發生錯誤。','Errors occurred while saving the configuration: %s'=>'儲存設定時發生錯誤：%s','An error occurred while saving the configuration: %s'=>'儲存設定時發生錯誤：%s','No configuration section was provided.'=>'未提供組態區段。','An unknown configuration section was provided.'=>'提供了未知的組態  區段。','No license was provided to install.'=>'未提供可供安裝的授權。','We received an error while trying to activate the license with the Wordfence servers: '=>'我們嘗試透過 Wordfence 伺服器啟用授權時收到錯誤： ','The Wordfence activation server returned an unexpected response. Please try again.'=>'Wordfence 啟用伺服器傳回非預期的回應。請再試一次。','The license provided is already in use on another site.'=>'提供的授權已在其他網站使用。','The license key entered is not in a valid format. It must contain only numbers and the letters A-F.'=>'輸入的授權金鑰格式無效。金鑰僅可包含數字及字母 A-F。','No blocks were provided.'=>'未提供任何區塊 [cite: 3]。','No block parameters were provided.'=>'未提供封鎖參數。','An error occurred while creating the block.'=>'建立封鎖時發生錯誤。','Permanent'=>'永久','Hostname'=>'主機名稱','Referrer'=>'參照來源','User Agent'=>'使用者代理程式','IP Range'=>'IP 範圍','Site Except Login'=>'除登入外的網站內容','Login Only'=>'僅限登入','Entire Site'=>'整個網站','%d Countries'=>'%d 個國家','1 Country'=>'1 個國家','All Countries'=>'所有國家','Wordfence Activity Log'=>'Wordfence 活動記錄','No Ignored Issues'=>'無已忽略的問題','## Ignored Issues (%d total)'=>'## 已忽略的問題 (總計 %d 個)','## New Issues (%d total)'=>'## 新增問題 (總計 %d 個)','# Scan Issues'=>'# 掃描問題','Unknown two-factor authentication mode.'=>'未知的兩步驟驗證 [cite: 1] 模式。','We could not generate a verification code.'=>'無法產生驗證碼。','Could not generate verification code: %s'=>'無法產生驗證碼：%s','Could not contact Wordfence servers to generate a verification code: %s'=>'無法聯絡 Wordfence 伺服器以產生驗證碼：%s','The phone number you entered must start with a \'+\', then country code and then area code and number. For example, a number in the United States with country code \'1\' would look like this: +1-123-555-1234'=>'輸入的電話號碼必須以「+」開頭，接續國家代碼、區碼及號碼。例如美國 (國家代碼為「1」) 的號碼格式如下：+1-123-555-1234','Unknown authentication mode.'=>'未知的驗證模式。','The username you specified is already enabled.'=>'指定的使用者名稱已啟用。','The username you specified does not exist.'=>'指定的使用者名稱不存在。','Cellphone Sign-in is only available to paid members. <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/gnl1twoFac3/wordfence-signup/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Click here to upgrade now.<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'手機登入僅供付費會員使用。<a href="https://www.wordfence.com/gnl1twoFac3/wordfence-signup/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">按一下這裡立即升級。<span class="screen-reader-text"> (','This is a test email from %1$s.
The IP address that requested this was: %2$s'=>'這是來自 %1$s 的測試郵件。
發出要求的 IP 位址為：%2$s','Wordfence Test Email'=>'Wordfence 測試郵件','We could not fetch a core WordPress file from the Wordfence API.'=>'無法從 Wordfence API 取得 WordPress 核心程式檔案。','An invalid type was specified to get file.'=>'取得檔案時指定了無效的類型。','Blocked by login security setting'=>'遭登入安全設定阻擋','Blocked by Wordfence Security Network'=>'遭 Wordfence 安全防護網路封鎖','<strong>Cellphone Sign-in Required</strong>: Cellphone Sign-in is required for all administrator accounts. Please contact the site administrator to enable it for your account.'=>'<strong>需要手機登入</strong>：所有管理員 [cite: 1] 帳號均需使用手機登入。請聯絡網站管理員為您的帳號啟用此功能。','<strong>INSECURE PASSWORD:</strong> Your login attempt has been blocked because the password you are using exists on lists of passwords leaked in data breaches. Attackers use such lists to break into sites and install malicious code. Please <a href="%1$s">reset your password</a> to reactivate your account. <a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More<span style="font-size:0;"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'<strong>不安全密碼：</strong>登入嘗試已遭封鎖，因為您使用的密碼出現在外洩清單中。攻擊者會利用此類清單入侵網站並植入惡意程式碼。請<a href="%1$s">重設密碼</a>以重新啟用帳號。<a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">了解更多<span style="font-size:0;"> (在新分頁開啟)</span></a>','<strong>WARNING: </strong>Your login has been allowed because you have previously logged in from the same IP, but you will be blocked if your IP changes. The password you are using exists on lists of passwords leaked in data breaches. Attackers use such lists to break into sites and install malicious code. Please <a href="%1$s">change your password</a>. <a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'<strong>警告：</strong>系統已允許你的登入要求，這是因為你之前曾從相同的 IP 位址登入，但如果你的 IP 位址變更，你將會被封鎖。你目前使用的密碼存在於資料外洩事件中流出的密碼清單上，攻擊者會利用這類清單入侵網站並安裝惡意程式碼。請 <a href="%1$s">變更密碼</a>。<a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">了解詳情<span class="screen-reader-text"> (','<strong>CHECK YOUR PHONE</strong>: A code has been sent to your phone and will arrive within 30 seconds. Please sign in again and add a space and the code to the end of your password (e.g., <code>wfABCD</code>).'=>'<strong>請檢查手機</strong>：代碼已傳送至手機並將在 30 秒內送達。請重新登入，並在密碼末尾加上一個空格與代碼 (例如：<code>wfABCD</code>)。','<strong>CHECK YOUR PHONE</strong>: A code has been sent to your phone and will arrive within 30 seconds. Please sign in again and add a space, the letters <code>wf</code>, and the code to the end of your password (e.g., <code>wf123456</code>).'=>'<strong>請檢查手機</strong>：代碼已傳送至手機並將在 30 秒內送達。請重新登入，並在密碼末尾加上一個空格、<code>wf</code> 字母及代碼 (例如：<code>wf123456</code>)。','<strong>CHECK YOUR PHONE</strong>: A code has been sent to your phone and will arrive within 30 seconds. Enter it below to sign in.'=>'<strong>請檢查手機</strong>：代碼已傳送至手機並將在 30 秒內送達。請在下方輸入代碼以登入。','<strong>CODE REQUIRED</strong>: Please check your authenticator app for the current code. Please sign in again and add a space, the letters <code>wf</code>, and the code to the end of your password (e.g., <code>wf123456</code>).'=>'<strong>需要驗證碼</strong>：請檢查驗證碼產生器 App 取得目前的代碼。請重新登入，並在密碼末尾加上一個空格、<code>wf</code> 字母及代碼 (例如：<code>wf123456</code>)。','<strong>CODE REQUIRED</strong>: Please check your authenticator app for the current code. Enter it below to sign in.'=>'<strong>需要驗證碼</strong>：請檢查驗證碼產生器 App 取得目前的代碼，並在下方輸入以登入。','<strong>INVALID CODE</strong>: You need to enter your password and the code we sent to your phone. The code should start with \'wf\' and should be four characters (e.g., wfAB12).'=>'<strong>無效驗證碼</strong>：您必須輸入密碼及傳送至手機的代碼。代碼應以「wf」開頭且長度為四個字元 (例如：wfAB12)。','<strong>CODE EXPIRED. CHECK YOUR PHONE:</strong> The code you entered has expired. Codes are only valid for 30 minutes for security reasons. We have sent you a new code. Please sign in using your username, password, and the new code we sent you.'=>'<strong>驗證碼已過期。請檢查手機：</strong>您輸入的代碼已過期。基於安全性考量，代碼的有效期僅 30 分鐘。我們已傳送新代碼，請使用使用者名稱、密碼及新代碼登入。','<strong>INVALID CODE</strong>: You need to enter the code generated sent to your phone. The code should be a six digit number (e.g., 123456).'=>'<strong>無效驗證碼</strong>：您必須輸入傳送至手機的代碼。代碼應為六位數字 (例如：123456)。','<strong>INVALID CODE</strong>: You need to enter the code generated by your authenticator app. The code should be a six digit number (e.g., 123456).'=>'<strong>無效驗證碼</strong>：您必須輸入驗證碼產生器 App 產生的代碼。代碼應為六位數字 (例如：123456)。','<strong>AUTHENTICATION FAILURE</strong>: A temporary failure was encountered while trying to log in. Please try again.'=>'<strong>驗證失敗</strong>：登入時發生暫時性失敗。請再試一次。','<strong>INVALID CODE</strong>: Please sign in again and add a space, the letters <code>wf</code>, and the code sent to your phone to the end of your password (e.g., <code>wf123456</code>).'=>'<strong>無效代碼</strong>：請重新登入，並在密碼末尾加上一個空格、<code>wf</code> 字母及傳送至手機的代碼 (例如：<code>wf123456</code>)。','<strong>INVALID CODE</strong>: Please sign in again and add a space, the letters <code>wf</code>, and the code from your authenticator app to the end of your password (e.g., <code>wf123456</code>).'=>'<strong>無效代碼</strong>：請重新登入，並在密碼末尾加上一個空格、<code>wf</code> 字母及驗證碼產生器 App [cite: 1] 的代碼 (例如：<code>wf123456</code>)。','<strong>WARNING: </strong>The password you are using exists on lists of passwords leaked in data breaches. Attackers use such lists to break into sites and install malicious code. Please <a href="%1$s">change your password</a>. <a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'<strong>警告：</strong>你使用的密碼存在於資料外洩事故的密碼清單中。攻擊者會利用這類清單入侵網站並安裝惡意程式碼。請 <a href="%1$s">變更密碼</a>。<a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">了解更多<span class="screen-reader-text"> (','<strong>ERROR</strong>: The username or password you entered is incorrect. <a href="%2$s" title="Password Lost and Found">Lost your password</a>?'=>'<strong>錯誤</strong>：您輸入的使用者名稱或密碼不正確。<a href="%2$s" title="Password Lost and Found">忘記密碼了嗎</a>？','<strong>VERIFICATION FAILED</strong>: Two-factor authentication verification failed. Please try again.'=>'<strong>驗證失敗</strong>：兩步驟驗證  失敗。請再試一次 [cite: 203]。','Invalid user ID.'=>'無效的使用者 ID。','Sorry, you are not allowed to list users.'=>'抱歉，您無權列出使用者。','<strong>ERROR</strong>: You can\'t register using that username'=>'<strong>錯誤</strong>：您無法使用該使用者名稱註冊','POST received with blank user-agent and referer'=>'收到使用者代理程式 [cite: 8] 與參照來源欄位空白的 POST 要求','Accessed a banned URL'=>'存取了被封鎖的網址','An error occurred while saving the license: %s'=>'儲存授權時發生錯誤：%s','An error occurred while saving the license.'=>'儲存授權時發生錯誤。','Sorry but your browser sent an invalid security token when trying to use this form.'=>'抱歉，您的瀏覽器在嘗試使用此表單時傳送了無效的安全憑證 [cite: 16]。','Unsubscribe Requested'=>'已要求取消訂閱','Invalid function specified. Please check the link we emailed you and make sure it was not cut-off by your email reader.'=>'指定的功能無效。請檢查寄給您的連結，確保該連結未被電子郵件閱讀器截斷。','Request received via unlock email link to unblock all IPs via disabling firewall rules.'=>'已透過解鎖郵件連結收到要求，將透過停用防火牆規則來解除所有 IP 封鎖。','Request received via unlock email link to unblock all IPs.'=>'已透過解鎖郵件連結收到解除所有 IP 封鎖的要求。','Invalid key provided for authentication.'=>'驗證時提供的金鑰無效。','We received a request to email "%s" instructions to unlock their access. If that is the email address of a site administrator or someone on the Wordfence alert list, they have been emailed instructions on how to regain access to this system. The instructions we sent will expire 30 minutes from now.'=>'我們收到一項要求，要將解除存取鎖定的說明傳送至「%s」。若該地址屬於網站管理員或 Wordfence 警示清單成員，我們已傳送恢復系統存取權限的操作指引。說明的有效期為 30 分鐘。','Your request was received'=>'已收到您的要求','Please choose a different password. The password you are using exists on lists of passwords leaked in data breaches. Attackers use such lists to break into sites and install malicious code. <a href="%s">Learn More</a>'=>'請選擇其他密碼。您正使用的密碼出現在資料外洩事件的洩漏名單中。攻擊者會利用此類清單入侵網站並植入惡意程式碼。<a href="%s">了解更多</a>','Passwords containing a space followed by "wf" without quotes are not allowed.'=>'密碼不允許在空格後方包含不具引號的「wf」。','Automatically generated from previous country blocking settings'=>'根據先前的國家封鎖設定自動產生','Track each scan stage as Wordfence scans your entire site. Along the way you can see the activity log one line at a time or expand the activity log for a more detailed view. Clicking on scan results will reveal detailed scan findings.'=>'當 Wordfence 掃描整個網站時，您可追蹤每個掃描階段。過程中，您既能逐行檢視活動記錄，亦可展開活動記錄以獲取更詳盡的檢視。點擊掃描結果即可顯示詳細的掃描發現。','Scan Progress and Activity'=>'掃描進度與活動','All of your scan options, including scheduling, are now located here.'=>'您所有的掃描選項（包括排程功能）現已集中於此處。','Scan Options &amp; Settings'=>'掃描選項與設定','By default, Wordfence will scan your site daily. Start your first scan now to see if your site has any security issues that need to be addressed. From here you can run manual scans any time you like.'=>'預設情況下，Wordfence 將每日掃描您的網站。立即啟動首次掃描，以確認網站是否存在需處理的安全問題。您可隨時在此處手動執行掃描。','Start Your First Scan'=>'開始您的首次掃描','Set up the way you want the scan to monitor your site security including custom scan configurations and scheduling.'=>'設定您期望掃描監控網站安全的方式，包括自訂掃描設定與排程。','Manage Scan Settings'=>'管理掃描設定','A Wordfence scan looks for malware, malicious URLs, and patterns of infections by examining all of the files, posts, and comments on your WordPress website. It also checks your server and monitors your site\'s online reputation.'=>'Wordfence 掃描會檢查您 WordPress 網站上的所有檔案、文章及留言，以偵測惡意軟體、惡意網址及感染模式。它同時會檢測您的伺服器，並監控網站的線上聲譽。','Close'=>'關閉','Repair Files'=>'修復檔案','Do not repair files on your system unless you\'re ABSOLUTELY sure you know what you\'re doing. If you repair the wrong file it could cause your WordPress website to stop functioning and you will probably have to restore from backups. If you\'re unsure, Cancel and work with your hosting provider to clean your system of infected files.'=>'除非您絕對確定自己清楚操作內容，否則請勿在系統上修復檔案。若修復錯誤檔案，可能導致您的 WordPress 網站停止運作，屆時您很可能必須從備份中還原資料。若您不確定操作方式，請取消修復並聯繫您的主機服務供應商，協助清理系統中的受感染檔案。','Are you sure you want to repair?'=>'您確定要進行修復嗎？','Delete Files'=>'刪除檔案','Do not delete files on your system unless you\'re ABSOLUTELY sure you know what you\'re doing. If you delete the wrong file it could cause your WordPress website to stop functioning and you will probably have to restore from backups. If you\'re unsure, Cancel and work with your hosting provider to clean your system of infected files. If you\'d like to learn more, <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">click here for our help article<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>.'=>'除非您絕對確定自己清楚操作內容，否則請勿刪除系統中的檔案。若誤刪檔案，可能導致您的 WordPress 網站停止運作，屆時您很可能需要從備份中還原資料。若您不確定操作方式，請點選「取消」並聯繫您的主機服務供應商，協助清理系統中的受感染檔案。如需進一步了解，<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">請點擊此處參閱我們的說明文章<span class="screen-reader-text">（將在新分頁開啟）</span></a>。','<strong>WARNING:</strong> If you delete the wrong file, it could cause your WordPress website to stop functioning, and you will probably have to restore from a backup.'=>'<strong>警告：</strong>若誤刪檔案，可能導致您的 WordPress 網站無法運作，屆時您可能需要從備份中進行還原。','Are you sure you want to delete?'=>'您確定要刪除嗎？','Manage scan options including scheduling'=>'管理掃描選項，包括排程設定','Scan Options and Scheduling'=>'掃描選項與排程設定','Reputation Check Status'=>'聲譽檢查狀態','Manage Options'=>'管理選項','Check spam &amp; spamvertising blocklists'=>'檢查垃圾郵件與垃圾廣告封鎖清單','Reputation Checks'=>'聲譽審查','Enable Premium Scan Signatures.'=>'啟用高級掃描簽名。','Malware Signatures Status'=>'惡意軟體簽名狀態','Protect More Sites'=>'保護更多網站','Signature updates delayed by 30 days'=>'簽署更新延遲30天','Signatures updated in real-time'=>'簽名即時更新','Malware Signatures: '=>'惡意程式碼特徵碼： ','https://www.wordfence.com/help/scan/#scan-status'=>'https://www.wordfence.com/help/scan/#scan-status','Scan Status'=>'掃描狀態','Manage Scan'=>'管理掃描','Scan Type: '=>'掃描類型： ','Learn more<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> about the Scanner</span>'=>'深入了解<span class="wf-hidden-xs">掃描器</span>','Scan'=>'掃描','Your computer\'s time:'=>'您的電腦時間：','Generated by Wordfence at %s'=>'由 Wordfence 於 %s 生成','You can also read the documentation to learn about Wordfence\'s blocking tools, or visit wordfence.com to learn more about Wordfence.'=>'您亦可參閱文件以瞭解 Wordfence 的封鎖工具，或造訪 wordfence.com 進一步了解 Wordfence。','Wordfence is a security plugin installed on over 5 million WordPress sites. The owner of this site is using Wordfence to manage access to their site.'=>'Wordfence 是一款安裝於超過 500 萬個 WordPress 網站的安全外掛程式。本網站的擁有者正使用 Wordfence 來管理其網站的存取權限。','About Wordfence'=>'關於 Wordfence','Time'=>'時間','Block Reason'=>'封鎖原因','Block Technical Data'=>'區塊技術數據','If you think you have been blocked in error, contact the owner of this site for assistance.'=>'若您認為自己被錯誤封鎖，請聯繫本站所有者以獲取協助。','Your access to this service has been limited. (HTTP response code 503)'=>'您對本服務的存取權限已受限制。（HTTP回應代碼 503）','Your access to this site has been limited by the site owner'=>'您對本網站的存取權限已遭網站所有者限制','Your access to this site has been limited'=>'您對本網站的存取權限已受到限制','You\'ve chosen to block the network that <span style="color: #F00;">%s</span> is part of. We\'ve marked the networks we found that this IP address belongs to in red below. Make sure you read all the WHOIS information so that you see all networks this IP belongs to. We recommend blocking the network with the lowest number of addresses. You may find this is listed at the end as part of the \'rWHOIS\' query which contacts the local WHOIS server that is run by the network administrator.'=>'您已選擇封鎖包含 <span style="color: #F00;">%s</span> 的網路。我們已將此 IP 位址所屬的網路標記為紅色顯示於下方。請務必閱讀所有 WHOIS 資訊，以確認此 IP 位址所屬的所有網路。我們建議封鎖擁有最少位址數的網路，您可能發現該網路列於末尾，作為「rWHOIS」查詢的一部分——此查詢會聯繫由網路管理員運行的本地 WHOIS 伺服器。','How to block a network'=>'如何封鎖網路','The whois service gives you a way to look up who owns an IP address or domain name that is visiting your website or is engaging in malicious activity on your website.'=>'WHOIS 服務讓你能夠查詢正在造訪你的網站，或是在網站上進行惡意行為的 IP 位址或網域所有者。','Whois Lookup'=>'Whois 查詢','If you did not request this, you can safely ignore it.'=>'若您未曾提出此要求，可以安全地忽略此郵件。','Either you or someone at IP address <b>%1$s</b> requested an alert unsubscribe link for the website <a href="%2$s"><b>%3$s</b></a>.'=>'您或來自 IP 位址 