https://www.wordfence.com/zz1/wordfence-signup/','The Wordfence administrative URL for this site is: %s'=>'此網站的 Wordfence 管理網址為：%s','This email was sent from your website "%1$s" by the Wordfence plugin at %2$s'=>'此電子郵件由您的網站「%1$s」透過 Wordfence 外掛於 %2$s 傳送。','Live traffic now defaults to a summary view. Details are viewable by clicking anywhere within the summary record. To switch to the expanded view, click the <strong>Expand All Records</strong> switch. New installations will only log security-related traffic by default, though your previous setting has been preserved.'=>'即時流量 [cite: 12] 現在預設為摘要檢視 [cite: 12]。點擊摘要記錄中的任何位置即可查看詳細資料。若要切換到展開檢視，請點擊「<strong>展開所有記錄</strong>」開關。新安裝預設僅會記錄安全相關流量，但您先前的設定已保留。','Live traffic defaults to a summary view of all security-related traffic. Details are viewable by clicking anywhere within the summary record. To switch to the expanded view, click the <strong>Expand All Records</strong> switch.'=>'即時流量預設顯示所有安全相關流量的摘要檢視。點擊摘要記錄中的任何位置即可查看詳細資料。若要切換到展開檢視，請點擊「<strong>展開所有記錄</strong>」開關。','Recent'=>'近期','See recent traffic'=>'查看近期流量','Expand All Results'=>'展開所有結果','Show Advanced Filters'=>'顯示進階篩選條件','Blocked'=>'被封鎖','Warning'=>'警告','Bot'=>'機器人','Human'=>'人類','Regular traffic and security-related traffic will appear below.'=>'常規流量與安全相關的流量將顯示於下方。','Traffic logging mode: All traffic'=>'流量記錄模式：所有流量','Login and firewall activity will appear below.'=>'登入與防火牆活動記錄將顯示於下方。','Traffic logging mode: Security-related traffic only'=>'流量記錄模式：僅記錄與安全相關的流量','Wordfence Live Traffic shows you what is happening on your site in real-time, including user logins, hack attempts, and requests that were blocked by the Wordfence Firewall. You can choose to log security-related traffic only or all traffic. Traffic is logged directly on the server, which means it includes visits that don\'t execute JavaScript. Google and other JavaScript-based analytics packages typically only show visits from browsers that are operated by a human, while Live Traffic can show visits from crawlers like Google and Bing.'=>'Wordfence 即時流量功能可讓您即時掌握網站動態，包括使用者登入、駭客攻擊嘗試，以及被 Wordfence 防火牆攔截的請求。您可選擇僅記錄安全相關流量，或記錄所有流量。 流量直接記錄於伺服器端，因此包含未執行 JavaScript 的造訪紀錄。Google 等基於 JavaScript 的分析套件通常僅顯示人類操作瀏覽器的造訪，而即時流量功能可同步呈現 Google、Bing 等爬蟲程式的造訪行為。','Click inside window to resume'=>'點擊視窗內部以繼續','Live Updates Paused'=>'即時更新暫停','Live Traffic'=>'即時交通','Continue'=>'繼續','Congratulations! Wordfence Premium is now active on your website. Please note that some Premium features are not enabled by default.'=>'恭喜！Wordfence Premium 現已於您的網站啟用。請注意，部分進階功能預設為未啟用狀態。','Premium License Installed'=>'高級授權已安裝','View Documentation'=>'檢視文件','Documentation about Wordfence may be found on our website by clicking the button below or by clicking the <i class="wf-fa wf-fa-question-circle-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> links on any of the plugin\'s pages.'=>'有關 Wordfence 的文件，您可透過點擊下方按鈕，或點擊外掛程式任一頁面上的連結<i class="wf-fa wf-fa-question-circle-o" aria-hidden="true"></i>，於我們的網站上查閱。','Documentation'=>'文件','Top Topics and Questions'=>'熱門話題與常見問題','All Documentation'=>'所有文件','To continue using Defiant products and services including the Wordfence plugin, all customers must review and agree to the updated terms and privacy policies. These changes reflect our commitment to follow data protection best practices and regulations. The Wordfence interface will remain disabled until these terms are agreed to.'=>'為繼續使用 Defiant 產品及服務（包含 Wordfence 外掛程式），所有客戶必須審閱並同意更新後的條款與隱私權政策。此項變更體現我們遵循資料保護最佳實務與法規的承諾。在同意這些條款前，Wordfence 介面將持續處於停用狀態。','Agreement to New Terms and Privacy Policies'=>'新條款與隱私權政策同意書','The GDPR is a set of rules that provides more control over EU personal data. Defiant has updated its terms of service, privacy policies, and software, as well as made available standard contractual clauses to meet GDPR compliance.'=>'《一般資料保護規範》（GDPR）是一套賦予歐盟個人資料更多控制權的法規。Defiant 已更新其服務條款、隱私政策及軟體，並提供標準合約條款以符合 GDPR 合規要求。','General Data Protection Regulation'=>'一般資料保護規範','GDPR Information'=>'GDPR 資訊','Upgrade Now to Access Premium Support'=>'立即升級以獲取高級支援服務','Our senior support engineers <strong>respond to Premium tickets within a few hours</strong> on average and have a direct line to our QA and development teams.'=>'我們的資深支援工程師平均<strong>在數小時內回應高級支援單</strong>，並能直接聯繫品質保證與開發團隊。','Premium Support'=>'高級支援','Go to Support Forums'=>'前往支援論壇','Support for free customers is available via our forums page on wordpress.org. The majority of requests <strong>receive an answer within a few days.</strong>'=>'免費用戶可透過我們在 wordpress.org 上的論壇頁面獲得支援。多數請求<strong>將在數日內獲得回覆。</strong>','Free Support'=>'免費支援','The GeoIP database that is required for country blocking has been updated to a new format. This new format requires sites to run PHP 5.4 or newer, and this site is on PHP %s. To ensure country blocking continues functioning, please update PHP.'=>'用於國家封鎖的 GeoIP 資料庫已更新至新格式。此新格式要求網站運行 PHP 5.4 或更新版本，而本網站目前使用 PHP %s。為確保國家封鎖功能持續運作，請更新 PHP 版本。','PHP Update Needed for Country Blocking'=>'國家封鎖功能需更新PHP版本','An admin user with a suspicious username %s was found. Administrators accounts with usernames similar to this are commonly seen created by hackers. It\'s possible a plugin could have created the account, but if you do not recognize the user, we suggest you remove it.'=>'發現一名管理員用戶名稱可疑，為 %s。此類用戶名稱的管理員帳戶通常由駭客所創建。雖然可能由外掛程式自動建立此帳戶，但若您不認識該用戶，建議您將其移除。','An admin user with a suspicious username %s was found.'=>'發現一名管理員用戶，其用戶名稱 %s 存在可疑情況。','An admin user with the username %s was created outside of WordPress. It\'s possible a plugin could have created the account, but if you do not recognize the user, we suggest you remove it.'=>'系統偵測到使用者名稱為 %s 的管理員帳戶是在 WordPress 系統外部建立的。此帳戶可能是外掛程式所建立，若您不認識該使用者，建議您將其移除。','An admin user with the username %s was created outside of WordPress.'=>'一名使用者名稱為 %s 的管理員使用者是在 WordPress 系統外部建立的。','Wordfence\'s Web Application Firewall has been unexpectedly disabled. If you see a notice at the top of the Wordfence admin pages that says "The Wordfence Web Application Firewall cannot run," click the link in that message to rebuild the configuration. If this does not work, you may need to fix file permissions. <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">More Details<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'Wordfence 的網頁應用程式防火牆已被意外停用。如果你在 Wordfence 管理頁面頂端看到顯示「Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆無法執行」的通知，請按一下該訊息中的連結以重新建立設定。如果這沒有作用，你可能需要修復檔案權限。<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">更多詳細資訊<span class="screen-reader-text"> (','Web Application Firewall is disabled'=>'網頁應用程式防火牆已停用','Checking Web Application Firewall status'=>'檢查網頁應用程式防火牆狀態','You only have %s of your disk space remaining. Please free up disk space or your website may stop serving requests.'=>'您的磁碟空間僅剩 %s。請釋放磁碟空間，否則您的網站可能會停止處理請求。','You have %s disk space remaining'=>'您剩餘 %s 磁碟空間','The disk has %s MB available'=>'磁碟剩餘可用空間為 %s MB','Total disk space: %1$s -- Free disk space: %2$s'=>'總磁碟空間：%1$s -- 可用磁碟空間：%2$s','Unable to access available disk space information'=>'無法存取可用磁碟空間資訊','Scanning to check available disk space'=>'掃描以檢查可用磁碟空間','The option "Scan files outside your WordPress installation" is off by default, which means %1$d path and its file(s) will not be scanned for malware or unauthorized changes. To continue skipping this path, you may ignore this issue. Or to start scanning it, enable the option and subsequent scans will include it. Some paths may not be necessary to scan, so this is optional. <a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'「掃描 WordPress 安裝目錄外的檔案」選項預設為關閉，這代表 %1$d 個路徑及其檔案將不會被掃描是否有惡意程式或未經授權的變更。若要繼續跳過此路徑，你可以忽略此問題。或者，若要開始進行掃描，請啟用該選項，後續的掃描便會將其包含在內。某些路徑可能不需要掃描，因此這是選用的。<a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">了解更多<span class="screen-reader-text"> (','%d path was skipped for the malware scan due to scan settings'=>'%d 條路徑因掃描設定而被跳過惡意軟體掃描',', and %d more.'=>'以及另外 %d 個。','Do this if you keep getting locked out or blocked and can\'t access your site. You can re-enable login security and the firewall once you sign-in to the site by visiting the Wordfence Firewall menu, clicking and then turning on the firewall and login security options. If you use country blocking, you will also need to choose which countries to block.'=>'若您持續遭遇鎖定或封鎖而無法存取網站，請執行以下操作：登入網站後，前往 Wordfence 防火牆選單，點擊並啟用防火牆與登入安全選項即可重新啟用相關防護。若您啟用了國家封鎖功能，還需選擇需封鎖的國家清單。','Click here to unlock all IP addresses and disable the Wordfence Firewall and Wordfence login security for all users'=>'點擊此處以解除所有IP位址的封鎖，並為所有使用者停用Wordfence防火牆及Wordfence登入安全功能','Do this if you still can\'t regain access using the link above. It causes everyone who is blocked or locked out to be able to access your site again.'=>'若您仍無法透過上述連結恢復存取權限，請執行此操作。此舉將使所有遭封鎖或鎖定帳戶的使用者，重新獲得存取您網站的權限。','Click here to unblock all IP addresses.'=>'點擊此處解除所有IP位址的封鎖。','Do this if you simply need to regain access because you were accidentally locked out. If you received an "Insecure Password" message before getting locked out, you may also need to reset your password.'=>'若您僅因意外遭鎖定而需重新取得存取權限，請執行此步驟。若在遭鎖定前收到「密碼安全性不足」的提示訊息，您可能還需重設密碼。','Click here to unlock your ability to sign-in and to access to the site.'=>'點擊此處解鎖您的登入權限，即可存取本網站。','These instructions <b>will be valid for 30 minutes</b> from the time they were sent.'=>'本指示自發出時起，<b>有效期為30分鐘</b>。','If you did not request these instructions then you can safely ignore them.'=>'若您未曾要求這些指示，則可安全地忽略它們。','Request was generated at: %s'=>'要求產生於：%s','Either you or someone else at IP address <b>%1$s</b> requested instructions to regain access to the website <a href="%2$s"><b>%3$s</b></a>.'=>'您或 IP 位址 <b>%1$s</b> 上的其他使用者已請求重新取得存取網站 <a href="%2$s"><b>%3$s</b></a> 的權限。','An error occurred: Invalid options format received.'=>'發生錯誤：接收到無效的選項格式。','Invalid response: '=>'無效回應： ','An error occurred: '=>'發生錯誤： ','All of the Firewall settings are now located here. This includes configuration options for the web application firewall, brute force protection, rate limiting, allowlisted URLs, and blocking.'=>'所有防火牆設定現已集中於此處。此處包含網頁應用程式防火牆、暴力破解防護、速率限制、允許清單網址及封鎖功能的相關設定選項。','Got it'=>'明白了','Set up the way you want the firewall to protect your site including the web application firewall, brute force protection, rate limiting, and blocking.'=>'設定您期望防火牆保護網站的方式，包括網頁應用程式防火牆、暴力破解防護、速率限制及封鎖功能。','Firewall Options'=>'防火牆選項','Wordfence protects your site from password-guessing attacks by locking out attackers and helping you avoid weak passwords.'=>'Wordfence 透過鎖定攻擊者並協助您避免使用弱密碼，保護您的網站免受密碼猜測攻擊。','Previous'=>'先前','The Wordfence Web Application Firewall blocks known and emerging attacks using firewall rules. When you first install the WAF, it will be in learning mode. This allows Wordfence to learn about your site so that we can understand how to protect it and how to allow normal visitors through the firewall. We recommend you let Wordfence learn for a week before you enable the firewall.'=>'Wordfence 網頁應用程式防火牆透過防火牆規則阻擋已知與新興攻擊。初次安裝 WAF 時，系統將處於學習模式。此模式可讓 Wordfence 了解您的網站特性，從而掌握保護策略並允許正常訪客通過防火牆。建議您讓 Wordfence 學習一週後，再啟用防火牆功能。','Web Application Firewall (WAF)'=>'網頁應用程式防火牆 (WAF)','Next'=>'下一頁','This is where you can monitor the work Wordfence is doing to protect your site and also where you can manage the options to optimize the firewall\'s configuration.'=>'此處可監控 Wordfence 為保護您的網站所執行的任務，同時也能在此管理各項選項以優化防火牆的設定。','The Wordfence firewall protects your sites from attackers'=>'Wordfence 防火牆保護您的網站免受攻擊者侵害','Manage global and advanced firewall options'=>'管理全球與進階防火牆選項','All Firewall Options'=>'所有防火牆選項','Find the documentation and help you need'=>'尋找您所需的文件與協助','Help'=>'幫助','Block traffic by country, IP, IP range, user agent, referrer, or hostname'=>'依據國家、IP位址、IP位址範圍、使用者代理程式、來源網址或主機名稱封鎖流量','Blocking'=>'阻斷','Block crawlers that are using too many resources or stealing content'=>'封鎖那些消耗過多資源或竊取內容的爬蟲程式','Rate Limiting'=>'速率限制','Brute Force Protection Status'=>'暴力密碼破解防護狀態','Manage Brute Force Protection'=>'管理暴力密碼破解防護','Stops Password Guessing Attacks'=>'停止密碼猜測攻擊',': Disabled'=>'：已停用','Brute Force Protection'=>'暴力密碼破解防護','Blocklist Status'=>'封鎖清單狀態','Enable'=>'啟用','Manage Real-Time IP Blocklist'=>'管理即時 IP 封鎖清單','Blocks requests from known malicious IPs'=>'封鎖來自已知惡意 IP 的要求','Disabled'=>'停用','Enabled'=>'已啟用','Real-Time IP Blocklist: '=>'即時 IP 封鎖清單： ','Firewall Rules Status'=>'防火牆規則狀態','Upgrade to Premium'=>'升級至高級版','Manage Firewall Rules'=>'管理防火牆規則','Rule updates delayed by 30 days'=>'規則更新延遲 30 天','Rules updated in real-time'=>'規則即時更新','Community'=>'社群','Premium'=>'高級','Firewall Rules: '=>'防火牆規則： ','https://www.wordfence.com/help/firewall/#firewall-status'=>'https://www.wordfence.com/help/firewall/#firewall-status','Web Application Firewall Status'=>'網頁應用程式防火牆狀態','Manage WAF'=>'管理 WAF','Stops Complex Attacks'=>'阻止複雜攻擊','Currently in Learning Mode'=>'目前處於學習模式','Web Application Firewall'=>'網頁應用程式防火牆','Click here to upgrade to Wordfence Premium:'=>'點擊此處升級至 Wordfence 專業版：','Discounts for multi-year and multi-license purchases'=>'多年期及多授權購買折扣','Access to Premium Support'=>'高級支援服務','Schedule scans to run more frequently and at optimal times'=>'安排掃描以更頻繁地執行，並在最佳時段運行','IP reputation monitoring'=>'IP信譽監測','Country blocking'=>'國家封鎖','Real-time IP Blocklist blocks the most malicious IPs from accessing your site'=>'即時IP封鎖清單可阻止惡意IP存取您的網站','Receive real-time Firewall and Scan engine rule updates for protection as threats emerge'=>'即時接收防火牆與掃描引擎規則更新，在威脅出現時提供防護','NOTE: You are using the free version of Wordfence. Upgrade today:'=>'注意：您正在使用 Wordfence 免費版。立即升級：','View every issue:'=>'瀏覽所有期數：','%d issue was omitted from this email due to length limits.'=>'由於篇幅限制，此電子郵件中省略了第%d期內容。','%d existing issue was found again and is not shown.'=>'已發現%d個現有問題，且未顯示。','Update includes security-related fixes.'=>'本次更新包含與安全性相關的修復。','Learn More'=>'了解更多','Scanning additional paths is optional and is not always necessary.'=>'掃描額外路徑屬可選操作，並非總是必要。','More Details and Instructions'=>'更多詳情與說明','Firewall issues may be caused by file permission changes or other technical problems.'=>'防火牆問題可能由檔案權限變更或其他技術問題所引發。','The core files scan has not run because this version is not currently indexed by Wordfence. New WordPress versions may take up to a day to be indexed.'=>'核心檔案掃描尚未執行，因為此版本目前尚未被 Wordfence 索引。新的 WordPress 版本可能需要長達一天的時間才能被索引。','Vulnerability Information'=>'漏洞資訊','Plugin contains an unpatched security vulnerability.'=>'此外掛程式包含未修補的安全漏洞。','Low Severity Problems:'=>'低嚴重性問題：','Medium Severity Problems:'=>'中等嚴重性問題：','High Severity Problems:'=>'高嚴重性問題：','Critical Problems:'=>'關鍵問題：','The scan was terminated early because it reached the time limit for scans. If you would like to allow your scans to run longer, you can customize the limit on the options page: <a href="%1$s">%2$s</a> or read more about scan options to improve scan speed here: <a href="%3$s">%4$s</a>'=>'掃描因達到掃描時間限制而提前終止。若您希望延長掃描執行時間，可於選項頁面自訂限制：<a href="%1$s">%2$s</a> 或在此處進一步了解掃描選項以提升掃描速度：<a href="%3$s">%4$s</a>','HIGH SENSITIVITY scanning is enabled, it may produce false positives'=>'高靈敏度掃描功能已啟用，可能產生誤報','See the details of these scan results on your site at: %s'=>'請至您的網站查看這些掃描結果的詳細資訊：%s','Alert generated at %s'=>'警報生成於 %s','Wordfence found the following new issues on "%1$s".'=>'Wordfence 在「%1$s」上發現以下新問題：','This email was sent from your website "%s" by the Wordfence plugin.'=>'此電子郵件由您的網站「%s」透過 Wordfence 外掛程式發送。','Send Unlock Email'=>'發送解鎖電子郵件','If you are a WordPress user with administrative privileges on this site please enter your email in the box below and click "Send". You will then receive an email that helps you regain access.'=>'若您是本網站的 WordPress 管理員，請在下方欄位輸入您的電子郵件地址並點擊「寄送」。您將收到一封協助您重新取得存取權限的電子郵件。','1 more similar file was found.'=>'又找到 1 個類似的檔案。','%d more similar files were found.'=>'又找到 %d 個相似的檔案。','(+ %d more)'=>'(+ %d 更多)','This file is in a WordPress core location but is not distributed with this version of WordPress. This scan often includes files left over from a previous WordPress version, but it may also find files added by another plugin, files added by your host, or malicious files added by an attacker. <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'此檔案位於 WordPress 核心位置，但並未隨此版本的 WordPress 發佈。此掃描通常包含先前 WordPress 版本所殘留的檔案，但也可能發現由其他外掛新增的檔案、你的主機商新增的檔案，或是攻擊者新增的惡意檔案。<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">了解更多<span class="screen-reader-text"> (','This file is in a WordPress core location but is not distributed with this version of WordPress. This scan often includes files left over from a previous WordPress version, but it may also find files added by another plugin, files added by your host, or malicious files added by an attacker.'=>'此檔案位於 WordPress 核心位置，但未隨此版本的 WordPress 一併發布。此掃描常包含先前 WordPress 版本遺留的檔案，但也可能發現其他外掛新增的檔案、主機商新增的檔案，或攻擊者植入的惡意檔案。','Unknown file in WordPress core: %s'=>'WordPress 核心中發現未知檔案：%s','This file is in a WordPress core location but is from an older version of WordPress and not used with your current version. Hosting or permissions issues can cause these files to get left behind when WordPress is updated and they should be removed if possible.'=>'此檔案位於 WordPress 核心位置，但屬於舊版 WordPress 的組件，與您當前的版本不相容。當 WordPress 更新時，主機設定或權限問題可能導致這些檔案殘留，建議盡可能將其移除。','Old WordPress core file not removed during update: %s'=>'舊版 WordPress 核心檔案於更新期間未被移除：%s','Manual block by administrator'=>'由管理員手動封鎖','Access from your area has been temporarily limited for security reasons'=>'基於安全考量，您所在地區的存取權限已暫時受限','Wordfence'=>'Wordfence','Wordfence Security - Anti-virus, Firewall and Malware Scan'=>'Wordfence Security - 防毒、防火牆和惡意程式掃描','https://www.wordfence.com/'=>'https://www.wordfence.com/','Wordfence Security'=>'Wordfence Security']];